hadiths[607]{hadithnumber,text}:
2791,"Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, aik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya ke ehram baandhney wala kaisey kapdey pahney? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab diya : na qamees pahno na amama , na shalwaar , na kot (topi juda labaada (aur na mozey pahno , siwaey iske jisey jootey muyassar na hon wo mozey pahan ley , aur unhein takhnon ke nichey tak kaat ley. aur aisa kapda na pahno jisey kuchh bhi zafran ya waras ( zard chola ( laga ho."
2792,"Hazrat Salim ne apne walid ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya, ehram baandhney wala kaisa libaas pahney ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) na qamis pahney , na amama , na topi juda labaada , na shalwaar , na aisey kapdey pahney jisey waras ya zafran laga ho, aur na mozey pahney , magar jisey jootey na milein to (wo mozey pahan ley aur) unhein ( uper se) itna kaat ley ke wo takhnon se nichey ho jaaein."
2793,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram baandhney waley ko zafran ya waras mein rangey huey kapdey pahnney se mana kya, sath hi farmaya : jo jootey na paaey to wo mozey pahan ley aur unhein takhnon ke nichey tak kaat ley."
2794,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Amr-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne Jaabir bin Zaid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khutba detey huey suna, aap farma rahe they : shalwaar uske liye ( jaaiz ( hai jisey tehband na miley, aur mozey uske liye jisey jootey muyassar na ho, yani ehram baandhney waley ke liye."
2795,"Shoba ne Amr-bin-Dinar se ye riwayat isi sanad ke sath bayan ki ke unhon (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Arafaat mein khutba detey suna, phir yahi hadis sunai."
2796,"ibne-Uena , Hushaim , Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Juraij aur Ayub ( sakhtiyan ( un tamam ne Amr-bin-Dinar se mazkura (uper zikr) sanad ke sath riwayat ki, un tamam mein se akeley Shoba ke ilawa kisi ne ye zikr nahi kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Arafaat mein khutba irshad farma rahe they."
2797,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisey jootey na milein wo mozey pahan ley , aur jisey tehband na miley wo shalwaar pahan ley."
2798,"Hammam ne kaha : hamein ata ibne-abi ribah ne safwan bin Yala bin Umayya se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid ( Yala bin Umayya tamimi (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik shakhs hazir hua. (is waqt) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jaraana (ke maqam ( par they, us (ke badan ( par jubba tha, is par zafran mili khushbu (lagi hui ( thi. ya kaha : zardi ka nishan tha. usne kaha : aap mujhey mere Umerey mein kya karne ka hukm detey hain? ( Yala (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ( itney mein) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi utarney lagi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par kapda taan diya gaya. Yala (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko (is aalim mein) dekhun jab aap par wahi utar rahi ho. ( Yala (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ( ) umr (Raziallahu anhu)) kehney lagey : kya tumhen pasand hai ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi utar rahi ho to tum unhein dekho ? (Yala (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kapdey ka aik kinara uthaya maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf dekha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke saans leney ki bhari awaz aa rahi thi. Safwan ne kaha : mera guman hai unhon-ne kaha : jis tarah jawan oont ke saans ki awaz hoti hai. ( Yala (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ye kaifiyat door hui (to (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Umerey ke barey mein sawal karne wala kahan hai? ( phir us ne farmaya : ( tum apne ( kapdon ( se zardi ( zafran (ka nishan. ya farmaya : khushbu ka asar. dho dalo , apna jubba utaar do aur Umerey mein wahi kuchh karo jo tum apne Haj mein kartey ho."
2799,"Amr-bin-Dinar ne Ata se unhon-ne Safwan bin Yala se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jaarana mein they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik shakhs aaya, main ( Yala (Raziallahu anhu)) bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein maujood tha, us (ke badan) par tukdiyon wala ( libas) , yani jubba tha wo zafran mili khushbu se lathpath tha. usne kaha maine Umerey ka ehram bandha hai. aur mere jism par ye libas hai. aur maine khushbu bhi lagai hai. (kya ye durust hai?) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : tum apne Haj mein kya kartey? usne kaha : main ye apne kapdey utaar deta to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : jo tum apne Haj mein kartey ho wahi apne Umerey mein karo."
2800,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Ata ne khabar di ke Safwan bin Yala bin Umayya ne unhein khabar di ke Yala (Raziallahu anhu) umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha kartey they : kash! main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us waqt dekhun jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil ho rahi ho. (eik martaba ( jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jaarana mein they. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par aik kapdey se saaya kya gaya tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) bhi they. jin mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi shamil they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik shakhs aaya. us ne khushbu se tar jubba pehna hua tha, usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka us shakhs ke barey mein kya khayal hai. jisne achi tarah khushbu laga kar jubbey mein Umerey ka ehram baandha hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh der uski taraf dekha, phir sukoot ikhtiyar farmaya to (is beech mein) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil hona shuru ho gaee. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne hath se Yala (Raziallahu anhu) ko ishara kya, idhar aao, Yala (Raziallahu anhu) aagey aur apna sar ( chadar ( mein dakhil kar diya, us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra surkh ho raha tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kuchh der bhari bhari saans letey rahe phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se wo kaifiyat door ho gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo shakhs kahan hai jisne abhi mujh se Umerey ke mutaalliq sawal kya tha? aadmi ko talash karke hazir kya gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo khushbu jo tum ne laga rakhi hai. usey teen martaba dho lo aur ye jubba ( libaas ( , usey utaar do, phir apne Umerey mein waisey hi karo jaisey tum apne Haj mein kartey ho."
2801,"Qais, Ata se hadis bayan kartey hain, wo Safwan bin Yala bin Umayya se, wo apne walid (Yala (Raziallahu anhu)) se ke jab Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jaarana mein they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik shakhs aaya, wo Umerey ka ehram baandh kar talbiya keh chuka tha, us ne apna sar aur apni dadhi ko zard rang se ranga hua tha, aur us (ke jism ( par jubba tha. us ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! maine Umerey ka ehram baandha hai aur main is haalat mein hun jo aap dekh rahe hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jubba utaar do, apne aap se zard rang ko dho dalo aur jo tum ne apne Haj mein karna tha wahi Umerey mein karo."
2802,"Ribah bin abi Maruf ne ham se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Ata se suna, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Safwan bin Yala ne apne walid Yala (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they ke aik shakhs aaya, us ne jubba pahan rakha tha jis par zafran mili khushbu ke nishanat they, usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! maine Umerey ka ehram baandha hai to main kis tarah karun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh rahe aur usey koi jawab na diya, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi utarti to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke aagey ot kartey, aap par saaya kartey. maine Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : meri khahish hai ke jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil ho, main bhi kapdey mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath apna sar dakhil karun. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil honey lagi, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aapko kapdey se chipa diya. main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kapdey mein apna sar dakhil kar diya aur aapko (wahi ke nuzool ki haalat mein) dekha. jab aap ki wo kaifiyat zaayel kar di gaee to farmaya : abhi Umerey ke mutaalliq sawal karne wala shakhs kahan hai? ( itney mein) wo shakhs aap ke paas aa gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apna jubba utaar do, apne jism se zafran mili khushbu ka nishan dho dalo aur Umerey mein wahi karo jo tum ne Haj mein karna tha."
2803,"Amr-bin-Dinar ne Taaus se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina walon ke liye zul-Hulaifa Sham (Syria) walon ke liye Johfa Najad walon ke liye Qarnul-Manaazil aur Yaman walon ke liye Yalamlam ko meeqaat muqarrar kya aur farmaya : ye ( charon meeqaat ( un jaghon ( par rehney waale) aur wahan na rehney waale, wahan tak pahunchne waley aisey logon ke liye hain jo Haj aur Umerey ka irada karein aur jo un ( maqamat) ke andar ho wo apne ghar hi se ehram baandh ley jo us se zyada Haram ke qareeb ho wo isi tarah karey yahan tak ke Makka waley Makka hi se ehram baandhein ."
2804,"Wuhaib ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin Taaus ne apne walid se unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina walon ke liye zul-Hulaifa Sham (Syria) walon ke liye Johfa Najad walon ke liye Qarnul-Manaazil aur Yaman walon ke liye Yalamlam ko meeqaat muqarrar kya aur farmaya : ye ( maqamat ( wahan ke baashindon aur har aaney waley aisey shakhs ke liye ( meeqaat ( hain jo doosrey ilaaqon se wahan pahunchey aur Haj w Umerey ka irada rakhta ho. aur jo koi un ( maqamat ( se andar ho wo usi jagah se ( ehram ( baandh ley ( jahan se wo chaley yahan tak ke Makka waley Makka hi se ( ehram baandhein.)"
2805,Naafe ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Madina waley zul-Hulaifa se Sham (Syria) waley Johfa se aur Najad waley Qarnul-Manaazil se ( ehram baandh kar) talbiya kahin . Aabdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey ye baat bhi pahunchi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Yaman waley Yalamlam se ( ehram baandh kar) talbiya kahin .
2806,Salim bin-Abdullah-bin umr bin-Khattab ne apne walid se riwayat ki. kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : ahale-Madina ka maqam talbiya (wo jagah jahan se baa-aawaaz buland ( لبيك اللهم لبيك ( kehney ka shuruat hota hai yani meeqaat murad hai) zul-Hulaifa hai ahale-Sham (Syria) ka maqam talbiya ( مهيعه ( wahi ( Johfa ( hai aur ahale-Najad ka Qarn (al-manazil) Aabdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : (mujhey batane waale) un logon ka khayal hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne. maine aap se khud nahi suna. farmaya aur ahale-Yaman ka maqam talbiya Yalamlam hai.
2807,Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat hai unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina walon ko hukm diya ke wo zul-Hulaifa se Sham (Syria) walon ko hukm diya ke wo ( Johfa ( se aur Najad walon ko hukm diya ke wo Qarn (manaazil) se ( ehram baandh kar) talbiya ka aaghaz karein. Aabdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha mujhey khabar di gaee ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Yaman waley Yalamlam se ehram baandhein .
2808,"Rooh bin Ubada ne kaha hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna unse maqam talbiya ke barey mein puchha ja raha tha to unhon-ne kaha : maine suna phir ruk gaey aur) kuchh waqfey (kuchh dinon) ke baad) kaha : un ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu)) ki murad Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se thi (ke Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse suna)"
2809,Sufiyan ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Salim se unhon-ne apne walid (ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se hadis bayan ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Madina waley zul-Hulaifa se Sham (Syria) waley (Johfa) se aur Najad waley Qarn al-manazil se ehram baandhein . ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha mujhey bataya gaya. maine khud nahi suna. ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Yaman waley Yalamlam se ehram baandhein.
2810,"Muhammad-bin-Bakr se riwayat hai kaha mujhey ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, kaha mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna unse maqam talbiya ke mutaalliq sawal kya gaya tha ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha maine suna. mera khayal hai ke unhon-ne hadis ki nisbat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf ki. aap ne farmaya : Madina walon ka maqam talbiya (ehram baandhney ki jagah) zul-Hulaifa hai aur doosrey rastey (se aaney walon ka maqam ( ) Johfa ( hai. Iraq walon ka maqam talbiya zaat arq, Najad walon ka Qarn ( manaazil (aur Yaman walon ka Yalamlam hai."
2811,"Yahya-bin-Yahya tamimi ne kaha maine Malik ke samney (is hadis ki) qirat ki, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka talbiya ye hua karta tha. (لَبَّيْكَ اللَّهُمَّ لَبَّيْكَ ، لَبَّيْكَ لاَ شَرِيكَ لَكَ لَبَّيْكَ ، إِنَّ الْحَمْدَ ، وَالنِّعْمَةَ ، لَكَ وَالْمُلْكَ ، لاَ شَرِيكَ لَكَ ) mein baar-baar hazir hun, aey Allah ! terey huzoor hazir hun, main hazir hun. yaqinan ta'reefein aur saari ne'matein teri hain aur saari badhshahat bhi teri hai. ( kisi bhi cheez mein) tera koi Sharik nahi. aur) Naafe ne) kaha Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) us (mazkura (uper zikr) talbiya ( mein ye izafa farmaya kartey they. ( لبيك لبيك وسعديك , والخير بيديك , والرغباء إليك والعمل ( mein terey samney hazir hun hazir hon teri ita'et ki aik ke baad dusri khush-naseebi ( hasil karne ke liye har waqt taiyaar hon (aur har qism ki khair terey donon hathon mein hai aey Allah ! main terey huzoor hazir hun. (har dam ( tujhii se maangney ki raghbat (dilchaspi) hai. aur tamam amal (teri hi raza ke liye hain.)"
2812,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne Saalim-bin-Abdullah-bin umr aur Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Naafe aur Hamza-bin-Abdullah ke waastey se Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari jab aapko lekar masjid zul-Hulaifa ke paas seedhi khadi ho jati to aap talbiya pukaartey aur kehtey : main baar-baar hazir hun. aey Allah ! main terey huzoor hazir hun, main hazir hun. yaqinan tamam ta'reefein aur saari ne'matein teri hain aur saari badhshahat bhi teri hai) kisi bhi cheez mein) tera koi Sharik nahi. ( Salim Naafe aur Hamza ne) kaha Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke ye Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka talbiya hai. Naafe ne kaha ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) un ( uper zikr ki gaee ( kalimaat ke sath un alfaz ka izaafa kartey : main terey samney hazir hun, hazir hun, teri itaat ki, aik ke baad dusri khush-naseebi ( hasil karne ke liye har waqt taiyaar hun (aur har qism ki khair terey donon hathon mein hai aey Allah ! main terey huzoor hazir hun. (har dam) tujhii se maangney ki raghbat hai. aur tamam amal (teri raza ke liye hain.)"
2813,Ubaidullah (bin-Umar-bin-Hafs-al-madani) ne kaha mujhey Naafe ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh se suntey hi talbiya yad kar liya phir Salim Naafe aur Hamza ki hadis ki tarah riwayat bayan ki.
2814,"ibne-Shahab ne kaha : bila shubah Saalim-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar ne mujhey apne walid ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se khabar di unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us haal mein talbiya pukaartey suna ke aap ke baal judey ( gond ya khitmi bootii wghaira ke zariey se aapas mein chupkey ( huey they. aap keh rahe they.  (لَبَّيْكَ اللَّهُمَّ لَبَّيْكَ ، لَبَّيْكَ لاَ شَرِيكَ لَكَ لَبَّيْكَ ، إِنَّ الْحَمْدَ ، وَالنِّعْمَةَ ، لَكَ وَالْمُلْكَ ، لاَ شَرِيكَ لَك  )  in kalimaat par izafa nahi farmatey they. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zul-Hulaifa mein do rakaat Namaz ada kartey phir jab aap ki ontni masjid zul-Hulaifa ke paas aapko lekar khadi ho jati to aap in kalimaat se talbiya pukaartey . Aabdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) in kalimaat ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jaisa talbiya pukaartey they aur ( sath ye ( kehtey :       (لبيك اللهم لبيك لبيك لبيك وسعديك , والخير بيديك , والرغباء إليك والعمل ( main baar-baar hazir hun, aey Allah ! main terey samney hazir hun, hazir hun, teri taraf se sa'adaton ka talabgar hun, har qism ki bhalai terey donon hathon mein hai. aey Allah ! main terey huzoor hazir hun. har dam tujhii se maangney ki raghbat hai aur har amal teri raza ke liye hai."
2815,"Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha mushrekeen kaha kartey they ham hazir hain. tera koi Sharik nahi. kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey : tumhari barbadi ! bas karo, bas karo) yahin par ruk jaao) magar wo aagey kehtey : magar aik hai Sharik jo tumhara hai tum uske Malik ho. wo Malik nahi, wo log Baitullah ka tawaaf kartey huey yahi kehtey they."
2816,Yahya-bin-Yahya ne hadis bayan ki kaha maine Malik ke samney qirat ki unhon-ne Musa-bin-Aqba se aur unhon-ne Salim bin-Abdullah se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne apne walid ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se suna unhon-ne farmaya : ye tumhara chatiyal medan (baidaa) wo maqam hai jiske hawale se tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barey mein ghalat bayaanii kartey ho. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi aur jagah se nahi magar masjid ke qareeb (yani zul-Hulaifa ( hi se ehram baandha tha.
2817,"Hatim yani ibne- Ismail ne Musa-bin-Aqba se unhon-ne Salim se hadis bayan ki kaha : jab ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se ye kaha jata ke ehram beda se ( baandha jata ( hai to wo kehtey beda wo maqam hai jiske hawale se tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ghalat bayaanii kartey ho. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi aur jagah se nahi, darakht ke paas hi se ehram baandha tha. jab aap ki ontni aapko lekar khadi ho gaee thi."
2818,"Saeed-bin-abi-Saeed Maqbari ne Ubaid-bin-Juraij se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha aey abu Abdur-Rehman ! maine aapko char ( aisey ( kaam kartey dekha hai jo aap ke kisi aur sathi ko kartey nahi dekha. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ibne-Juraij ! wo kon se ( char kaam ( hain? ibne-Juraij ne kaha : maine aapko dekha hai ke aap ( Baitullah ke) do Yamani ruknon ( konon (ke siwa aur kisi rukn ko hath nahi lagaatey, maine aapko dekha hai sabtii ( rangey huey saaf chamdey ke) jootey pahntey hain. neez (isi ke saath) aapko dekha ke zard rang se (kapdon ko) rangtey hain aur aapko dekha hai ke jab aap Makka mein hotey hain to log ( zul-hijja ki) pehli ka chaand dekhtey hi labbaik pukar naa shuru kar detey hain. lekin aap aathwein ka din aaney tak talbiya nahi pukaartey. Aabdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : jahan tak arkaan ( Baitullah ke konon ( ki baat hai to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko do yamnii ruknon ke siwa ( kisi aur rukn ko) hath lagaatey nahi dekha. rahe sabtii jootey to bila shubah maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aisey jootey pahney dekha ke jin par baal na hotey they aap unhein pahan kar wuzu farmatey. (lihaza) mujhey pasand hai ke main yahi ( sabtii jootey ( pahnoon . raha zard rang to bila shubah maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aap ye (rang) istemal kartey they. isliye main pasand karta hun ke main bhi is rang ko istemal karun aur rahi baat talbiya ( labbaik pukarney ( ki to maine aapko (us waqt tak) labbaik kehtey nahi suna jab tak aap ki sawari aapko lekar khadi na ho jati."
2819,"ibne- qaseet ne Ubaid-bin-Juraij se riwayat ki kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath baara (12) baar Haj aur Umerey kiye. maine kaha : aey Abdur-Rehman ! maine aap mein char cheezein dekhi hain aur usi ke ham maana hadis bayan ki magar ( talbiya buland karne ke) qissey mein Maqbari ki riwayat ki mukhalifat ki, un alfaz ke baghair riwayat maana ke saath ki."
2820,Ubaidullah ne Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab rikaab mein paon rakh letey aur aap ki ontni aapko lekar khadi ho jati to aap zul-Hulaifa se (us waqt) buland awaz mein labbaik pukaarnaa shuru farmatey.
2821,"Saleh-bin-kaisaan ne Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, wo bataya kartey they ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt talbiya pukara jab aap ki ontni aapko lekar seedhi khadi ho gaee."
2822,Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne khabar di ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha maine Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap zul-Hulaifa main apni sawari par Sawar huey. phir sawari aapko lekar seedhi khadi ho gaee to aap talbiya pukarney lagey.
2823,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (safar ke) shuru mein zul-Hulaifa mein raat guzari aur wahan ki masjid mein Namaz ada ki.
2824,Urwa ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne farmaya : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram baandha to maine ehram ke liye aur aap ke tawaaf Baitullah se pahley ehram kholney ke liye aapko khushbu lagai. .
2825,"aflah-bin-Humaid ne Qasim-bin-Muhammad ke waastey se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram baandha to ehram ke liye aur tawaaf Baitullah se pahley jab aap ne ehram khola to aap ke ehram kholney ke liye maine aapko apne hath se khushbu lagai."
2826,ham se Yahya-bin-Yahya ne hadis bayan ki kaha : maine Malik ke samney qirat ki ke Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim ne apne walid ( Qasim -bin-abi-Bakr ( se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ehram baandhney se pahley aap ke ehram ke liye aur tawaaf ( ifaaza ( karne se pahley ehram kholney ke liye khushbu lagaatii thi.
2827,Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne hadis sunai kaha : maine Qasim ko Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey huey suna unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ehram kholney aur ehram baandhney ke liye khushbu lagai.
2828,Umar-bin-Abdullah-bin-Urwa ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Urwa aur Qasim ko Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar detey huey suna unhon-ne kaha hujja-tul-wada'a ke mauqe par maine apne hathon se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ehram kholney aur ehram baandhney ke liye zareera (naam ki) khushbu lagai .
2829,"Sufiyan ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Usman-bin-Urwa ne apne walid (Urwa) se hadis bayan ki kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kiya, aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ehram baandhtey waqt kon si khushbu lagai thi? unhon-ne farmaya sabse achi khushbu."
2830,"Hisham se riwayat hai unhon-ne Usman-bin-Urwa se riwayat ki kaha : maine Urwa ko Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna unhon-ne kaha, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ehram baandhney se pahley jo sabse umda khushbu laga sakti thi lagaatii phir aap ehram baandhtey they."
2831,"abu-rajaal ( Muhammad-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Haarisa Ansari ( ne apni walida ( Umra-binte-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Sad-Zarara ansariya ( se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ehram baandhtey waqt jab aap ehram ka irada farmatey aur tawaaf ifaaza karne se pahley ehram kholtey waqt jo sabse umda khushbu paai wo lagai."
2832,Mansoor ne Ibrahim se unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : mujhey aisa lagta hai ke jaisey main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maang mein khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun jabke aap ehram baandh chukey hain. Khalaf ne ''jabke aap ehram baandh chukey hain'' ke alfaz nahi kahey . lekin unhon-ne ye kaha wo aap ke ehram ki khushbu thi. (jo aap ne ehram baandhney se pahley apne jism ko lagwaaii thi.)
2833,"Aamash ne Ibrahim se unhon-ne Aswad se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey aisey lagta hai ke main (ab bhi) aap ki maang mein khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) buland awaz se labbaik pukar rahe hain."
2834,"abu-zuha ne Masruq se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aisey lagta hai jaisey main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maang mein khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun aur aap talbiya pukar rahe hain."
2835,"Muslim ne Masruq se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha lagta hai ke main dekh rahi hun ( aagey ( Wakee ki hadis ki tarah hai."
2836,"Hakam ne kaha : maine Ibrahim ko Aswad se hadis bayan kartey suna unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jaisey main ( ab bhi) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sar ke baalon ko juda karne wali lakeeron ( maang ( mein khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun jabke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram baandha hua hai."
2837,Maalik-bin-Mighwal ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Aswad se unhon-ne apne walid se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne farmaya : bila shubah main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sar ke baalon ko juda karne wali lakeeron mein khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun aur aap ehram ki haalat mein hain.
2838,Abu-Ishaq ne ( Abdur-Rehman ( bin-Aswad ko apne walid ( Aswad-bin-Yazeed ( se riwayat kartey huey suna Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ehram baandhney ka irada farmatey to (us waqt) jo behtreen khushbu aapko muyassar hoti usey lagaatey iske baad main (aap ke ehram baandhney ke baad) aap ke sar aur dadhi main ( khushbu ke) tel ki chamak dekhti.
2839,Hasan-bin- Abdullah se riwayat hai kaha hamein Ibrahim ne Aswad se hadis bayan ki kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : aisa lagta hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maang mein kastoori ki chamak dekh rahi hun aur aap ehram baandhey huey hain.
2840,Sufiyan ne Hasan-bin-Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
2841,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ehram baandhney se pahley aur qurbani ke din Baitullah ka tawaaf karne se pahley aisi khushbu lagaatii jis mein kastoori mili hoti thi.
2842,abu-Awana ne Ibrahim-bin-Muhammad-bin muntashir se unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki kaha maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se us shakhs ke barey mein sawal kiya jo khushbu lagata hai phir ehram bandh leta hai. unhon-ne jawab diya mujhey ye pasand nahi ke main ehram baandhon (aur) mujh se khushbu phoot rahi ho ye baat mujhey aisa karne se zyada pasand hai ke main apne uper taarkol mal loon. phir main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur unhein bataya ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne to kaha hai mujhey ye pasand nahi ke main mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) hon aur mujh (mere jism) se khushbu phoot rahi ho aisa karne se zyada mujhey ye pasand hai ke main apne jism par taarkol mal loon. to Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ehram baandhtey waqt khushbu lagai thi phir aap ne apni tamam beeviyon ke yahan chakkar lagaya phir aap ne ehram ki niyat kar li (ehram ka aaghaz kar liya yani khushbu lagaaney se thodi der baad ehram baandh liya.)
2843,"Shoba ne Ibrahim-bin-Muhammad-bin muntashir se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha maine apne walid ko Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan kartey suna unhon-ne farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khushbu lagaatii phir aap apni tamam beeviyon ke yahan tashrif ley jatey iskey baad aap ehram baandh letey (aur (aap se khushbu phoot rahi hoti thi."
2844,Sufiyan ne Ibrahim-bin-Muhammad-bin-muntashir se unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna unhon-ne kaha : ye baat ke main taarkol mal loon. mujhey uski nisbat zyada pasand hai ke main ehram baandhon aur mujh se khushbu phoot rahi ho. (Muhammad ne kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aapko un ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ki baat batai. unhon-ne kaha maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khushbu lagai phir aap apni tamam beeviyon ke yahan tashrif le gaey phir aap mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) ho gaey. (ehram ki niyat kar li.)
2845,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab se unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah se unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Sa'b-bin-jassaama- Lesi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik zebra hadiyatan pesh kiya aap abu-awa ya waddan maqam par they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey wapas kar diya (unhon-ne ( kaha : jab Rasulullah ne mere chehrey ki kaifiyat dekhi to farmaya : bila shubah ham ne tumhara hadiya radd nahi kiya lekin ham haalate-ehram mein hain (is liye usey nahi kha saktey.)"
2846,Lais-bin-Sad Mamar aur Abu-Saleh un sab ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki (ke Hazrat Sa'b-bin-jassaama (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha) maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik zebraa hidaayatan pesh kiya jis tarah Malik ke alfaz hain aur Leis aur Saleh ki riwayat mein (yun) hai ke Sa'b-bin-jassaama ne unhein (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko) khabar di.
2847,Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur kaha : maine aapko zebrey ka gosht hadiyatan pesh kiya.
2848,Aamash ne Habib-bin-abi-Sabit se unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha Sa'b-bin-jassaama (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hadiyatan zubairaa pesh kiya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ehram mein they so aap ne usey lota diya aur farmaya : ''agar ham ehram ki haalat mein na hotey to ham isey tumhari taraf se (zaroor) qabool kartey.''
2849,Mansoor ne hukm se isi tarah Shoba ne Hakam ke waastey se aur waastey ke baghair ( seedhey-seedhey ( bhi Habib se unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se aur unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. hukm se Mansoor ki riwayat ke alfaz hain ke Sa'b-bin-jassaama (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zebrey ki raan hadiyatan pesh ki. hukm se Shoba ki riwayat ke alfaz hain zebrey ka pichhlaa dhad pesh kiya jis se khoon tapak raha tha aur Habib se Shoba ki riwayat mein hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zebrey ka (eik taraf ka ( aadha hissey hadiya kiya gaya to aap ne usey wapas kar diya.
2850,Taaus ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : (eik baar) Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laey to Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein yad karatey huey kaha : aap ne mujhey us shikar ke gosht ke mutaalliq kis tarah bataya tha jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ehram ki haalat mein hadiyatan pesh kiya gaya tha? (Taaus ne) kaha ( Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ne) bataya : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko shikar ke gosht ka aik tukda pesh kiya gaya to aap ne usey wapas kar diya aur farmaya : ''ham isey nahi kha saktey (kyonke) ham ehram mein hain.''
2851,"Saleh-bin-kaisaan ne kaha : maine abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula abu-Muhammad se suna, wo keh rahe they ke maine abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley yahan tak ke jab ham (Madina se teen manzil door wadi ( qaaha mein they, to ham mein se kuchh ehram ki haalat mein they aur koi baghair ehram ke tha. achcha meri nigaah apne sathiyon par padi to wo aik doosrey ko kuchh dikhaa rahe they maine dekha to aik zebraa tha maine ( fauran ( apne ghodey par zeen kasi apna neza thaamaa aur Sawar ho gaya. ( jaldi mein) mujh se mera kodaa gir gaya maine apne sathiyon se jo ehram baandhey huey they kaha : mujhey kodaa pakda do unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ham is ( shikar ( mein tumhari koi madad nahi karengey. bil-aakhir main utra usey pakda . phir sawar hua aur zebrey ko uske peechhey se ja liya aur wo aik teeley ke peechhey tha. maine usey apne neze ka nishana banaya aur usey gira liya. phir main usey sathiyon ke paas ley aaya. unmein se kuchh ne kaha : isey kha lo aur kuchh ne kaha : isey mat khana , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( kuchh faasley par) ham se aagey they. maine apne ghodey ko harkat di aur aap ke paas pahunch gaya (aur iske barey mein puchha (aap ne farmaya : wo halal hai usey kha lo."
2852,"abu-Nazar ne abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Naafe se unhon-ne abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo ( Umra Hudaibiya mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. yahan tak ke jab wo Makka ke rastey ke aik hissey mein they, wo apne chand ehram waley sathiyon ke sath peechhey reh gaey wo khud ehram ke baghair they. to (achanak) unhon-ne zebra dekha, wo apne ghodey ki pusht par seedhey huey aur apne sathiyon se apna kodaa pakdane ko kaha unhon-ne inkar kar diya. phir unse apna neza maanga (ke unko hath mein thamaa dein ( unhon-ne (is se bhi) inkar kar diya. unhon-ne khud hi neza uthaya phir zebrey par hamla karke usey mar liya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh sathiyon ne usmein se khaya aur kuchh ne ( khaney se) inkar kar diya. jab wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pahunchey to aap se us ( shikar (ke barey mein puchha : aap ne farmaya : ye khana hi hai, jo Allah Taala ne tumhen khilaaya hai."
2853,Zaid-bin-Aslam ne Ata-bin-Yasar se unhon-ne abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se abu-Nazar ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki albatta Zaid-bin-Aslam ki hadis mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tumharey paas iske gosht mein se kuchh baqi hai?
2854,"Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se riwayat hai, ( unhon-ne kaha : ( mujh se Abdullah-bin-Ubai-Qatada ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mere walid Hudaibiya ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rawaana huey unke sathiyon ne (umrey) ka ehram baandha lekin unhon-ne na baandha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bataya gaya ke ghaiqa maqam par dushman ( ghaat mein) hai) magar ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chal padey. abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : main aap ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ke sath tha wo aik doosrey ke sath mil kar hans rahe they. itney mein maine dekha to meri nazar zebrey par padi maine is par hamla kar diya aur usey neza mar kar be harkat kar diya phir maine unse madad chahi to unhon-ne meri madad karne se inkar kar diya. phir ham ne iska gosht khaya aur hamein andesha hua ke ham (aap se) kaat ( kar alag kar) diye jaengey. to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki talash mein rawaana hua kabhi main ghodey ko bahut tez-tez daudaataa to kabhi ( aaraam se) chalaataa aadhi raat ke waqt mujhey banu- ghifaar ka aik shakhs mila maine us se puchha tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kahan miley they? usne kaha : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko t'ahin ke maqam par chhoda hai aap farma rahe they ( pahuncho ( chunanche main aap se ja mila aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) aapko salam arz kartey hain aur unhein dar hai ke unhein aap se kaat ( kar alag kar) diya jaeyga aap unka intizar farma lijiye . to aap ne ( wahan ( unka intizar farmaya, phir maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! maine shikar kiya tha aur uska bacha hua kuchh ( hissey ( mere paas baqi hai Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon se farmaya, kha lo jabke wo sab ehram ki haalat mein they."
2855,"Usman-bin-Abdullah-bin Mohab ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai-Qatada se unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) haj ke liye nikley. ham bhi aap ke sath nikley, kaha : aap ne apne sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) mein kuchh logon ko jin mein abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bhi shamil they hata ( kar aik samt bhej ( diya aur farmaya : saahil samandar ley ke chalo yahan tak ke mujh se aa milo. kaha : unhon-ne saahil samandar ka raasta ikhtiyar kiya. jab unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf rukh kiya to abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ke ilawa sab ne ehram baandh liya ( bas ( unhon-ne ehram nahi baandha tha. usi beech mein jab wo chal rahe they unhon-ne zebrey dekhey. abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne un par hamla kar diya aur unmein se aik maadda zebre ko gira liya. wo (log) utrey aur uska gosht tanaawul kiya (khaya). kaha wo ( sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( kehney lagey. ham ne (to shikar (ka gosht kha liya, jabke ham ehram ki haalat mein hain. (rawi ne) kaha : unhon-ne maadda zebrey ka bacha hua gosht utha liya (aur chal padey) jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey kehney lagey. ham sab ne ehram baandh liya tha jabke abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne un par hamla kar diya aur unmein se aik maadda zebraa mar liya. to ham utrey aur iska gosht khaayaa. baad mein ham ne kaha : ham ehram baandhey huey hain aur shikar ka gosht kha rahe hain ! phir ham ne iska baqi gosht uthaya (aur aa gaey) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum mein se kisi ne abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se ( shikar karne ko) kaha tha.? ya kisi cheez se us ( shikar ( ki taraf ishara kiya tha? unhon-ne kaha nahi aap ne farmaya : iska baqi gosht bhi tum kha lo."
2856,Shoba aur Sheban donon ne Usman-bin-Abdullah-bin-Mohab se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki. Sheban ki riwayat mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum mein se kisi ne unse kaha tha ke wo is par hamla karein ya uski taraf ishara kiya tha? Shoba ki riwayat mein hai ke (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya : kya tum logon ne ishara kiya ya madad ki ya shikar karaya? Shoba ne kaha : main nahi janta ke aap ne kaha : tum logon ne madad ki ya kaha : tum logon ne shikar karaya.
2857,"Yahya (bin-abi-kaseer ( ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Ubai-Qatada ne khabar di ke unke walid ne, Allah unse razi ho, unhein khabar di ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jang Hudaibiya mein shirkat ki, kaha : mere ilawa sab ne Umerey ka ( ehram baandh liya aur) talbiya shuru kar diya. kaha : maine aik zebraa shikar kiya aur apne sathiyon ko khilaaya jabke wo sab ehram ki haalat mein they. phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir hua aur unhein bataya ke hamarey paas us ( shikar (ka kuchh gosht bacha hua hai. aap ne apne ( sathiyon se) farmaya : usey khaao , halanke wo sab ehram mein they."
2858,"hamein abu-Hazim ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai-Qatada se unhon-ne apne walid ( abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu)) se hadis sunai ke wo log (Madina se) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley, wo ehram mein they aur abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) baghair ehram ke they. aur) uper zikr ki gaee ( hadis bayan ki aur is mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas usmein se kuchh ( bacha hua) hai? unhon-ne arz kiya, uski aik raan hamarey paas maujood hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo ley li aur usey khaya.''"
2859,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-rafeea' ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai Qatada se riwayat ki, kaha : abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ke saath mein they, unhon-ne ehram baandha hua tha aur wo khud ehram ke baghair they aur hadis bayan ki aur is mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum mein se kisi insan ne us ( shikar ( ki taraf ishara kiya tha ya unhein ( abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ko) kuchh karne ko kaha tha? unhon-ne kaha : nahi aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap ne farmaya : to phir tum isey khaao ."
2860,"Muaz-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Usman Taimi ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha ham ehram ki haalat mein Talha-bin-Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they. aik ( shikar shuda ( parinda bataur hadiya unke liye laya gaya. Talha (Raziallahu anhu) (us waqt) so rahe they. ham mein se kuchh ne ( iska gosht ( khaya aur kuchh ne ehtiyat bartii. jab Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) bedaar huey to aap ne unki taaiid ki jinhoney usey khaya tha aur kaha ham ne usey (shikaar ke gosht ko haalate-ehram mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaya tha."
2861,"Qasim-bin-Muhammad kehtey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna wo keh rahi thin : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : char janwar hain sabhii eiizaa (takleef) dene waley hain. wo hudude-Haram se bahar aur haram mein) jahaan-paae jayen ( qatl kar diye jayen, cheel, kowa, choohaa aur kaatney wala kutta .) Ubaidullah-bin-muqsim ne) kaha : maine Qasim se kaha aap ka sanp ke barey mein kya khayal hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : usey uske chhoteypan (ghatiyaa rawaiye) ki bina par qatl kiya jaeyga. (jo usmein hai.)"
2862,"Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : panch moozii (jan-daar) hain. hil w haram mein) jahan bhi mil jayen ( mar diye jayen sanp , kowa jiske sar par safaid nishan hota hai, choohaa , kaatney wala kutta aur cheel."
2863,"Hammad-bin-Yazeed ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa (ke waastey se Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : panch ( jaandaar ( moozii hain. haram mein bhi qatl kar diye jaaein. bichho , choohaa , cheel , dhabbon wala kowa aur kaatney wala kutta .) char ya panch kehney ka maqsad mehdood karna nahi tha. aagey jitney naam liye gaey unka bayan tha.)"
2864,ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne uper zikr ki gaee sanad se bhi hadis bayan ki.
2865,"Yazeed-bin-Zaree ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha ( hamein Mamar ne Zohri se unhon-ne Urwa se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : panch ( ja n-daar moozii hain haram mein bhi mar daley jaaein. choohaa , bichho , kowa, cheel aur kaatney wala kutta.)"
2866,hamein Abdur-Razzaq ne khabar di (kaha ( hamein Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hil w haram mein panch moozii ( janwaron ( ko qatl karne ka hukm diya. phir ( Abdur-Razzaq ( ne Yazeed-bin-Zaree ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
2867,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, (unhon-ne) kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : panch janwar hain sab ke sab moozii hain unhein haram mein bhi mar diya jaey. kowa , cheel , kaatney wala kutta , bichho , aur choohaa."
2868,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur ibne-abi-Umar ne Sufiyan-bin-Uena se unhon-ne Zohri se unhon-ne Salim se unhon-ne apne walid ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : panch ( moozii janwar ( hain jo unhein haram mein aur ehram ki haalat mein mar de is par koi gunah nahi. choohaa , bichho , kowa, cheel aur kaatney wala kutta. ibne-abi-Umar ne apni riwayat mein kaha : hurmat waley maqamat mein aur ehram ki haalat mein."
2869,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab ke waastey se khabar di kaha : mujhey Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne khabar di ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : janwaron mein se panch hain, jo sab ke sab moozii hain unhein qatl karne waley par koi gunah nahi. bichho , kowa , cheel, choohaa aur kaatney wala kutta ."
2870,"ham se Zuhair ne bayan kiya (kaha ( hamein Zaid-bin-Juber ne hadis sunai ke aik shakhs ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kiya : ehram wala kis janwar ko mar sakta hai? unhon-ne farmaya : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik ahliya ne khabar di ke aap ne hukm diya ya aapko ( Allah ki taraf se) hukm diya gaya ke choohaa, bichho,  cheel , kaatney wala kutta aur kowa qatl kar diye jaaein."
2871,"abu-Awana ne Zaid-bin-Juber se hadis sunai kaha aik shakhs ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : aik aadmi ehram ki haalat mein kon se janwar ko qatl kar sakta hai? unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik ahliya ne bataya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( ehram ki haalat mein) baawley kuttey , choohey , bichho , cheel , koey aur sanp ko maarney ka hukm detey they. ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) farmaya : aur Namaz mein bhii."
2872,"Malik ne Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : panch ( moozii janwar aisey ( hain ke ehram baandhney waley par unhein qatl kar dene mein koi gunah nahi hai. kowa , cheel , bichho , choohaa aur kaatney wala kutta."
2873,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : maine Naafe se puchha : aap ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se kya suna wo ehram waley shakhs ke liye kin janwaron ko maarna halal qarar detey they? Naafe ne mujh se kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey suna : panch ( moozii ( janwar hain unhein maarney mein unke maarney waley par koi gunah nahi. kowa , cheel, bichho , choohaa aur kaatney wala kutta."
2874,"Lais-bin-Sad aur Jarir yani ibne- Hazim ne Naafe se isi tarah Ubaidullah , Ayub aur Yahya-bin-Saeed un teenon ne bhi Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah Malik aur ibne-Juraij ki tarah hi hadis bayan ki unmein se kisi aik ne bhi Naafe ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke alfaz nahi kahey . siwaey akeley ibne-Juraij ke) albatta ( ibne- Ishaq ne un alfaz mein ibne-Juraij ki pairwi ki hai."
2875,"Muhammad-bin-Ishaq ne Naafe aur Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah se khabar di unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''panch ( moozii janwar ( hain, unmein se jo bhi haram mein qatl kar diya jaey uske qatl par koi gunah nahi.''  phir uper zikr ki gaee hadis bayan ki."
2876,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , Yahya-bin-Ayub Quteba aur ibne- hijr ne ismaeel-bin-Jafar se hadis bayan ki kaha : Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''panch ( moozii janwar ( hain jo unhein ehram ki haalat mein mar de is par koi gunah nahi. choohaa , bichho , kowa, cheel aur kaatney wala kutta.''  alfaz Yahya-bin-Yahya ke hain."
2877,"mujhey Ubaidullah-bin-Umar qawaareerii aur abu-Rabe ne hadis bayan ki (donon ne kaha) hamein himaad-bin-Zaid ne hadis sunai ( Hammad-bin-Zaid ne kaha ( hamein Ayub ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Mujahid se suna, wo Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Lela se hadis bayan kar rahe they unhon-ne Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hudaibiya ke dinon main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif laey. main. ......۔ . qawaareerii ke baqaul apni handiya ke nichey aur abu Rabe ke baqaul apni patthar ki deg ke nichey aag jalaa raha tha aur) mere sar ki) juein mere chehrey par gir rahi thin aap ne farmaya : kya tumharey sar ki makhlooq ( juein tumharey liye ba'ayse azeeyat hain? kaha : maine jawab diya ji haan , aap ne farmaya : to apna sar mundwaa do (aur fidye ke taur par) teen din ke rozey rakho. ya chh (6) miskinon ko khana khilaao ya (eik ( qurbaani de do. Ayub ne kaha : mujhey ilm nahi un (fidye ki Suraton mein) se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kis cheez ka pahley zikr kiya."
2878,ibne-Ulaih ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
2879,"Ibne-Aun ne Mujahid se unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Lela se unhon-ne Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : ye aayat mere barey mein nazil hui : phir agar tum mein se koi shakhs bimar ho ya uske sar mein takleef ho (aur wo sar mundwaa ley) to fidye mein rozey rakhey ya sadqa de ya qurbani kare. kaha, main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua aap ne farmaya : zara qareeb aao. main aap ke (kuchh) qareeb ho gaya aap ne farmaya : aur qareeb aao. to main aap ke aur qareeb ho gaya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kya tumhari juein tumhen eiizaa (pareshani) deti hain? Ibne-Aun ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke unhon ( Kab (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha ji haan ( Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to aap ne mujhey hukm diya ke rozey, sadqey ya qurbani mein se jo aasan ho bataur fidya dun."
2880,"saif (bin-Sulaiman) ne kaha : maine Mujahid se suna wo keh rahe they ke mujhey Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Lela ne hadis sunai kaha mujhey Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke uper (ki taraf ( khadey huey aur unke sar se juein gir rahi thin. aap ne farmaya kya tumhari juein tumhen azeeyat deti hain? maine kaha : ji haan , aap ne farmaya : to apna sar mundwaa lo. ( Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to mere barey mein ye aayat nazil hui phir agar koi shakhs bimar ho ya uske sar mein takleef ho (aur wo sar mundwaa ley ( to fidye mein rozey rakhey ya sadqa de ya qurbani kare. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : teen din ke rozey rakho ya ( kisi bhi jins ka ( aik farq ( teen saa ( chh (6) miskinon mein sadqa karo ya jo qurbani muyassar ho karo."
2881,"ibne-abi-najeeh Ayub Humaid aur abdul kareem ne Mujahid se unhon-ne ibne-abi-Lela se unhon-ne Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein dakhil honey se pahley jab Hudaibiya mein they unke paas se guzrey jabke wo ( Kab (Raziallahu anhu)) ehram ki haalat mein they aur aik handiya ke nichey aag jalaa ne mein lagey huey they. juein unke chehrey par gir rahi thin, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tumhari sar ki juein tumhen azeeyat de rahi hain? unhon-ne kaha ji haan , aap ne farmaya : to apna sar mundwaa lo aur aik farq khana chh (6) miskinon ko khila do. padhi. aik farq teen saa ka hota hai. padhi. ya teen din ke rozey rakho ya qurbani ke aik janwar ki qurbani kar do. padhi. ibne-abi najeeh (ke alfaz hain) , ya aik bakri zabah kar do."
2882,abu-Qilaba ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Lela se unhon-ne Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hudaibiya ke dinon mein unke paas guzrey aur unse puchha tumharey sar ki juon ne tumhen azeeyat di hai? unhon-ne kaha : ji haan to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : sar mundwaa do. phir aik bakri bataur qurbani zabah karo ya teen din ke rozey rakho ya khajooron ke teen saa chh (6)  miskinon ko khila do.
2883,Shoba ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-asbahaani se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-ma'qil se unhon-ne kaha : main Kab (bin-ajra ( (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas ja betha wo us waqt ( Kufa ki aik ( masjid mein tashrif farma they maine unse us aayat ke mutaalliq sawal kiya :                                                                                                                                                  ( فَفِدْيَةٌ مِّن صِيَامٍ أَوْ صَدَقَةٍ أَوْ نُسُكٍ )                                                                                                                                                          ''to rozon ya sadqa ya qurbani se fidya de.''  Hazrat Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke ye aayat mere barey mein nazil hui thi. mere sar mein takleef thi mujhey us haal mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley jaya gaya ke juein mere chehrey par pad rahi thin. to aap ne farmaya : mera khayal nahi tha ke tumhari takleef is had tak pahunch gaee hai jaisey main dekh raha hun. kya tumharey paas koi bakri hai? maine kaha nahi is par ye aayat nazil hui.                                                                                                                                                                                    (فَفِدْيَةٌ مِّن صِيَامٍ أَوْ صَدَقَةٍ أَوْ نُسُكٍ )                                                                                                                                                           (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya : ( tumharey zimmey ( teen dinon ke rozey hain ya chh (6) miskinon ka khana har miskeen ke liye aadha saa khana .) phir Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ye aayat khususi taur par mere liye utri aur umumi taur par ye tumharey liye bhi hai.
2884,"Zakariiyaa-bin-abi-Zayda se riwayat hai kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-asbahaani ne hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha mujhey Abdullah-bin Maaqil ne unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke wo ehram baandh kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley unke sar aur dadhi mein (kasarat se) juein pad gain. us ( baat ( ki khabar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pahunchi to aap ne unhein bula bheja aur hajjaam ko bula kar unka sar moond diya phir unse puchha : kya tumharey paas koi qurbani hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : (aey Allah ke rasool ( mein iski istitaat (taqet) nahi rakhta aap ne unhein hukm diya : teen din ke rozey rakh lo ya chh miskinon ko khana muhaiya kar do miskinon ke liye aik saa ho izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne khas unke barey mein ye aayat nazil farmai : ''jo shakhs tum mein se mareez ho ya iske sar mein takleef ho, iske baad ye ( ijazat ( umumi taur par tamam musalmanon ke liye hai.''"
2885,Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram ki haalat mein seengi lagwaaii.
2886,Hazrat ibne- Buhaina (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Makka ke rastey mein ehram ki haalat main apne sar ke darmyan ke hissey par seengi lagwaaii.
2887,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis bayan ki (kaha ( hamein Ayub-bin-Musa ne nabiiya-bin-Wahab se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha ham Abaan-bin-Usman ke sath ( Haj ke liye) nikley jab ham milal ke maqam par pahunchey to Umar-bin-Ubaidullah ki aankhon mein takleef shuru ho gaee, jab ham Roha mein they, to unki takleef shiddat ikhtiyar kar gaee unhon-ne masla poochhaney ke liye Abaan-bin-Usman ki taraf qaasid bheja. unhon-ne unki taraf jawab bheja ke donon (aankhon) par eilwey ka lep karo. Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke waastey se us shakhs ke mutaalliq hadis bayan ki thi jo ehram ki haalat mein tha jab uski aankhon mein takleef shuru ho gaee to aap ne ( uski aankhon par) eilwey ka lep karaya tha."
2888,hamein Abdus-Samad-bin-Abdul Waris ne khabar di kaha : mujh se mere walid ne hadis bayan ki kaha : ham se Ayub-bin-Musa ne hadis bayan ki kaha : mujh se nabiiya-bin-Wahab ne hadis bayan ki ke (eik baar ehram ki haalat mein) Umar-bin Ubaidullah-bin-Mamar ki aankhen dukhney lagein unhon-ne unmein surmaa lagaaney ka irada farmaya to Abaan-bin-Usman ne unhein rokaa aur kaha ke is par eilwey ka lep kar lein aur Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ke waastey se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan ki ke aap ne aisa hi kiya tha.
2889,Sufiyan-bin-Uena aur Malik-bin-Anas ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se unhon-ne Ibrahim-bin-Abdullah-bin-Hunain se unhon-ne apne walid ( Abdullah-bin Hunain ( se unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Abbas aur Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke abuwa ke maqam par un donon ke darmyan ikhtilaaf hua. Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) shakhs apna sar dho sakta hai aur Miswar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) apna sar nahi dho sakta. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey ( Abdullah-bin Hunain ko) abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf bheja ke main unse (iske barey mein) masla poochhoon (jab main unke paas pahuncha to) unhein aik kapdey se parda karke kuwein ki do lakdiyon ke darmyan (jo kuwein se faasley par lagai jati thin aur un par lagi hui charkhii par se oont wghaira ke zariey dol ka rassa kheenchaa jata tha) ghusl kartey huey paya. ( Abdullah-bin-Hunain ne) kaha : maine unhein salam kaha : wo boley : ye kon (aaya) hai? maine kaha : main Abdullah-bin Hunain hon mujhey Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ki taraf bheja hai ke main aap se poochhoon : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ehram ki haalat mein apna sar kaisey dhoya kartey they? ( meri baat sun kar) Hazrat abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna hath kapdey par rakh kar usey nichey kiya yahan tak ke mujhey unka sar nazar aaney laga phir us shakhs se jo aap par pani undel raha tha kaha : pani dalo us ne aap ke sar par pani undela phir aap ne apne donon hathon se apne sar ko khub harkat di apne donon hathon ko aagey ley aaey aur peechhey ley gaey. phir kaha : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is tarah kartey huey dekha tha.
2890,ham se ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki kaha mujhey Zaid-bin-Aslam ne isi sanad ke sath khabar di aur kaha ke Abu-Ayub ne apne donon hathon ko apne poorey sar par pher unhein aagey aur peechhey le gaey iske baad Hazrat Miswar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : main aap se kabhi bahas nahi kiya karunga .
2891,Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Amr (bin-Dinar ( se ( unhon-ne ( Saeed-bin-Jubair se unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs apne oont se gir gaya. uski gardan toot gaee aur wo fout ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey pani aur berii ke patton se ghusl do usi ke donon kapdon ( ehram ki donon chaadaron ( mein usey kafan do iska sar na dhaanpo . bila shubah Allah Taala usey qiyamat ke din is haal mein uthaaeyga ke wo talbiya pukar raha hoga.
2892,"Hammad ne Amr-bin-Dinar aur Ayub se unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : aik shakhs Arafaat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath waquf mein tha ke apni sawari se gir gaya Ayub ne kaha : uski sawari ne uski gardan tod dali . ya kaha : usey usi waqt mar dala. padhi. aur Amr ne kaha, ''uski gardan ka manka tod diya.''  Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye baat batai gaee to farmaya : usey pani aur berii ke patton se ghusl do, usey do kapdon mein kafan do, isey khushbu lagaao na iska sar dhaanapo . Ayub ne kaha : bila shubah Allah Taala qiyamat ke din usey usi haalat mein talbiya kehta hua uthaaeyga aur Amr ne kaha : bila shubah Allah Taala usey qiyamat ke din uthaaeyga . wo talbiya pukar raha hoga."
2893,"Ismail-bin-Ibrahim ne Ayub se hadis bayan ki. kaha mujhey Saeed-bin-Jubair se khabar di gaee, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath waquf kar raha tha aur ehram ki haalat mein tha ( aagey ( Ayub se Hammad ki riwayat ki manind (tarah) hadis zikr ki."
2894,"hamein Esa-bin-Yonus ne khabar di kaha : ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Dinar ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se khabar di unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, farmaya : aik shakhs ehram ki haalat mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aaya wo apne oont se gir gaya (is se) uski gardan toot gaee aur wo faut ho gaya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey pani aur berii ke patton se ghusl do. uske apne ( ehram ke) do kapdey pehnao iska sar na dhaanpo bila shubah wo qiyamat ke roz aayega . talbiya pukar raha hoga."
2895,Muhammad-bin-Bakr bursaani ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne Amr-bin-Dinar se khabar di ke unhein Saeed-bin-Jubair ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey khabar di. kaha : aik shakhs ehram ki haalat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aaya. ( aagey ( usi ki tarah hai magar ( Muhammad-bin-Bakr ne) kaha : bila shubah usey qiyamat ke roz talbiya kehta hua uthaya jaeyga.  usmein ye izafa kiya ke Saeed-bin-Jubair ne girney ki jagah ka naam nahi liya.
2896,Sufiyan Sory ne Amr-bin-Dinar se unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs ko uski sawari ne gira kar mar diya wo ehram ki haalat mein tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya : usey pani aur berii ke patton se ghusl do usi ke) ehram ke) do kapdon mein kafnaa do iska sar aur chehra na dhaanpo . bila shubah usey qiyamat ke din talbiya pukar ta hua uthaya jaeyga.
2897,hamein abu-Bishr ne hadis sunai kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-Jubair ne hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs ehram ki haalat mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha oontni ne gira kar uski gardan tod di aur wo faut ho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey pani aur berii ke patton se ghusl do usey uske do kapdon ( ehram ki do chaadaron ( mein kafan do na usey khushbu lagaao na iska sar dhaanpo bila shubah ye qiyamat ke din is haalat mein uthaya jaeyga ke iske baal chipkey huey hongey. (jis tarah maut ke waqt ehram ki haalat mein they.)
2898,abu-Awana ne abu-Bishr se hadis sunai unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs ko uske oont ne ( gira kar) us (ki gardan (ka manka tod diya. jabke wo (shakhs) ehram ki haalat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (safar Haj mein Sharik ( tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske mutaalliq hukm diya ke usey pani aur berii ke patton se ghusl diya jaey khushbu na lagai jaey na hi iska sar dhaanpaa jaey. bila shubah usey qiyamat ke roz (ehram ki haalat mein) chipkey huey baalon ke sath uthaya jaeyga
2899,Shoba ne kaha : maine abu-Bishr se suna wo Saeed-bin-Jubair se hadis bayan kar rahe they unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko hadis bayan kartey huey suna ke aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabke wo ehram ki haalat mein tha (usi doran mein) wo apni ontni se gir gaya to usne usi waqt usey mar diya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke usey pani aur beeri ke patton se ghusl diya jaey aur usey do kapdon mein kafan diya jaey khushbu na lagai jaey aur iska sar (kafan se) baahar nikla hua ho. Shoba ne kaha mujhey baad mein unhon-ne yahi hadis (is tarah) bayan ki ke iska sar aur chehra bahar ho. bila shubah usey qiyamat ke din (ehram mein) chipkey baalon ke sath uthaya jaeyga.
2900,"abu-Zubair ne kaha maine Saeed-bin-Jubair ko kehtey huey suna ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aik shakhs ko uski sawari ne gira kar gardan tod di wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un ( sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) ko hukm diya ke usey pani aur berii ke patton se ghusl dein iska chehra . ۔.. aur mera khayal hai kaha, aur sar bahar rakhein. bila shubah qiyamat ke din usey is tarah uthaya jaeyga ke wo buland awaz se talbiya pukar raha hoga."
2901,Mansoor ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik shakhs (safar Haj mein Sharik ( tha usey uski ontni ne gira kar uski gardan tod di aur wo faut ho gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey ghusl do aur khushbu iske qareeb na lao na hi iska sar dhaanpo . bila shubah wo qiyamat ke din is tarah uthaya jaeyga ke wo talbiya keh raha hoga.
2902,abu-Usama ne Hisham se unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa-bin-Zubair ( se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zuba'a-binte-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) (bin-abdul-Muttalib) ke yahan tashrif le gaey aur malum kiya : tum Haj ka irada rakhti ho? unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism main khud ko bimari ki haalat mein pa tii hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : Haj (ki niyat) karo aur shart kar lo aur yun kaho :                                                                                                                                              (اللهم مَحِلِّي حيث حبستني)                                                                                                                                                                    ''aey Allah ! main wahan ehram khol dun gii jahan to mujhey rok dega.''                                                                                  wo Hazrat Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) ki ahliya thin.
2903,Zohri ne Urwa se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zuba'a-binte-Zubair-bin-abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan tashrif le gaey unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main Haj karna chahti hoon jabke main bimar (bhi) hoon to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum Haj ke liye nikal pado aur ye shart kar lo ke) aey Allah !) main usi jagah ehram khol dun gii jahan to mujhey rok dega.
2904,Mamar ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa-bin-Zubair ( se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se usi ( guzishta hadis) ke mutabiq hadis riwayat ki.
2905,abu-Zubair ne Taaus ko aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Ikrima ko Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey suna ke zuba'a-binte-Zubair-bin-abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein aur kaha : main ( bimari ki wjah se) khud ko mushkil se utha paatii hon aur Haj bhi karna chahti hun. aap ne farmaya Haj ka ehram baandh lo aur shart laga lo ke) aey Allah ! ( jahan to mujhey rok dega wahi mere ehram khol dene ka maqam hoga. (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ke) zuba'a (Raziallahu anhu) ne) Haj kar liya.
2906,Amr-bin-haram ne Saeed-bin-Jubair aur Ikrima se unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke zuba'a (Raziallahu anhu) ne Haj karna chaha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya ke wo shart laga lein unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm par aisa hi kiya.
2907,hamein Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim-abu-Ayub ghailaani aur Ahmed-bin-kharaash ne hadis bayan ki. Ishaq ne kaha : ham ko khabar di aur dusron ne kaha : hamein hadis bayan ki. abu-Aamir ne jo abdul-Malik-bin-Amr hain unhon-ne kaha hamein Ribah ne jo ibne-abi-Maruf hain Ata se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne  zuba'a (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : Haj (ki niyat ( karo aur) ehram bandtey huey) shart kar lo ke) aey Allah ! ( tu ney jahan mujhey rok diya wahin mera ehram khatm ho jaeyga aur Ishaq ki riwayat ke alfaz hain (aap ne) zuba'a (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya.
2908,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai unhon-ne bayan kiya ke) zul-Hulaifa ke maqam par waaqe ( darakht ke qareeb ( qiyam ke doran mein) Hazrat Asma-binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu) ko Muhammad-bin-abi-Bakr ki (paidaaish ki) wjah se nifaas ka khoon aana shuru ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke un (apni ahliya Asma (Raziallahu anha) ( se kahin ke wo ghusl kar lein aur ehram baandh lein.
2909,Jafar (sadiq) ne apne walid Muhammad ( Baqar-bin-Ali-Zainul-Aabedeen-bin-Husain-bin-Ali) se unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se Asma-binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis (ke barey) mein riwayat ki ke jab unhein zul-Hulaifa mein nifaas aa gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya unhon-ne un ( Asma-binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu)) se kaha ke wo ghusl kar lein aur ehram baandh lein.
2910,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab se unhon-ne Urwa se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham hijjatul-wadaa' ke saal (uski adaaeygi ke liye) Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rawaana huey aur ham (main se kuchh) ne Umerey ke liye (ehram baandh kar) talbiya kaha, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya : qurbani ka janwar jiske sath ho wo Umerey ke sath hi Haj ka bhi talbiya pukarey aur us waqt tak ehram na kholey jab tak donon (ke liye lagaai gai ehram ki paabandiyon) se aazad na ho jaey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha jab main Makka pahunchi to dinon makhsoosa mein thi maine Haj ka tawaaf kiya aur na Safa Marwa ke darmyan saee ki maine is (surate haal) ka shikwa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kiya to aap ne farmaya : apne sar ke baal kholo aur kanghi karo (phir) Haj ka talbiya pukaarnaa shuru kar do aur Umerey ko chhod do. unhon-ne kaha : maine aisa hi kiya phir jab ham ne Haj ada kar liya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey (mere bhai) Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath taneem bheja. maine (wahan se ehram baandh kar) Umra kiya. aap ne farmaya : ye (Umra) tumharey (us reh janey waale) Umerey ki jagah hai. jin logon ne Umerey ke liye talbiya pukara tha. unhon-ne Baitullah aur Safa Marwa ka tawaaf kiya aur phir ehram khol diye. phir jab wo log ( Haj ke doran mein) Mina se lautey to unhon-ne apne Haj ke liye dusri baar tawaaf kiya albatta wo log jinhoney Haj aur Umerey ko jama kiya tha (hajje-Qiran kiya tha) to unhon-ne ( Safa Marwa ka ( aik hi tawaaf kiya."
2911,Aqeel-bin-Khalid ne ibne-Shahab se unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : ham hijjatul-wadaa' ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley ham mein se kuchh ne Umerey ke liye talbiya pukara aur kuchh ne ( sirf ( Haj ke liye. yahan tak ke ham Makka pahunch gaey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne Umerey ke liye talbiya pukara tha. wo qurbani nahi laya. wo ehram khol de. aur jisne Umerey ka ehram baandha tha aur sath qurbani bhi laya hai wo jab tak qurbani zabah na kar ley ehram khatm na kare. aur jisne sirf Haj ke liye talbiya kaha tha wo apna Haj mukammal kare. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha mujhey (rastey mein) dinon shuru ho gaey. mein Arfa ke din tak dinon hi mein rahi aur maine sirf Umerey ke liye talbiya pukara tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya ke main apne sar ke baal kholun kanghi karun aur Haj ke liye talbiya pukaarun aur Umerey (ke a'amal) chhod dun to maine yahi kiya. jab maine apna Haj ada kar liya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere sath (mere bhai) Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja aur mujhey hukm diya ke main us Umerey ki jagah Umra kar loon jisey Haj ka din aa ja ne ki bina par mukammal karke main uska eharam na khol paai thi.
2912,"Mamar ne Zohri se unhon-ne Urwa se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha Hijjatul-wada ke saal ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (hajj ke safar ke liye) nikley. maine Umerey ke liye talbiya pukara tha lekin (apne) sath qurbani nahi laai thi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jiske sath qurbani ke janwar hon wo apne Umerey ke sath Haj ka talbiya pakarey aur us waqt tak ehram na kholey jab tak un donon se farigh na ho jaey, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : mujhey dinon shuru ho gaey jab Arfa ki raat aa gaee maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! maine to Umerey ke liye talbiya pukara tha. ab main apne Haj ka kya karun? aap ne farmaya : apne sar ke baal kho lo kanghi karo aur Umerey se ruk jao Haj ke liye talbiya pukaro. unhon-ne kaha : jab maine apna Haj mukammal kar liya (to aap ne mere bhai ( Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya unhon-ne mujhey sawari par apne peechhey bithaya aur maqame-taneem se us Umerey ki jagah jis se main ruk gaee thi (doosra) Umra karwaa diya."
2913,"Sufiyan ne Zohri se unhon-ne Urwa se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : ham (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath safar Haj ke liye) nikley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se jo ikatthey Umerey aur Haj ke liye talbiya pukaarnaa chahey pukaarey. jo (sirf) Haj ke liye talbiya pukaarnaa chahey pukaarey aur jo (sirf) Umerey ke liye pakaarnaa chahey wo aisa kar ley. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj ke liye talbiya pukara aur aap ke sath kai logon ne (akeley Haj ke liye) talbiya kaha, kai logon ne Umerey aur Haj (donon) ke liye talbiya kaha aur kai logon ne sirf Umerey ke liye kaha aur main un logon mein shamil thi jinhoney sirf Umerey ka talbiya kaha."
2914,"Abda-bin-Sulaiman ne Hisham se unhon-ne apne walid (Urwa) se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha ham Hijjatul-wada' ke mauqe par zul-hijja ka chaand nikalney ke qareeb-qareeb Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley, kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se jo sirf Umerey ke liye talbiya kehna chahey kahey. agar ye baat na hoti ke main qurbani sath laya hon to main bhi Umerey ka talbiya kehta. (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : logon mein kuchh aisey they jinhoney sirf Umerey ka talbiya kaha aur kuchh aisey they jinhoney sirf Haj ka talbiya kaha aur main un logon mein se thi jinhoney sirf Umerey ka talbiya kaha. ham nikal padey yahan tak ke Makka aagey mere liye Arfa ka din is tarah aaya ke main dinon mein thi aur maine (abhi) Umerey (ko puraa karke us) ka ehram khola nahi tha. maine is (baat) ka shikwa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kiya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apna Umra chhod do apne sar ke baal khol do, kanghi kar lo aur Haj ka talbiya kehna shuru kar do. unhon-ne kaha : maine yahi kiya jab hasba ki raat aa gaee aur Allah Taala ne hamara Haj mukammal farma diya tha to (aap ne) mere sath ( mere bhai ( Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja unhon-ne mujhey sath bithaya aur mujhey lekar taneem ki taraf nikal padey wahan se maine Umerey ka talbiya kaha. is tarah Allah ne hamara Haj pura kara diya aur Umra bhii. (Hisham ne kaha is (alag umrey) ke liye na qurbani ka koi janwar ( sath laya gaya) tha na sadqa tha aur na roza. (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko unmein se koi kaam karne ki zarurat pesh nahi aai.)"
2915,ibne-Numair ne Hisham se pichhli sanad ke sath riwayat ki Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath zul-hijja ka chaand nikalney ke qareeb-qareeb (hajj ke liye) nikley aur hamarey peshe-nazar sirf Haj hi tha. (lekin) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se jo Umerey ka talbiya pukaarnaa chahey wo (akeley) Umerey ka talbiya pakaarey. phir Abda ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
2916,"Wakee ne Hisham se pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : ham zul-hijja ka chaand nikalney ke qareeb Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (hajj ke liye Madina se) nikley ham mein se kuchh ne Umerey ka talbiya pukara, kuchh ne Haj ka aur main un logon mein shamil thi jinhoney sirf Umerey ka talbiya pukara tha. aur (Wakee ne) aagey un donon ( Abda aur ibne-Numair ( ki tarah hadis bayan ki. aur is mein ye kaha Urwa ne iske barey mein kaha : bila shubah Allah ne un (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha)) ka Haj bhi mukammal karwaa diya aur Umra bhii. Hisham ne kaha : aur) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke) is tarah Umra karne mein na koi qurbani thi, na roza aur na sadqa ."
2917,"Muhammad-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-naufal ne Urwa se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : ham Hijjatul-wada' ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley. ham mein se kuchh aisey they jinhoney (sirf) Umerey ka talbiya kaha, kuchh ne Haj aur Umerey donon ka aur kuchh ne sirf Haj kaa. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj ka talbiya pukara . jisne Umerey ka talbiya kaha tha wo to ( Umerey ki takmeel ke baad) halal ho gaya aur jinhoney sirf Haj ka ya Haj aur Umerey donon ka talbiya kaha tha aur qurbani ke janwar sath laey they wo log qurbani ka din aaney tak ehram ki paabandiyon se aazad nahi huey."
2918,"Qasim ne apne walid (Muhammad-bin-abi-Bakr ( se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley aur hamarey peshe-nazar Haj ke siwa aur kuchh na tha. jab ham maqame-sarf ya iske qareeb pahunchey to mujhey dinon shuru ho gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif laey aur mujhey rotaa hua paya. aap ne farmaya : kya tumharey dinon shuru ho gaey hain? (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : maine jawab diya : ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah ye cheez Allah Taala ne Adam ki betiyon ke liye likh (kar muqaddar kar) di hai. tum (sarey) kaam waisey hi sar anjam do jaisey haji kartey hain siwaey ye ke jab tak ghusl na kar lo Baitullah ka tawaaf na karna. (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha (is Haj mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ki taraf se gaaey ki qurbani ki."
2919,Abdul-Azeez-bin-abi-Salma maajishoon ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim se unhon-ne apne walid (Qasim) se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki. ( unhon-ne ( kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley aur Haj hi ka zikr kar rahe they. jab ham sarif ke maqam par pahunchey to mere dinon shuru ho gaey. (is beech mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere (hujrey mein) dakhil huey to main ro rahi thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : tumhen kya rulaa raha hai? maine jawab diya Allah ki qism ! kash! main is saal Haj ke liye na nikalti. aap ne puchha : tumharey sath kya masla hai? kahin tumhen dinon to shuru nahi ho gaey? maine kaha : ji haan aap ne farmaya : ye cheez to Allah ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ki betiyon ke liye muqaddar kar di hai. tum tamam kaam waisey karti jao jaisey (tamam) haji karein magar jab tak paak na ho jao Baitullah ka tawaaf na karo. unhon (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : jab main Makka pahunchi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) se farmaya : tum usey (hajj ki niyat ko badal kar) Umra kar lo. jinke paas qurbaniyan thin unke ilawa tamam sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne (usi ke mutabiq Umerey ka ( talbiya pukaarnaa shuru kar diya. (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha aur qurbaniyan (sirf) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar w umr aur (kuchh) ashaab sarwat (doulet-mand) (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) (hi) ke paas thin. jab wo chaley to unhon-ne (hajj) ka talbiya pukara. (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : jab qurbani ka din aaya to main paak ho gaee. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya to maine tawaaf ( ifaaza ( kar liya. ( unhon-ne ( kaha : hamarey paas gaaey ka gosht laya gaya maine puchha : ye kya hai? unhon ( laney walon ( ne jawab diya ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ki taraf se gaaey ki qurbani di hai. jab (Madina ke rastey Mina ke fauran baad ki manzil ( Muhassab ki raat aai to maine kaha aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! log Haj aur Umra ( donon ( karke lautiin aur main ( akeli ( Haj karke lautoon? kaha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (mere bhai) Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya unhon-ne mujhey apne oont par sath bithaya. unhon-ne kaha : mujhey yad padta hai ke main (us waqt nau umr ladki thi ( rastey mein) main oongh rahi thi aur mera munh ( baar-baar ( kajaawey ki pichhli lakdi se takraataa tha yahan tak ke ham taneem pahunch gaey. phir maine wahan se us Umerey ke badley jo logon ne kiya tha (aur main us se mahroom reh gaee thi) Umerey ka ( ehram baandh kar) talbiya pukara.
2920,"Hammad (bin-Salma) ne Abdur-Rehman se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne apne walid ( Qasim ( se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : ham ne Haj ka talbiya pukara, jab ham sarif maqam par they. mere dinon shuru ho gaey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( mere hujrey mein) dakhil huey to main ro rahi thi (Hammad ne) is se aagey maajishoon ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya magar Hammad ki hadis mein ye (alfaz ( nahi : qurbani Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar w umr aur ashaab sarwat (doulet-mand saathiyon) (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) hi ke paas thi. phir jab wo chaley to unhon-ne talbiya pukara aur na ye qaul (unki hadis mein hai) ke main nau umr ladki thi mujhey oongh aati to mera sar ( baar-baar ( paalaan ki pichhli lakdi ko lagta tha."
2921,Malik ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim se unhon-ne apne walid ( Qasim ( se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne akelaa Haj kiya tha.
2922,"aflah-bin-Humaid ne Qasim se unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : ham Haj ka talbiya kehtey huey Haj ke mahiney mein Haj ki hurmaton ( paabandiyon ( mein aur Haj ke dinon mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rawaana huey yahan tak ke sarif ke maqam par utrey. ( wahan pahunch kar) aap apne sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ke paas tashrif le gaey aur farmaya : tum mein se jiske sath qurbani nahi hai. aur wo apne Haj ko Umerey mein badalnaa chahta hai. to aisa kar ley aur jiske sath qurbani ke janwar hain wo (aisa) na kare. unmein se kuchh ne jinke paas qurbani nahi thi is ( Umerey ( ko ikhtiyar kar liya aur kuchh logon ne rehney diya. albatta Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aur aap ke sath kuchh sahib istitaat sahaba (doulet-mand saathiyon) ke sath qurbaniyan thin. phir aap mere paas tashrif laey to main ro rahi thi. aap ne farmaya : kyon roti ho? maine jawab diya maine aap ki aap ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ke sath guftgu suni hai aur Umerey ke mutaalliq bhi sun liya hai main Umerey se rok di gaee hun. aap ne puchha : ( kyon ( tumhen kya hai? maine jawab diya : main Namaz ada nahi kar sakti . aap ne farmaya : ye ( dinon umrey, Haj mein) tumharey liye nuqsan deh nahi tum apne Haj main ( lagii) raho ummeed hai ke Allah Taala tumhen ye ( Umerey ka ( ajr bhi dega. tum Adam ki betiyon mein se ho. Allah Taala ne tumharey liye bhi wahi kuchh likh diya hai jo unki qismat mein likha hai. kaha : ( phir ( main ( ehramm hi ki haalat mein) apne Haj ke safar mein nikli yahan tak ke ham Mina mein ja utrey. aur (tab) main dinon se paak ho gaee phir ham sab ne Baitullah ka tawaaf ( ifaaza ( kiya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wadi Muhassab mein padao dala. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu)) mere bhai ( ko bulaya aur) unse ( farmaya : apni behan ko haram se bahar ( taneem ( ley jao taake ye ( ehram baandh kar) Umerey ka talbiya kahey aur) Umerey ke liye) Baitullah (aur Safa Marwa (ka tawaaf kar ley. main ( tumhari waapsii tak) tum donon ka yahin intizar karunga. (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : ham nikal padey maine ( ehram baandh kar) Baitullah aur Safa Marwa ka tawaaf kiya. ham lot aaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aadhi raat ke waqt apni manzil hi par they. aap ne (mujh se) puchha : kya tum ( Umerey se) farigh ho gaee ho? maine kaha ji haan phir aap ne apne sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) mein kooch ke elaan ka hukm diya. aap (wahan se) nikley Baitullah ke paas se guzrey aur fajr ki Namaz se pahley iska tawaaf (wadaa') kiya phir Madina ki taraf rawaana ho gaey."
2923,"Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne Qasim-bin-Muhammad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya (jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj ke liye nikley they to) ham mein se kuchh ne akeley Haj ( afraad (ka talbiya kaha kuchh ne aik sath donon (Quran) aur kuchh ne hajje-tamatto ka irada kiya."
2924,Qasim-bin-Muhammad se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (sirf) Haj ke liye aaein thin.
2925,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Umra se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, wo farma rahi thin : zul-Qada ke panch din baqi they ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( Haj ke liye) nikley, hamarey peshe-nazar sirf Haj tha. jab ham Makka ke qareeb pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm farmaya : jiske sath qurbani nahi hai wo jab Baitullah ka tawaaf aur Safa Marwa ki saee kar ley to ehram khol de. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : eid ke din hamarey paas gaaey ka gosht laya gaya. maine puchha : ye kya hai? bataya gaya : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni paak beeviyon (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se (ye gaaey ( zabah ki hai Yahya ne kaha : maine ye hadis Qasim-bin-Muhammad ke samney pesh ki to (unhon-ne ( farmaya : Allah ki qism us ( Umra ( ne tumhen ye hadis bilkul sahi sura mein pahunchaii hai."
2926,Abdul Wahab aur Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Yahya se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
2927,"Ibrahim ne Aswad aur Qasim se un donon ne Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ( Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine kaha : aey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! log ( Haj aur Umra ( do-do manaasik ada karke (apne gharon ko) lautiin gey aur main sirf aik mansak ( Haj ( karke lautoon gii? aap ne farmaya : tum zara intizar karo ! jab tum paak ho jao to taneem (ki taraf ( chali ja naa aur wahan se (ehram baandh kar Umerey ka ( talbiya pakaarna phir falan maqam par ham se aa milnaa. Ibrahim ne kaha : mera khayal hai aap ne farmaya tha : kal . padhi. aur) farmaya : ( lekin wo ( tumharey Umerey ka ajr ( . tumhari mashaqqat ya farmaya : kharch hi ke mutabiq hoga."
2928,"ibne-abi-Adi ne Ibne-Aun se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Qasim aur Ibrahim se riwayat ki) Ibne-Aun ne) kaha : main unmein se aik ki hadis doosrey ki hadis se alag nahi kar sakta. Ummul-Momenin (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! log Haj aur Umra karke lautiin aur aagey (usi tarah) hadis bayan ki."
2929,"Mansoor ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Aswad se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley aur ham usko Haj hi samajhtey they. jab ham Makka pahunchey aur Baitullah ka tawaaf kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya : jo apne sath qurbani nahi laya wo ehram khol de. (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : jitney log bhi qurbani sath nahi laey they. unhon-ne ehram khatm kar diya. aap ki beeviyan bhi apne sath qurbaniyan nahi laaein thin to wo bhi ehram se bahar aa gain. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : (lekin) mere dinon shuru ho gaey they aur main Baitullah ka tawaaf na kar saki jab hasba ki raat aai , kaha : to maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! log Haj aur Umra karke lautiin aur main sirf Haj karke lautoon gii ? aap ne farmaya : jin raaton ( taareekhon ( mein ham Makka aaey they kya tum ne tawaaf nahi kiya tha? maine kaha, ji nahi aap ne farmaya : to phir apne bhai ( Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu)) ke sath maqam taneem tak chali jao aur wahan se ( Umerey ka eharam baandh kar) Umerey ka talbiya pukaaro (aur Umra kar lo ( phir tum falan maqam par aa milnaa . Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagein : main apne barey mein samajhtii hon ke main ( bhi) aapko rokney wali hongi. aap ne farmaya : (apni qaum ki zaban mein aqraa halqaa (be aulad , be baal , yahood haaiza aurat ke liye yahi lafz boitey they) kya tum ne eid ke din tawaaf nahi kiya tha? kaha : kyon nahi (kiya tha !) aap ne farmaya : (to phir ( koi baat nahi, ab chal pado . Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : (doosri subah) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujh se (us waqt) miley jab aap Makka se chadhaai par aa rahe they aur main Makka ki samt utar rahi thi..... padhi. ya mein chadhaai par ja rahi thi aur aap us se utar rahe they ( wapas aa rahe they)....... padhi. aur Ishaq ne ( muthabbita ( ) utarney wali) aur) muthabbit ( ) utarney waale) ke alfaz kahey .) mafhoom wahi hai)"
2930,"Aamash ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Aswad ke waastey se Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath talbiya kehtey huey nikley ham Haj ya Umerey ka zikr nahi kar rahe they. aur aagey (Aamash ne) Mansoor ke ham mana hi hadis bayan ki."
2931,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ( ghandar ( ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hakam se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ( Zainul-Aabedeen ( Ali-bin-Husain se, unhon-ne Zakwan Maula Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya : zul-hijja ke char ya panch din guzar chukey they ke aap mere paas ( khemey mein) tashrif laaey, aap ghussey ki haalat mein they, maine malum kiya : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aapko kis ne ghussa dilaya? Allah usey aag mein dakhil kare. aap ne jawab diya : kya tum nahi janateen ! maine logon ko aik hukm diya (ke jo qurbani sath nahi laaey, wo Umerey ke baad ehram khol dein) magar is par amal karne main to wo kasmasa rahe hain..... padhi.  Hakam ne kaha : mera khayal hai (ke mere ustad Ali-bin-Husain ne) aisa lagta hai wo to kasmasa rahe hain, kaha...... padhi. agar apne is mamley mein wo baat pahley mere samney aa jati, jo baad mein aai to main apne sath qurbani na laataa yahan tak ke main usey ( yahan aa kar) khareedtaa. phir main waisey ehram se bahar aa jata, jaisey ye sab ( sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) Umerey ke baad) aagey hain."
2932,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ne kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Shoba se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zul-hijja ki char ya panch raatein guzarney ke baad Makka tashrif laey. aagey ( Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ne) ghandar ki riwayat ki tarah hi hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kasmasa ke hawale se hakam ka shak zikr nahi kiya."
2933,"Taaus ne Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Umerey ka talbiya pukara tha Makka pahunchein , abhi Baitullah ka tawaaf nahi kiya tha ke dinon shuru ho gaey, unhon-ne Haj ka talbiya kaha aur tamam manaasik (hajj) ada kiye. waapsii ke din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse ( mukhaatab ho kar) farmaya : tumhara tawaaf tumharey Haj aur Umerey ( donon (ke liye kafi hai. ( ab tumhen mazeed Umerey ki zarurat nahi ( magar wo na maaniin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein (unke bhai ( Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath taneem bheja aur unhon-ne Haj ke baad (eik aur) Umra ada kiya."
2934,Mujahid ne Hazrat Aaisha se riwayat ki ke unhein maqam sarif se dinon shuru huey phir wo Arfa mein ja kar paak hui. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya tha : tumhari taraf se tumhara Safa-Marwa ka tawaaf tumharey Haj aur Umerey (donon) ke liye kafi hai.
2935,"Safiya-binte-Sheba ne bayan kiya, kaha Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! log to do (amalon ka ( sawab lekar laut gey aur main ( sirf ( aik (amal ka ( sawab lekar lautoon? to (Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki baat sun kar) aap ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke wo unhein (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko) taneem tak ley jaey. (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : chunanche Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne oont par mujhey apne peechhey sawar kar liya ( rastey mein) apni odhnii ko apni gardan se sarkane ke liye ( baar-baar ( usey uper uthati to ( Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu)) sawari ko maarney ke bahaney mere paon par maartey (ke odhnii kyon utha rahi hain?) mein unse kehti : aap yahan kisi ( ajnabii ( ko dekh rahe hain? (jo mujhey aisa karta hua dekh lega) farmati hain : maine ( wahan se) Umerey ka ( ehram baandh kar) talbiya pukara (aur Umra kiya ( phir ham ( wapas aaey yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pahunch gaey. aap (us waqt) maqam hasba par they."
2936,Amr-bin-Aos ne khabar di ke Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya tha ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko sath ley lein aur unhein maqame-taneem se Umra karwaaein.
2937,"Quteba ne kaha : ham se Leis ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath akeley hajj  ka talbiya pukaartey huey aaey aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sirf Umerey ki niyat se aaein . jab ham maqam sarif pahunchey to Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko dinon shuru ho gaey yahan tak ke jab ham Makka aaey to ham ne Kaba aur Safa Marwa ka tawaaf kar liya phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke ham mein se jis kisi ke sath qurbani nahi, wo ( ehram chhod kar) hillat (bina ehram ki haalat) ikhtiyaar kar ley. ham ne puchha : kon si hillat? aap ne farmaya : mukammal hillat ( ehram ki tamam paabandiyon se aazadi ( to phir ham apni aurton ke paas gaey khushbu lagai aur) mamool (routine) ke) kapdey pahan liye. (aur us waqt) hamarey aur Arfa (ko rawaangii) ke darmyan char raatein baqi thin. phir ham ne tarwiya waley din ( aath (8) zul-hijja ko) talbiya pukara . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke khemey mein dakhil huey to unhein rotaa hua paya. puchha : tumhara kya mamla hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : mera mamla ye hai ke mujhey dinon shuru ho gaey hain. log halal (ehram se farigh) ho chukey hain aur main abhi nahi hui aur na maine abhi Baitullah ka tawaaf kiya hai log ab Haj ke liye rawaana ho rahe hain aap ne farmaya : ( pareshan mat ho ( ye ( haiz ( aisa mamla hai jo Allah ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ki betiyon ki qismat mein likh diya hai tum ghusl kar lo aur Haj ka ( ehram baandh kar) talbiya pukaaro. unhon-ne aisa hi kiya aur waquf ke har maqam par waquf kiya (haziri di, duaein kiin) aur jab paak ho gain to Arfa ke din) Baitullah aur Safa Marwa ka tawaaf kiya. phir aap ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se) farmaya : tum apne Haj aur Umerey donon ( mukammal karke unke ehram ki paabandiyon ( se aazad ho chuki ho. unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mere dil main ( hamesha ( ye khatkaa rahega ke main Haj karne tak Baitullah ka tawaaf nahi kar sakii. aap ne farmaya : aey Abdur-Rehman ! unhein ( ley jao aur) taneem se Umra kara lao. aur ye ( Mina se waapsii par) hasba (main qiyam wali raat ka waqia hai.)"
2938,"ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey suna, keh rahe they : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke khemey mein dakhil huey to wo ro rahi thin. phir ( aakhir tak) Leis ki riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah riwayat bayan ki, lekin Leis ki hadis mein us se pahley ka jo hissa hai wo bayan nahi kiya."
2939,"Matar ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Haj (hijjatul-wadaa') ke mauqe par Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Umerey ka ( ehram baandh kar) talbiya pukara tha. Matar ne aagey Leis ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, ( albatta apni ( hadis mein ye izafa kiya, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahut narm khoo they. wo (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( jab bhi koi khahish kartin, aap usmein unki baat maan letey. lihaza Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bheja aur unhon-ne taneem se Umerey ka talbiya pukara (aur Umra ada kiya). Matar (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha : abu-Zubair ne bayan kiya : (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) jab bhi Haj farmaatiin to wahi kartin jo unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kiya tha."
2940,"Zuhair aur abu-khaisma ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj ka talbiya pukaartey huey nikley. hamarey sath auratein aur bachchey bhi they. jab ham Makka pahunchey to ham ne Baitullah aur Safa Marwa ka tawaaf kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein irshad farmaya : jiske sath qurbani ke janwar nahi hain wo ( ehram se) aazad ho jaey. ham ne malum kiya : kon si aazadi (hillat)? aap ne farmaya : ( ehram ki paabandiyon se) poori aazadi .) Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ham ne apni aurton se qurbat ki, apne ( mamool (routine) ke) libaas pahney aur khushbu (ka bhi) istemal kiya. jab tarwiya (aath (8) zul-hijja) ka din aaya ham ne Haj ka (ehram baandh kar) talbiya pukaarnaa shuru kiya aur hamein (hajje-Quran karne walon ko) Safa Marwa ke darmyan pahlaa tawaaf (saee murad hai) hi kafi ho gaya. (hamein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ye bhi) hukm diya ke gaaey aur oont ki qurbani mein ham saat (7) saat afraad Sharik ho jaaein."
2941,ibne-Juraij se riwayat hai (kaha :) mujhey abu-Zubair ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di kaha : jab ham hillat ki kaifiyat mein aagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke jab Mina ka rukh karne lagein to ehram baandh lein. (hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to ham ne maqame-Abtah se talbiya pukaarnaa shuru kiya.
2942,"Yahya-bin-Saeed aur abd-bin-Humaid ne Muhammad-bin-Bakr ke waastey se ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di kaha unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo farma rahe they Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne Safa, Marwa ke darmyan tawaaf (saee) aik hi martaba kiya tha. (abd-bin-Humaid ne) Muhammad-bin-Bakr ki hadis mein ye izafa kiya : (Safa Marwa ke darmyan) apna pahlaa tawaaf (yani saee jo wo pehli martaba kar chukey they.)"
2943,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Ata ne khabar di ke maine apne bahut se sathiyon ke sath Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne ( ehram ke waqt) sirf akeley Haj hi ka talbiya pukara. Ata ne kaha : Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) char zul-hijja ki subah Makka pahunchey they. aap ne hamein hukm diya ke ham halal (ehram ki paabandiyon se farigh) ho jaaein. Ata ne bayan kiya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : halal ho jao aur apni aurton ke paas jao . Ata ne kaha : ( aurton ki qurbat (aap ne un par lazim qarar nahi di thi balke beeviyon ko unke liye sirf halal qarar diya tha. ham ne kaha : jab hamarey aur yaume-Arfa ke darmyan mahz panch din baqi hain, aap ne hamein apni aurton ke paas janey ki ijazat marahmat farma di hai to (ye aisa hi hai ke) ham (is ( Arfa aaeingey to hamarey khas ang se mani ke qatrey tapak rahe hongey. Ata ne kaha : Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) apne hath se ( tapakney ka ( ishara kar rahe they. aisa lagta hai main ab bhi unke harkat kartey hath ka ishara dekh raha hun. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( khutba dene ke liye) ham mein khadey huey aur farmaya : tum ( achi tarah) jantey ho ke main tum sabse zyada Allah se darney waalaa, tum sabse zyada sachcha aur tum sabse zyada paarsaa hun. agar mere sath qurbani na hoti to main bhi waisey halal ( ehram se farigh (ho jata jaisey tum halal huey ho. agar wo cheez pahley mere samney aa jati jo baad mein aai to main qurbani apne sath na laataa. lihaza tum sab halal ( ehram se farigh (ho jao . chunanche phir ham halal ho gaey. ham ne (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baat ko) suna aur itaat ki. Ata ne kaha : Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya : ( itney mein) Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) apni zimme-dari se (faarigh ho kar) pahunch gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( unse ( puchha : ( Ali ( tum ne kis (hajj) ka talbiya pukara tha? unhon-ne jawab diya : jiska Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pukara . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : qurbani karo aur ehram hi ki haalat mein raho. ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) bayan kiya : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye bhi apne sath qurbani (ke janwar ( laey they. suraaqa-bin-Malik-bin-ja'sham (Raziallahu anhu) ne malum kiya aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ye (hajj ke mahinon mein Umra karna) sirf hamarey isi saal ke liye (jaaiz hua) hai ya hamesha ke liye? aap ne farmaya : hamesha ke liye."
2944,"abdul-Malik-bin-abi-Sulaiman ne Ata se unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj ka ( ehram baandh kar) talbiya kaha, jab ham Makka pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke ham halal ho jayen aur usey ( Haj ki niyat ko) Umerey mein badal dein. ye baat hamein bahut nagawar (burii) lagi aur us se hamarey dil bahut tang huey ( hamarey is beichainii ki khabar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pahunch gaee. malum nahi ke aapko aasman se (bazariey wahi) us cheez ki khabar pahunchi ya logon ke zariey se koi cheez malum hui. aap ne farmaya : aey logo ! halal ho jao (ehram khol do) agar mere sath qurbani na hoti to main bhi wahi karta jis tarah tum ne kiya hai (Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) bayan kiya : ham halal ( ehram se aazad (ho gaey yahan tak ke apni beeviyon se qurbat bhi ki aur (wo sab kuchh ( kiya jo halal ( ehram ke baghair ( insan karta hai. yahan tak ke tarwiya ka din ( aath (8) zul-hijja ( aa gaya aur ham ne Makka ko peechhey chhod ( khair baad kaha (aur Haj ka ( ehram baandh kar) talbiya kehney lagey."
2945,"Musa-bin-Naafe ne kaha : main Umerey ki niyat se yaum tarwiya ( aath (8) zul-hijja ( se char din pahley Makka pahuncha logon ne kaha : ab to tumhara Makki Haj hoga. (main unki baatein sun kar) Ata-bin-abi-Ribah ke yahan hazir hua aur unse (is masley ke barey mein) fatwa poochha. Ata ne jawab diya : mujhey Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke unhon-ne us saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj ki khush-naseebi hasil ki thi. logon ne Haj afraad ka (ehram baandh kar) talbiya kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : apne ehram se farigh ho jao. Baitullah ka aur Safa aur Marwa ka tawaaf (saee) karo. apne baal chhotey karo aur halal (ehram se aazad) ho jao jab tarwiya (aath (8) zul-hijja) ka din aa jaey to Haj ka (ehram baandh kar) talbiya kaho aur (hajj afraad ko) jiske liye tum aaey they usey hajje-tamatto bana lo. sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne kaha : (aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ( ham isey kaisey hajje-tamatto bana lein? ham ne to sirf Haj ka naam lekar talbiya kaha tha aap ne farmaya : maine tumhen jo hukm diya hai wahi karo. agar main apne sath qurbani na laataa to isi tarah karta jis tarah tumhen hukm de raha hun. lekin mujh par) ehram ki wjah se) haram karda cheezein us waqt tak halal nahi hon gii jab tak ke qurbani apni qurbaan gaah mein nahi pahunch jati. is par logon ne waisaa hi kiya. (jiska aap ne hukm diya tha.)"
2946,abu-Bishr ne Ata-bin-abi-Ribah se unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : ham Haj ka talbiya kehtey huey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (Makka) aaey aap ne hamein hukm diya ke ham is (hajj ki niyat aur ehram ko) Umerey mein badal dein aur (umrey ke baad) halal (umrey se farigh) ho jayen (hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath qurbani thi isliye aap apne Haj ko Umra nahi bana saktey they.
2947,"Shoba ne kaha : maine Qatada se suna, wo abu-Nazra se hadis bayan kar rahe they, kaha : Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) hajje-tamatto ka hukm diya kartey they aur ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) us se mana farmatey they. (abu-Nazra ne) kaha : maine is cheez ka zikr Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se kiya. unhon-ne farmaya : mere hi zariey se (hajj ki) ye hadis phailii hai. ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (ja kar) hajje-tamatto kiya tha. jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) (khaleefa bin kar) khadey huey ( bahaisiyat khaleefa khutba diyaa) to unhon ne farmaya : bila shubah Allah Taala apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye jo cheez jis zariey se chahta halal kar deta tha aur bila shubah Quraan ne jahan-jahan (jis-jis mamley mein) utarnaa tha, utar chuka. lihaza tum Allah ke liye Haj ko aur Umerey ko mukammal karo, jis tarah (alag-alag naam lekar) Allah Taala ne tumhen hukm diya hai. aur un aurton se hutamii (mukammal) taur par nikah kiya karo (waqti nahi). agar mere paas koi aisa shakhs laya gaya jisne kisi aurat se kisi khas muddat tak ke liye nikah kiya hoga to main usey pattharon se rajm (sangsaar) karunga."
2948,"hamein Hammam ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne usi (uper zikr ki gaee) sanad se hadis bayan ki, aur (apni) hadis mein kaha : apne Haj ko apne Umerey se alag (ada kiya) karo. bila shubah ye tumharey Haj ko aur tumharey Umerey ko zyada mukammal karne wala hai."
2949,"Mujahid ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( Haj ke liye) aaey aur ham keh rahe they : aey Allah ! main Haj karne ke liye hazir hun ( hamari niyat Haj ki thi rastey mein) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya. ke ham usey Umra bana lein. (aur ''labbaik Umra'' kahin .)"
2950,"ham se Hatim-bin-Ismail madni ne Jafar (sadiq) bin-Muhammad (al-baaqer) se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan aaey, unhon-ne sab ke mutaalliq poochhna shuru kiya. yahan tak ke mujh par aa kar ruk gaey, maine bataya : main Muhammad-bin-Ali-bin Husain hon, unhon-ne (az-raah shafqat) apna hath badha kar mere sar par rakha , phir mera uper , phir nichey ka batan khola aur) intihai shafqat aur mohabbat se) apni hatheli mere seeney ke darmyan rakh di, un dinon mein bilkul naujawaan tha, farmaney lagey : mere bhatijey tumhen khush aamadeed ! tum jo chaho poochh saktey ho, maine unse sawal kiya, wo un dinon naa-beenaa ho chukey they. (us waqt) Namaz ka waqt ho gaya tha. aur wo motii bunaaii ka aik odhney wala kapda lapet kar (namaz ke liye) khadey ho gaey. wo jab bhi us (ke aik pallu ( ko (doosri taraf ( kandhey par daltey to chhota honey ki bina par uske donon pallu wapas aa jatey jabke unki ( badi ( chadar unke pahlu mein aik khoontii par latkii hui thi. unhon-ne hamein Namaz padhai , (namaz se farigh ho kar) maine kaha : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Haj ke barey mein bataiye . unhon-ne apne hath se ishara kya aur nau (9) ki girah banai , aur kehney lagey : bila shubah nau (9) saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rukey rahe Haj nahi kiya, iske baad dasween saal Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon mein elaan karwaya ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Haj kar rahe hain. (ye elaan suntey hi) bahut zyada log Madina mein aa gaey. wo sab is baat ke khaahishmand they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) karein aur jo kuchh Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) karein is par amal karein.  (to) ham sab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley yahan tak ke zul-Hulaifa pahunch gaey. (wahan) Hazrat Asma-binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu) ne Muhammad-bin-abi-Bakr ko janm diya. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf paigham bhi bheja ke (zachgii ki is haalat mein ab) main kya karun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ghusl karo, kapdey ka langot kaso , aur Haj ka ehram baandh lo. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( zul-Hulaifa ki) masjid mein Namaz ada ki. aur apni oontni par Sawar ho gaey. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki oontni Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko lekar beda ke maqam par seedhi khadi hui. to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney , taa-had nigaah piyaadey aur sawar hi dekhey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daain , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baain , aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey bhi yahi haal tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey darmyan ( maujood ( they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par Quraan nazil hota tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi uski ( haqiqi ( tafseer jantey they. jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kartey they ham bhi is par amal kartey they. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Allah ki) tauheed ka talbiya pukara                                                                                                                                                          (لبيك اللهم لبيك . . لبيك لا شريك لك لبيك . . إن الحمد والنعمة لك والملك . . لا شريك لك )                                                                                          aur logon ne wahi talbiya pukara jo (kuchh alfaz ke izaafey ke saath) wo aaj pukaartey hain. aap ne unke talbiya mein kisi baat ko mustarad nahi kiya aur apna wahi talbiya (jo pukar rahe they) pukaartey rahe. Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : hamari niyat Haj ke ilawa koi (aur) na thi, (hajj ke mahinon mein) Umerey ko ham jantey (tak) na they. yahan tak ke jab ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Makka gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hajre-Aswad ka istilaam ( hath ya honton se chhoonaa ( kiya, phir ( tawaaf shuru kiya ( , teen chakkaron mein chhotey qadam uthatey , kandhon ko harkat detey huey, tez chaley, aur char chakkaron mein) aaraam se) chaley, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maqaame-Ibraaheem ki taraf badhey aur ye aayat tilawat farmai                             (وَاتَّخِذُوا مِن مَّقَامِ إِبْرَ‌اهِيمَ مُصَلًّى)                                                                                                                                                            aur maqaame-Ibraaheem ( jahan aap khadey huey they) ko Namaz ki jagah banao. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maqaame-Ibraaheem ko apne aur Baitullah ke darmyan rakha. mere walid (Muhammad-al-baaqer) kaha kartey they. aur mujhey malum nahi ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ilawa kisi aur (ke hawale) se ye kaha ho. ke aap do rakaton main (قُلْ هُوَ اللَّـهُ أَحَدٌ (aur (قُلْ يَا أَيُّهَا الْكَافِرُ‌ونَ) padha kartey they. phir aap hajre-Aswad ke paas tashrif laaey, iska istilaam kiya aur baabe-Safa se Safa (pahaadii) ki taraf nikley. jab aap (pahaad) Safa ke qareeb pahunchey to ye aayat tilawat farmai :                                                                                                                                      (إِنَّ الصَّفَا وَالْمَرْ‌وَةَ مِن شَعَائِرِ‌اللَّہِ)                                                                                                                                                        ''Safa aur Marwa Allah ke shuaair ( muqarrar karda alamaton ( mein se hain.'' main (bhi saee ki) wahin se shuruat kar raha hun jis (ke zikr) se Allah Taala ne shuruat farmaai. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safa se (saee ki) shuruat farmaai, is par chadhtey yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ko dekh liya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qibla rukh huey, Allah ki whdaniyat aur badai bayan farmai aur kaha : Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, wo akelaa hai, saari badhshahat usi ki hai aur saari tareef usi ke liye hai. akeley Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, us ne apna wada khub pura kiya, apne bandey ki nusret farmaai, tanha (usi ne) saari jamaton ( faujon ( ko shikast di. in ( kalimaat (ke beech mein dua farmai. aap ne ye kalimaat teen martaba irshad farmaai they. phir Marwa ki taraf utrey . yahan tak ke jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qadam Mubarak wadi ki taraaii mein padey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saee farmai, ( tez qadam chaley ( jab wo (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qadam Mubarak Marwa ki) chadhai chadhney lagey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( mamool (routine) ki raftaar se) chalney lagey yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Marwa ki taraf pahunch gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Marwa par isi tarah kiya jis tarah Safa par kiya tha. jab Marwa par aakhiri chakkar tha to farmaya : agar pahley mere samney wo baat hoti jo baad mein aai to main qurbani sath na laataa , aur is (ibadet ke amal) ko Umerey mein badal deta. lihaza tum mein se jiske sath qurbani nahi, wo halal ho jaey aur is (ibadet ke amal) ko Umra qarar de ley. ( itney mein) suraaqa-bin-Malik Jaasham (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ( Haj ke mahinon mein Umra karna) hamarey isi saal ke liye ( khas ( hai ya hamesha ke liye? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni ( donon hathon ki) ungliyan aik doosrey mein dakhil kin, aur farmaya : Umra , Haj mein dakhil ho gaya. do martaba (aisa kiya aur sath hi farmaya :) sirf isi saal ke liye nahi balke hamesha-hamesha ke liye. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yaman se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qurbani ki oontniyan lekar aaey. unhon-ne Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko dekha ke wo un logon mein se thin jo ehram se farigh ho chukey they. rangeen kapdey pahan liye they aur surma lagaya hua hai. usey unhon (Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) ne unke liye naa-durust qarar diya. unhon-ne jawab diya : mere walid giraamii ( Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ne mujhey aisa karne ka hukm diya hai. (Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Iraq mein kaha kartey they : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas , us kaam ki wjah se jo Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne kiya tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unke khilaf ubhaarney ke liye gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is baat ke mutaalliq poochhney ke liye jo unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barey mein kahi thi. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko (ye bhi) bataya ke maine unke us kaam ( ehram kholney ( par aetraz kiya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya : Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne sach kaha hai, us ne bilkul sach kaha hai. aur tum ne jab Haj ki niyat ki thi to kya kaha tha? maine jawab diya maine kaha tha : aey Allah ! main bhi usi (ibadet ke amal) ke liye talbiya pukarta hun. jiske liye terey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne talbiya pukara hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere sath qurbani hai. (main Umerey ke baad halal nahi ho sakta aur tumhari bhi niyat meri niyat jaisi hai, lihaza ( tum bhi Umerey se farigh honey ke baad ehram mat kholnaa. (hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : janwaron ki majmooii tadaad jo Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yaman se laey they aur jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sath lekar aaey they, aik sau thi. phir ( Umerey ke baad) tamam logon ne ( jinke paas qurbaniyan nahi thiin) ehram khol liya aur baal katarwaa liye magar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur wo log jinke sath qurbaniyan thin ( unhon-ne ehram nahi khola ), jab tarwiya ( aath (8) zul-hijja (ka din aaya to log Mina ki taraf rawaana huey, Haj (ka ehram baandh kar us (ka talbiya pukara. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par Sawar ho gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahan (Minaa mein) Zuhar, Asr, maghrib , isha aur fajr ki namazein ada farmaein . phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kuchh der thahrey rahe yahan tak ke suraj tuloo ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke baalon se bana hua yak khema Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye namra mein laga diya jaey, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chal padey , Quraish ko is barey mein koi shak na tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mash'are haram ke paas ja kar thahar jaengey. jaisa ke Quraish jahiliyat mein kiya kartey they. ( lekin) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( wahan se aagey ( guzar gaey yahan tak ke Arafaat mein pahunch gaey. wahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wadi namra mein apne liye khema laga hua mila. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein thaher gaey. jab suraj dhala to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (apni oontni ( qaswaa ko laney ka hukm diya, is par aap ke liye paalaan kas diya gaya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wadi ( Arfa (ke darmyan tashrif ley aaey, aur logon ko khutba diya : tumharey khoon aur amwaal aik doosrey par) aisey ( haram hain jaisey aaj ke din ki hurmat is mahiney aur is Shahar mein hai aur zamana jahiliyat ki har cheez mere donon pairon ke nichey rakh di gaee (yani un chizon ka eitibaar na raha (aur jahiliyat ke khoon be eitibaar ho gaey aur pehlaa khoon jo main apne khoonon mein se maaf karta hun wo ibne- Rabee ka khoon hai ke wo bani Sad mein doodh peetaa tha aur usko huzail ne qatl kar daala ( gharaz mein iska badla nahi leta (aur isi tarah zamana jahiliyat ka sood sab chhod diya gaya (yani us waqt ka chadhaa sood koi na ley) aur pahley jo sood ham apne yahan ke sood mein se chhodtey hain (aur talab nahi kartey) wo Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bin-abdul-Muttalib ka sood hai is liye ke wo sab chhod diya gaya. aur tum log aurton ke barey mein Allah se daro. isliye ke unko tum ne Allah Taala ki aman se liya hai aur tum ne unke sattar ko Allah Taala ke kalima ( nikah ( se halal kiya hai. aur tumhara haq un par ye hai ke tumharey bichhoney par kisi aisey shakhs ko na aaney dein (yani tumharey ghar mein) jiska aana tumhen na-gawar ho. phir agar wo aisa karein to unko aisa maaro ke unko sakht chot na lagey (yani haddi wghaira na tootey , koi uzu (khaas ang) zaaye na ho. Husane-surat mein farq na aaey ke tumhari kheti ujad jaey) aur unka tum par ye haq hai ke unki roti aur unka kapda dastoor ke muwafiq tumharey zimmey hai. aur main tumharey darmyan aisi cheez chhodey jata hun ke agar tum usey mazbut pakdey raho to kabhi gumrah na hogey (wo hai) Allah Taala ki kitab. aur tum se (qiyamat mein) mere barey mein sawal hoga to phir tum kya kaho gey? un sab ne arz kiya ke ham gawahi detey hain ke beshak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah Taala ka paigham pahunchaya aur risalat ka haq ada kiya aur ummat ki khairkhaahii ki. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni angusht shahadat ( shahadat ki ungli ( aasman ki taraf uthatey they aur logon ki taraf jhukaatey they aur farmatey they ke aey Allah ! gawah rehna , aey Allah ! gawah rehna , aey Allah ! gawah rehna. teen baar ( yahi farmaya aur yoonhii ishara kiya ( phir azan aur takbeer hui to Zohar ki Namaz padhai aur phir iqamat kahi aur Asr padhai aur in donon ke darmyan mein kuchh nahi padha (yani sunnat w nafl wghaira) phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Sawar ho kar mauqif mein aaey. oontni ka pet pattharon ki taraf kar diya aur pagdandii ko apne aagey kar liya aur qible ki taraf munh kiya aur ghurub aaftaab tak wahin thahrey rahe. zardi thodi-thodi jati rahi aur suraj ki tikiyaa doob gaee tab ( sawar huey) saiyedna Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ko peechhey bitha liya aur wapas ( Muzdalfa ki taraf ( lautey aur qaswaa ki mahaar (nakeil) is qadr khinchi hui thi ke uska sar kajaawa ke) agley hissey ( muwarrik se lag gaya tha ( muwarrik wo jagah hai jahan sawar kuchh waqt thak kar apna pair jo latkaa hua hota hai us jagah rakhta hai) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) seedhey hath se ishara kartey they ke aey logo ! ahista-ahista aaraam se chalo aur jab kisi ret ki dheri par aa jatey ( jahan bheed kam patey ( to zara mahaar dheelii kar detey yahan tak ke ontni chadh jati. (aakhir Muzdalfa pahunch gaey aur wahan maghrib aur isha aik azan aur do takbeeron se padhein aur un donon farzon ke beech mein nafl kuchh nahi padhi (yani sunnat wghaira nahi padhi ). phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) letey rahe. ( Subhan-Allah kaisey-kaisey khaadim hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke, ke din raat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke soney, baithney , uthney, jaagney , khaney, peeney par nazar hai. aur har kaam Mubarak ki yaaddaasht aur hifazat hai. Allah Taala un par rehmat karey) yahan tak ke subah hui jab fajr zahir ho gaee to azan aur takbeer ke sath namaze-Fajr padhi phir qaswaa oontni par Sawar huey yahan tak ke mash'ar-al-haram mein aaey aur wahan qible ki taraf munh kiya aur Allah Taala se dua ki aur Allahu-akbar kaha aur ''لا الہ الا اللہ'' kaha aur uski tauheed pukaarii aur wahan thahrey rahe yahan tak ke ba-khoobii roshni ho gaee. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan se tuloo aaftaab se qabl lautey aur saiyedna Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne peechhey bitha liya aur Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) aik naujawaan achchhey baalon wala goraa chitaa khoobsurat jawan tha. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chaley to aurton ka aik aisa giroh chala jata tha ke aik oont par aik aurat sawar thi aur sab chali jati thin aur saiyedna Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) unki taraf dekhney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Fazal ke chehrey par hath rakh diya (aur zaban se kuchh na farmaya, Subhan-Allah ye akhlaq ki baat thi aur buraai se rokney ka kaam kis khoobi se ada kiya) aur Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna munh dusri taraf pher liya. aur dekhney lagey (ye unke kamaal itminan ki wjah thi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke akhlaq par) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir apna hath idhar pher kar unke munh par rakh diya to Fazal dusri taraf munh pher kar phir dekhney lagey yahan tak ke mohsir ki ghatin mein pahunchey tab oontni ko zara tez challaayaa aur beech ki raah li jo jamara kubraa par ja nikalti hai. yahan tak ke us jamara ke paas aaey jo darakht ke paas hai (aur usi ko jamara Aqba kehtey hain) aur saat (7) kankariyaan usko maarein . har kankari par) Allahu-akbar ( kehtey, aisi kankariyaan jo chutkii se maari jati hain aur wadi ke beech mein khadey ho kar maarein (ke Mina , Arafaat aur Muzdalfa dahini taraf aur Makka baain taraf raha). phir nehar ki jagah aaey aur tiresath oont apne hath se nehar (yani qurbaan ( kiye. baqi saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko unhon-ne nehar kiye. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko apni qurbani mein Sharik kiya aur phir har oont se gosht ka aik tukda leney ka hukm farmaya, (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm ke mutabiq lekar ( aik handi mein daala aur pakaya gaya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aur saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) donon ne usmein se gosht khaya aur iska shorba piyaa . phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sawar huey aur Baitullah ki taraf aaey aur tawaafe ifaaza kiya. aur Zohar Makka mein padhi. phir bani abdul-Muttalib ke paas aaey ke wo log zamzam par pani pilaa rahe they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke pani bharo aey abdul-Muttalib ki aulad ! agar mujhey ye khayal na hota ke log bheed karke tumhen pani na bharney dengey to main bhi tumhare Sharik ho kar pani bharta (yani jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhartey to sunnat ho jata to phir saari ummat bharney lagti aur unki siqaayat jati rehti ( phir un logon ne aik dol Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko diya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein se piyaa ."
2951,"Umar-bin-Hafs-bin-Ghiyas ne bayan kiya : mujhey mere walid ( Hafs-bin-Ghiyas ( ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Jafar-bin-Muhammad ne bayan kiya (kaha) : mujhey mere walid ne hadis bayan ki ke main Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur unse Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Haj ke mutaalliq sawal kiya, aagey Hatim-bin-Ismail ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta (is) hadis mein ye izafa kiya : (Islam se qabl ( Arab ko abu sayyaara naam ke shakhs apne be paalaan gadhey par lekar chalta tha. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Mina se aatey huey) Muzdalfa mein mash'are-haram ko uboor (paar) kiya. Quraish ko yaqin tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usi par ruk jaeinge ( mazeed aagey nahi badhiin gey ). aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qiyam gaah yahin hogi, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aagey guzar gaey aur uski taraf rukh na kiya yahan tak ke Arafaat tashrif ley aaey aur wahan padao farmaya."
2952,"Hazrat Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, (kaha) : mujhey mere walid ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hui apni us hadis mein ye bhi bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine yahan qurbani ki hai. ( lekin) pura Mina qurbaan gaah hai, isliye tum apne-apney padao hi par qurbani karo. maine usi jagah waquf (qiyaam) kiya hai) lekin) pura Arfa hi maqame-wuqoof hai aur maine ( Muzdalfa mein) yahan waquf kiya hai (thehra hoon). aur pura Muzdalfa mauqif hai. (is mein kahin bhi padao kiya ja skata hai.)"
2953,"Sufiyan (Sory) ne Jafar-bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne pichhli sanad ke sath Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka tashrif laey to hajre-Aswad ke paas aaey, usey bosa diya, phir ( tawaaf ke liye) apni daain taraf rawaana huey. (teen chakkaron mein) chhotey chhotey qadam uthatey huey tezi se aur) baqi ( char mein aam raftaar se chaley."
2954,"Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne kaha ke Quraish aur wo log jo Quraish ke Deen par they, Muzdalfa mein waquf (qiyaam) kartey they aur apne ko teiswin kehtey they ( abul-Haisam ne kaha hai ke ye naam Quraish ka hai aur unki aulad ka aur kinaana aur jadeela Qais ka isliye ke wo apne Deen mein teiswin rakhtey they yani tashaddud aur sakhti kartey they). aur baqi Arab ke log Arfa mein waquf kartey they. phir jab Islam aaya to Allah Taala ne apne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hukm farmaya ke Arafaat mein aaein aur wahan waquf farmaein. aur wahin se lautiin aur yahi matlab hai us aayat ka ke ''wahin se lauto jahan se sab log laut'tey hain.''"
2955,"abu-Usama ne kaha, hamein Hisham ne apne walid se bayan kiya, kaha : teiswin ( kahlaaney waley qabaayel (ke ilawa Arab (ke tamam qabaayel ( uriyaan (nange) ho kar Baitullah ka tawaaf kartey they. teiswin (se murad ( Quraish aur un (ki bahar biyaahii hui khawaateen (ke yahan janm leney waley hain. aam log barahna hi tawaaf kartey they, siwaey unke jinhein ahal teiswin kapdey de detey (dastoor ye tha ke) mard mardon ko) tawaaf ke liye) libaas detey aur aurtein aurton ko . (isi tarah) teiswin ( dorane Haj ( Muzdalfa se aagey nahi badhtey they aur baqi sab log Arafaat tak pahunchtey they. Hisham ne kaha : mujhey mere walid ( Urwa ( ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne farmaya : ye teiswin hi they jinke mutaalliq Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai : ''phir tum wahin se ( tawaaf ke liye) chalo jahan se (doosrey ( log chalein.'' unhon-ne farmaya : log (hajj mein) Arafaat se laut'tey they aur ahal-e-Hims Muzdalfa se chaltey they. aur kehtey they : ham haram ke siwa kahin aur se nahi chalein gey. jab aayat phir tum wahin se chalo jahan se doosrey log chalein nazil hui to ye Arafaat ki taraf lot aaey."
2956,"Muhammad-bin-Juber-bin-mut'iim ne apne walid Hazrat Juber-bin-mut'iim (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine apna aik oont kho diya, mein Arfa ke din usey talash karne ke liye nikla to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko logon ke sath Arafaat mein khadey dekha, maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! ye ( Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) to ahale-Hims mein se hain, aap ka yahan ( Arafaat mein) kya kaam? (kyonke) Quraish teiswin mein shumaar hotey they (aur aap quresh hi they)."
2957,"saiyedna abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka ki kankreelii zamin mein oont bithaaey huey they (yani wahan manzil ki hui thi) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se puchha ke tum ne kis niyat se ehram baandha hai? maine arz kiya ke jis niyat se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram baandha hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke tum qurbani sath laey ho? maine kaha nahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Baitullah aur Safa Marwa ka tawaaf karke ehram khol dalo. to maine Baitullah ka tawaaf aur Safa Marwa ki saee ki, phir main apni qaum ki aik aurat ke paas aaya (ye unki mehrem (ehraam walaa shakhs) thi) to usne mere sar mein kanghi ki aur mera sar dho diya. phir main Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilafat mein logon ko yahi fatwa dene laga. (yani jo baghair qurbani ke Haj par aaey to wo Umra karne ke baad ehram khol de. phir din aath (8) zul-hijj ko dobara Haj ka ehram baandhey). lekin aik martaba main Haj ke maqam par khada tha ke achcha aik shakhs aaya, usne kaha ke (tu to ehram kholney ka fatwa deta hai) aap jantey hain ke ameerul-momineen saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne qurbani ke mutaalliq nayaa kaam shuru kar diya. (yani umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka kehna tha ke Umra karke ehram ko kholnaa nahi chahiye) to maine kaha aey logo ! ham ne jis ko is masley ka fatwa diya hai usko ruk jana chahiye kyonke ameerul-momineen saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) aaney waley hain lihaza unki pairwi karo. jab saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) aaey to maine kaha, ameerul-momineen aap ne qurbani ke mutaalliq ye kya nayaa masla bataya hai? to saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : agar aap Allah ki kitab Quran par amal karein to Quran kehta hai :                                                                                                                                                                      (وَأَتِمُّوا الْحَجَّ وَالْعُمْرَ‌ةَ لِلَّهِ)                                                                                                                                                                      yani ''hajj aur Umra ko Allah ke liye pura karo'' (yani ehram na kholo) aur agar aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat par amal karein to unka apna tariqa ye tha ke unhon-ne ehram us waqt tak na khola jab tak qurbani na kar li. (aap Umra aur Haj ke darmyan halal nahi huey.)"
2958,Muaaz-bin-Muaaz ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
2959,"Sufiyan Sory ne Qais (bin-Muslim ( se, unhon-ne taariq-bin-shahaab se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : saiyedna abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Makka se bahar wadi ( Batha mein sawaariyaan bithaaey huey ( padao daley huey) they. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se puchha ke tum ne kon sa talbiya pukara hai? ( Haj ka, Umerey ka, ya donon ka ?) maine kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wala talbiya pukara . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke tum qurbani sath laey ho? maine kaha nahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Baitullah aur Safa Marwa ka tawaaf karke ehram khol dalo. to maine Baitullah ka tawaaf aur Safa Marwa ki saee ki, phir main apni qaum ki aik aurat ke paas aaya (ye unki mehrem thi) to usne mere sar mein kanghi ki aur mera sar dho diya. phir main Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilafat mein logon ko yahi fatwa dene laga. (yani jo baghair qurbani ke Haj par aaey to wo Umra karne ke baad ehram khol de, phir yaum aath (8) zul-hijj ko dobara Haj ka ehram baandhey, lekin aik martaba mein Haj ke maqam par khada tha ke achcha aik shakhs aaya, usne kaha ke (tu to ehram kholney ka fatwa deta hai) aap jantey hain ke ameerul-momineen saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne qurbani ke mutaalliq nayaa kaam shuru kar diya. (yani umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka kehna tha ke Umra karke ehram ko kholnaa nahi chahiye ( to maine kaha aey logo ! ham ne jis ko is masley ka fatwa diya hai usko ruk jana chahiye kyonke ameerul-momineen saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) aaney waley hain lihaza unki pairwi karo. jab saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) aaey to maine kaha, ameerul-momineen aap ne qurbani ke mutaalliq ye kya nayaa masla bataya hai? to saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : agar aap Allah ki kitab Quraan par amal karein to Quraan kehta hai :                                                                                                                                                                   (وَأَتِمُّوا الْحَجَّ وَالْعُمْرَ‌ةَ لِلَّهِ)                                                                                                                                                                     '' yani Haj aur Umra ko Allah ke liye pura karo'' (yani ehram na kholo) aur agar aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat par amal karein to unka apna tariqa ye tha ke unhon-ne ehram us waqt tak na khola jab tak qurbani na kar li."
2960,"abu Umais ne hamein Qais-bin-Muslim se khabar di, unhon-ne taariq-bin-shahaab se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey Yaman bheja tha, phir meri Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us saal mulaqat hui jis mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj ada farmaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se malum kiya : abu-Musa ! tum ne kon sa talbiya pukara hai? ( Haj ka, Umerey ka, ya donon ka ? ( maine kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wala talbiya pukara. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke tum qurbani sath laey ho? maine kaha nahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Baitullah aur Safa, Marwa ka tawaaf karke ehram khol dalo. aagey ( abu Umais ne) Shoba aur Sufiyan hi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
2961,"Ibrahim-bin-abi-Musa ne Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo hajje-tamatto ( karne) ka fatwa diya kartey they, aik shakhs ne unse kaha : apne kuchh fatwon mein zara ruk jao, tum nahi jantey ke ab ameerul-momeneen (Raziallahu anhu) ne manaasik ( Haj (ke mutaalliq kya nayaa farman jari kiya hai? baad mein abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ki Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat hui to abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse malum kiya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main janta hun ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye ( hukm saadir ( kiya, aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne (is par amal ( kiya. lekin mujhey ye baat na-gawar malum hui ke log Arafaat ke paas wadi Arfa ke qareeb araak maqam mein) ya peelu ke darakhton ki ot mein) apni aurton ke sath lutf andoz hotey rahen. phir jab wo ( aath (8) zul-hijja tarwiya ke din ki) subah Haj ke liye chalein to (ghusle-janabat karein aur) unke saron se pani tapak raha ho."
2962,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Abdullah-bin-Shaqeeq ne bayan kiya : Usman (Raziallahu anhu) hajje-tamatto se mana farmaya kartey they aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) iska hukm detey they. (eik martaba (Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se is barey mein koi baat kahi . iske baad Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aap achi tarah jantey hain ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hajje-tamatto kiya tha. (hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ji bilkul (kiya tha) lekin us waqt ham khaufzada they."
2963,"Khalid , yani ibne- Haris ne hamein hadis bayan ki, hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath usi ( uper zikr ki gaee hadis) ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
2964,"Amr-bin-Murra ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se riwayat ki, kaha : (eik martaba ( maqame-asfaan par Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ikatthey huey. Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) hajje-tamatto se ya ( Haj ke mahinon mein) Umra karne se mana farmatey they. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse puchha : aap us mamley mein kya karna chahtey hain jiska Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya aur aap (Raziallahu anhu) us se mana farmatey hain? Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : aap apni raey ke bajaey hamein hamari raey par chhod dein. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : (aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm ke khilaf hukm de rahe hain) mein aapko nahi chhod sakta. jab Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye ( israar ( dekha to Haj aur Umra donon ka talbiya pukaarnaa shuru kar diya (taake Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm ke mutabiq tamatto bhi raaij rahe.)"
2965,"Aamash ne Ibrahim Taimi se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Yazeed-bin-Sharik ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya : Haj mein tamatto ( Haj ka ehram baandhna phir Umra karke ehram khol dena ( sirf Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon ke liye khas tha."
2966,"Ayash Aamiri ne Ibrahim Taimi se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Yazeed-bin-Sharik ( se, unhon-ne Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ye rukhsat (choo'th) sirf hamarey hi liye thi, yani Haj mein tamatto ki."
2967,"Zubeda ne Ibrahim Taimi se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : do mut'ey hamarey ilawa kisi ke liye sahi nahi ( huey) yani aurton se ( nikah ( mutaa karna aur Haj mein tamatto ( Haj ka ehram baandh kar aana , phir us se Umra karke Haj se pahley ehram khol denaa, darmyan ke dinon mein beeviyon aur khushbu wghaira se faayda uthaana  aur aakhir mein rawaangii ke waqt Haj ka ehram baandhna .)"
2968,"hamein Quteba ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha) : hamein Jarir ne bayan se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Shasha se riwayat ki, kaha : main Ibrahim Nakhai aur Ibrahim Taimi ke paas aaya aur unse kaha : main chahta hun ke us saal Haj aur Umerey dono ko ikattha ada karun. Ibrahim Nakhai ne ( meri baat sun kar) kaha : tumharey walid ( abu-Shasa ( to kabhi aisa irada bhi na kartey. Quteba ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne bayan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ibrahim Taimi se unhon-ne apne walid ( Yazeed-bin-Sharik ( se riwayat ki ke aik martaba unka guzar Rabza ke maqam par Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se hua, unhon-ne un se, ( Haj mein tamatto (ka zikr kiya. Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : ye tum logon ko chhod kar khas hamarey liye tha."
2969,"Marwan bin Muawiya ne kaha : hamein Sulaiman Taimi ne ghaneem bin Qais se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se hajje-tamatto ke barey mein poocha. unhon-ne kaha ham ne hajje-tamatto kya tha aur ye (Muaawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu)) un dinon saaybanon ( waley gharon ( mein khud ko dhaanpey huey ( muqeem ( they, yani Makka ke gharon mein. (Muaawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki tarah hajje-afrad par israr kartey they. ("
2970,Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Sulaiman Taimi se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur apni riwayat mein kaha : unki murad Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se thi.
2971,Sufiyan aur Shoba donon ne Sulaiman Taimi se isi sanad ke sath un donon ( Marwan aur Yahya ( ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki hai. ( albatta ( Sufiyan ki hadis mein hai : Haj mein tamatto (ke barey mein malum kiya.)
2972,"hamein Ismail bin Ibrahim ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Jurairi ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abul-Ala se, unhon-ne Mutarrif se riwayat ki, (Mutarrif ne) kaha : Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha : main tumhen aaj aik aisi hadis bayan karne laga hun jis se Allah Taala aaj ke baad tumhen nafa dega. jaan lo! Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ghar walon mein se kuchh ko zul-hijja mein Umra karwaya, phir na to koi aisi aayat nazil hui jisne usey (hajj ke mahinon mein Umerey ko) mansukh qarar diya ho, aur na Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se roka, yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni manzil ki taraf tashrif ley gaey. baad mein har shakhs ne jo raaey qaaim karna chahi kar li."
2973,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur Muhammad-bin-Hatim donon ne Wakee se ye hadis bayan ki (kaha : ( hamein Sufiyan ne Jurairi se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, ( albatta ( ibne- Hatim ne apni riwayat mein kaha : baad mein aik aadmi ne apni raey se jo chaha nazariya bana liya, unki murad Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se thi."
2974,"hamein Muaz ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Shoba ne Humaid bin Hilal se, unhon-ne Mutarrif se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha : main tumhen aik hadis bayan karta hun. wo din door nahi jab Allah Taala tumhen us se fayda dega. bila shubah ! Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj aur Umra ko) Haj ke mahinon mein) ikattha kiya , phir aap ne wafat tak us se mana nahi farmaya, aur na iske barey mein Quran hi mein kuchh nazil hua jo usey haram qarar de aur ye bhi) bataya (ke mujhey ( farishton ki taraf se) salam kya jata tha. yahan tak ke) bawaaseer ki bina par) maine apne aapko daghwaya to mujhey (salam kehna) chhod diya gaya, phir maine daghwana chhod diya to (farishton ka salam) dobara shuru ho gaya."
2975,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha) hamein Shoba ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne Humaid bin Hilal se riwayat ki, kaha maine Mutarrif se suna, unhon-ne kaha Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha, aagey Muaz ki hadis ki tarah hai."
2976,"Qatada ne Mutarrif se riwayat ki, kaha : jis marz mein Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat hui, us doran mein unhon-ne mujhey bula bheja aur kaha, main tumhen chand hadisein bayan karna chahta hun. ummeed hai ke Allah Taala mere baad tumhen unse fayda pahunchaeyga , agar main ( shifayab ho kar) zinda raha to un baton ko meri taraf se posheeda rakhna agar faut ho gaya to chaho to bayan kar dena. mujh par) farishton ki taraf se) salam kaha jata tha ( tafseel pichhli hadis mein hai) aur yad rakho ! Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj aur Umerey ko ikattha kar diya, iske baad na to is barey mein Allah ki kitab nazil hui aur na ( aakhir tak) Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya, aik shakhs ne us barey main apni raey se jo chaha kaha."
2977,"hamein Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Mutarrif bin-Abdullah-bin-Shikhkhir se unhon-ne Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya : jaan lo ! Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj aur Umerey ko ikattha kya tha. iske baad na to us mamley mein Allah ki kitab (mein koi baat ( nazil hui aur na Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein un donon se mana farmaya : phir aik shakhs ne iske barey main apni raey se jo chaha kaha,"
2978,"Hammam ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne Mutarrif ke waastey se Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( Haj mein) tamatto kya tha aur uske baad iske mutaalliq Quran nazil na hua (ke ye durust nahi hai iske mutaalliq ( aik shakhs ne apni raey se jo chaha keh diya."
2979,"Muhammad-bin waase ne Mutarrif bin-Abdullah-bin Shikhkhir se, unhon-ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se yahi hadis bayan ki, ( Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Haj mein) tamatto ( Haj w Umerey ko aik sath ada ( kya aur ham ne bhi aap ke sath ( Haj mein) tamatto kya tha. ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Quran ki sura mein Haj w Umra ikattha ada kya, jo qurbaniyan sath na laey they unhon-ne unhi dinon mein alag alag ehram baandh kar donon ko ada kya ("
2980,"Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha hamein Imran bin Muslim ne abu -Rijaa se riwayat ki, ke Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mutaa yani Haj mein tamatto ki aayat Quran Majeed mein nazil hui aur Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi hamein iska hukm diya, uskey baad na to koi aayat nazil hui jisne Haj mein tamatto ki aayat ko mansookh kya ho aur na Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya yahan tak ke aap faut ho gaey baad mein aik shakhs ne apni raey se jo chaha kaha."
2981,Yahya-bin-Saeed ne hamein Imran qaseer se hadis sunai ( unhon-ne kaha : ( hamein abu -Rijaa ne Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se isi sanad (mazkura (uper zikr) bir-Riwayat ( ki tarah hadis bayan ki. albatta usmein ye kaha ke ham ne ye ( Haj mein tamatto ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kya ( Yahya-bin-Saeed ne) ye nahi kaha : aap ne hamein iska hukm diya.
2982,"Salim bin-Abdullah se riwayat hai ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj tak Umerey se tamatto farmaya aur hadiyae-qurbani ka ehtimaam kya aap zul-Hulaifa se qurbani ke janwar apne sath chala kar laey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shuruat ki to (pahley) Umerey ka talbiya pukara phir Haj ka talbiya pukara aur logon ne bhi aap ke sath Haj tak Umerey se tamatto kya. logon mein kuchh aisey they unhon-ne hadiyae-qurbani ka ehtimaam kya aur qurbani ke janwar chala kar sath laey they aur kuchh aisey they jo qurbaniyan lekar nahi chaley they. jab aap Makka tashrif le aaey to aap ne logon se farmaya : tum mein se jo qurbani le chala wo un chizon se jinhein us ne ( ehram baandh kar) haram kya us waqt tak halal nahi hoga jab tak ke Haj poora na kare. aur jo shakhs qurbaani nahi laya wo Baitullah aur Safa Marwa ka tawaaf karey aur baal katarwa kar halal ho jaey (aur aath (8) zul-hijja ko) phir Haj ka ( ehram baandh kar) talbiya pakarey (aur rami ke baad) qurbani kare. aur jisey qurbani muyassar na ho wo teen din Haj ke doran mein aur saat (7) din ghar lot kar rozey rakhey . jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka pahunchey they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ka tawaaf farmaya, sabse pahley hajre-Aswad ka istilaam kya. phir teen chakkaron mein tez chaley aur char chakkar mamool (routine) ki raftar se chal kar lagaey . jab aap ne Baitullah ka tawaaf mukammal kar liya to maqaame-Ibrahim ke paas 2 rakatein ada farmain. phir salam pher aur rukh badal liya. Safa par tashrif laey aur Safa Marwa ke) darmyan ( saat (7) chakkar lagaey. phir jab tak aap ne apna Haj mukammal na kya aap ne aisi kisi cheez ko (apne liye) halal na kya jisey aap ne haram kya tha qurbani ke din aap ne apne qurbani ke oont nehar kiye aur) tawaafe) ifaza farmaya, phir aap ne har wo cheez (apne liye) halal kar li jo (ehram ki wjah se) haram thahrai thi aur logon mein se jinhoney hadiya qurbani ka ehtimaam kya tha aur logon ke sath qurbani ke janwar haank kar ley aaey they. unhon-ne bhi waisaa hi kya jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha."
2983,ibne-Shahab ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein ( Urwa ko) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barey mein aap ke Haj ke sath Umerey ke tamatto ke mutaalliq aur jo aap ke sath they. unke tamatto ke mutaalliq isi tarah khabar di. jis tarah Salim bin-Abdullah ne mujhey Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ke waastey se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khabar di thi.
2984,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney padha , unhon-ne Naafe se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! logon ka mamla kya hai? unhon-ne ( Umerey ke baad) ehram khol diya hai. aur aap ne apne Umerey ( aatey hi tawaaf w saii jo Umerey ke mansak ke barabar hai) ke baad ehram nahi khola . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine apne sar (ke baalon ( ko gond ya khatmi buti se) chupka liya aur apni qurbaniyon ko haar daal diye. isliye main jab tak qurbani na kar loon. ehram nahi khol sakta."
2985,"Khalid-bin Mukhlid ne Malik se, unhon-ne Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya wjah hai ke aap ne ehram nahi khola? (aagey) uper zikr ki gaee hadis ki tarah hai."
2986,"Ubaidullah ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : logon ka kya mamla hai? unhon-ne ehram khol diya hai aur aap ne ( manasik) ada ho janey ke bawajood) abhi tak Umerey ka ehram nahi khola . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine apni qurbani ke oonton ko haar pehnaey aur apne sar (ke baalon) ko gond (jeli) se chipkaya, main jab tak Haj se farigh na ho jaaun. ehram se farigh nahi ho sakta."
2987,Ubaidullah ne Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne ( Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) se kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ( aagey ( Malik ki hadis ki tarah hai) albatta alfaz yun hain) : main jab tak qurbani na kar loon. ehram se farigh nahi ho sakta.
2988,"ibne-Juraij ne Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne hadis bayan farmai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ko Hijjatul-wada ke saal hukm diya tha ke wo (Umra karne ke baad) ehram khol dein. Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine kaha : aapko ehram kholney se kya cheez rukawat hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main apne sar (ke baalon ko) chupka chuka hun aur apni qurbani ko haar bhi pehna chuka hun, lihaza mein jab tak apni qurbani ke oont nehar na kar loon. ehram nahi khol sakta."
2989,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney ( hadis ki) qirat ki, unhon-ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) fitney ke dinon mein Umerey ke liye nikley aur kaha : agar mujhey Baitullah janey se rok diya gaya to ham waisey hi karengey jaisey ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kya tha. wo (Madina se) nikley aur) meeqaat se) Umerey ka talbiya pukara , aur chal padey jab maqame-beda (ki bulandi) par namudar huey to apne sathiyon ki taraf mutwajjeh ho kar farmaya : donon ( Haj w Umra (ka mamla aik hi jaisa hai. main tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine Umerey ke sath Haj ki niyat bhi kar li hai. phir aap nikal padey yahan tak ke Baitullah pahunchey to iske ( gird ( saat (7) chakkar lagaey aur Safa Marwa ke beech bhi saat (7) chakkar poorey kiye, un par koi izafa nahi kya. unki raey thi ke yahi (eik tawaaf aur aik saee ( unki taraf se kafi hai aur) baad azan ( unhon-ne ( Haj Qiran honey ki bina par) qurbani ki."
2990,Ubaidullah se riwayat hai kaha : mujhey Naafe ne hadis bayan ki ke jis saal Hajjaj-bin-Yosuf ne Hazrat ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se ladai karne ke liye Makka mein padao kya to Abdullah bin-Abdullah aur Salim bin-Abdullah ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se guftgu ki ke agar aap is saal Haj na farmaein to koi harj nahi hamein andesha hai ke logon (Hajjaj-bin-Yosuf aur Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ki faujon) ke darmyan jang hogi aur aap ke aur Baitullah ke darmyan rukawat ho jaeygi (aap Baitullah tak pahunch nahi paeingey ( unhon-ne farmaya : agar mere aur Baitullah ke darmyan koi rukawat aa gaee to main wahi karunga jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha (is mauqe par) main bhi aap ke sath (Sharike-safar) tha jab Quraish Makka aap ke aur Baitullah ke darmyan rukawat ho gaey they main tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine Umerey ki niyat kar li hai. ( phir Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) nikley jab zul-Hulaifa pahunchey to Umerey ka talbiya pukara phir farmaya : agar mera rasta khali raha to main apna Umra mukammal karunga aur agar mere aur Baitullah ke darmyan koi rukawat paida ho gaee to main wahi karunga jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha jab main bhi aap ke sath tha. phir ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) ye aayat tilawat farmai .) لَّقَدْ كَانَ لَكُمْ فِي رَ‌سُولِ اللَّهِ أُسْوَةٌ حَسَنَةٌ ( yaqinan tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ke amal ( mein behtreen namuna hai. phir (Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) chal padey jab maqam beda ki bulandi par pahunchey to farmaya : un donon ( Haj w Umra (ka hukm aik jaisa hai. agar mere aur Umerey ke darmyan koi rukawat aa gaee to (wahi rukawat) mere aur mere Haj ke darmyan haail hogi. main tumhen gawah thehrata hun ke maine apne Umerey ke sath Haj bhi lazim thehra liya hai aap chaltey rahe yahan tak ke maqam qudaid par aap ne qurbani ke oont kharidey phir aap ne un donon ( Haj aur Umerey (ke liye Baitullah aur ehram baandha tha usey na khola yahan tak ke qurbani ke din Haj (mukammal) karke donon ke ehram se farigh huey.
2991,"ibne-Numair ne hamein hadis sunai, (kaha :) hamein mere walid ( Abdullah ( ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Naafe se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne us mauqe par jab Hajjaj-bin-Yosuf , ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke muqabley mein utra , Haj ka irada kya. ( ibne-Numair ne poori ( hadis (Yahya qattan ke) us qissey ki tarah bayan ki. albatta hadis ke aakhir mein kaha ke) ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ye kaha kartey they : jo shakhs Haj w Umra ikattha (hajje-qiran ki sura mein) ada karey to usey aik hi tawaaf kafi hai. aur wo us waqt tak ehram se farigh nahi hoga jab tak donon se farigh na ho jaey."
2992,"Muhammad-bin Rumeh aur Quteba ne Leis se, unhon-ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke jis saal Hajjaj-bin-Yosuf , ibne-Zubair ke muqabley mein utra us saal Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Haj ka irada farmaya, unse kaha gaya : logon ke beech to ladai honey wali hai, hamein khadsha hai ke wo aapko ( Baitullah se pahley hi ( rok dengey. unhon-ne farmaya : bila shubah tumharey liye Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaat mein behtreen namoona hai. main is tarah karunga jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha. main tumhen gawah thahrata hun ke maine (khud par) Umra wajib kar liya hai. phir rawana huey, jab maqam beda ki bulandi par pahunchey to farmaya : ( kisi rukawat ke baais Baitullah tak na pahunch sakney ke lihaaz se) Haj w Umerey ka mamla yaksan hi hai. ( logo ! ( tum gawah raho. ibne- Rumeh ki riwayat hai : main tumhen gawah banata hun. maine apne Umerey ke sath Haj bhi khud par wajib kar liya hai. aur wo qurbani jo maqam qudaid se kharidi thi usey sath liya aur Haj aur Umra donon ka talbiya pukaartey huey aagey badhey , yahan tak ke Makka aa pahunchey, wahan aap ne Baitullah ka aur Safa Marwa ka tawaaf kya. us se zyada (koi aur tawaaf ( nahi kya, na qurbani ki na baal mundwaaey , na katarwaaey aur na kisi aisi hi cheez ko apne liye halal qarar diya jo ( ehram ki wjah se aap par) haram thi. yahan tak ke jab nehar ka din (das zul-hijja) aaya to aap ne qurbani ki aur sar mundaya. un (Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ki raey yahi thi ke unhon-ne apne tawaaf ke zariey se Haj w Umerey ( donon (ka tawaaf mukammal kar liya hai. aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa hi kya tha (eik tawaaf ke sath saee ki)"
2993,"Ayub ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se yahi qissa riwayat kya hai, albatta unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr sirf hadis ki shuruat mein kya ke jab unse kaha gaya ke wo aapko Baitullah ( tak pahunchne ( se rok dengey , unhon-ne kaha : main isi tarah karunga jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha aur hadis ke aakhir mein ye nahi kaha ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa hi kya tha jaisa ke Leis ne kaha hai."
2994,"Yahya-bin-Ayub aur Abdullah-bin-Aun Hilali ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Ibad bin Ibad mohlabi ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai. Yahya ki riwayat mein hai. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sirf Haj ka talbiya pukara aur Ibne-Aun ki riwayat mein hai ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sirf Haj ka talbiya pukara ."
2995,"Humaid ne Bakr se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Haj w Umerey ka ikattha talbiya pukartey huey suna. Bakr ne kaha : maine (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki) ye baat Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko batai to unhon-ne farmaya ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne akeley Haj hi ka talbiya pukara tha. (Bakr ne kaha :) phir meri mulaqat Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hui to maine unhein ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka qaul sunaya , Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : (is waqt ke lihaaz se) tum hamein bachchey hi samajhtey ho? ( halanke aisa na tha) maine khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna ""aey Allah main Haj aur Umerey ke liye hazir hun."""
2996,"Habib bin Shahid ne Bakr-bin-Abdullah se riwayat ki, (kaha : ( hamein Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ne un donon ko milaya tha, Haj aur Umerey ko . (Bakr ne) kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se iske mutaalliq malum kya to unhon-ne farmaya : ham ne ( sirf ( Haj ka talbiya kaha tha. (Bakr ne kaha : ( phir maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se rujoo kya aur unhein ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat batai . unhon-ne jawab diya : jaisey ham to us waqt bachchey they?"
2997,"Ismail bin abi Khalid ne Wabra se riwayat ki, kaha : main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas betha hua tha ke unke paas aik shakhs aaya, us ne puchha : kya Arafaat pahunchne se pahley mein Baitullah ka tawaaf kar sakta hun? unhon-ne jawab diya, haan ( kar saktey ho ( usne kaha : Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne to kaha hai ke Arfa pahunchne se qabl Baitullah ka tawaaf na karna. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey jawab diya : (suno!) Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab Haj farmaya to aap ne maidane-Arafaat pahunchne se qabl Baitullah ka tawaaf kya tha. (ab socho) ke tum Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka qaul apnaao ye zyada haq hai? ya ye ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ka qaul? agar tum (unke barey mein) sach keh rahe ho."
2998,"Bayan ne Wabra se riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs ne saiyedna ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kya : maine Haj ka ehram bandha hai, to kya main Baitullah ka tawaaf kar lun? unhon-ne farmaya : (haan) tumhen kya rukawat hai? usne kaha : maine ibne-falan (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ko dekha hai ke wo usey na-pasand kartey hain aur aap hamein unse zyada mehbub hain ham ne dekha hai ke duniya ne unhein fitney mein daal diya hai Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham mein se kon ya tum mein se kon . jisey duniya ne fitney mein nahi daala? (tum un par duniya daari ka aetraz na karo, ( phir farmaya : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap ne Haj ka ehram baandha, Baitullah ka tawaaf kya aur Safa Marwa ki saee farmai, ( ab socho ( Allah Taala aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke tareeqey ki pairwi ka zyada haq hai. ya falan ke rastey ka ke uski ittiba (pairvi) ki jaaey? agar tum sach keh rahe ho."
2999,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Amr-bin-Dinar se Hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se us shakhs ke mutaalliq puchha jo Umerey ki gharaz se aaya, us ne Baitullah ka tawaaf kar liya ( lekin abhi ( Safa Marwa ki saee nahi ki, kya wo apni biwi se sohbat kar sakta hai? unhon-ne farmaya : (jab ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey they, to aap ne Baitullah ka saat (7) baar tawaaf kya, maqame-Ibrahim ke peechhey 2 rakatein ada farmain, aur) phir ( Safa Marwa ke darmyan saat (7) baar chakkar lagaey aur) yad rakho ( tumharey liye Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ke tareeqey) mein behtreen namuna hai."
3000,"Hammad-bin-Zaid aur ibne-Juraij donon ne Amr-bin-Dinar ke waastey se Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ibne-Uena ki) guzishta ( hadis ki tarah riwayat bayan ki."
3001,"Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman se riwayat hai ke aik iraaqi shakhs ne unse kaha : meri taraf se Urwa-bin-Zubair se us shakhs ke barey mein sawal kijiye jo Haj ka talbiya pukarta hai, jab wo Baitullah ka tawaaf kar ley to kya ehram se aazad ho jaeyga ya nahi? agar wo tumhen jawab dein ke wo aazad nahi hoga to unse kehna ke aik shakhs hai jo ye kehta hai) Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman ne) kaha : maine Urwa se uski baabat sawal kya to unhoney kaha : jo shakhs Haj ka ehram baandhey, wo Haj kiye baghair ehram se farigh nahi hoga. main (Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman) ne kaha ke aik shakhs hai jo yahi baat kehta hai unhon-ne farmaya : kitni buri baat hai jo usney kahi hai. phir mera takraw (is iraqi) shakhs se hua to usne mujh se (apne sawal ke mutaalliq ( poochha. maine usey bata diya. us ( iraqi) ne kaha : un ( Urwa ( se kaho , bila shubah aik shakhs khabar de raha tha ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa hukm kya tha ( hukm diya tha) Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) aur Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ka kya mamla tha? unhon-ne ( bhi to) aisa kya tha. ( Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman ne) kaha : main Urwa ke paas aaya aur unko ye baat sunai. unhon-ne puchha : ye ( saail ( kon hai? maine kaha : main nahi janta. unhon-ne kaha : usey kya hai? wo khud mere paas aakar mujh se sawal kyon nahi karta ? mera khayal hai, wo koi iraaqi hoga. maine kaha : main nahi janta. ( Urwa ne) kaha : bila shubah us ne jhoot bola hai. mujhey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj kya, Makka aa kar aap ne jo kaam sabse pahley kya, ye tha ke aap ne wuzu farmaya aur phir Baitullah ka tawaaf kya. phir unke baad Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Haj kya, unhon-ne bhi, sabse pahley jo kya, yahi tha ke Baitullah ka tawaaf kya aur uske siwa koi kaam na kya ( na baal katwaaey na ehram khola ( , phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aisa hi kya. phir Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Haj kya. maine unhein dekha, unhon-ne bhi sabse pehla kaam jis se shuruat ki, Baitullah ka tawaaf tha. phir iske ilawa koi kaam na hua. phir Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) (ne bhi aisa hi kya) phir maine apne walid Zubair-bin-Awaam (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Haj kya, unhon-ne bhi sabse pahley jis se shuruat ki Baitullah ka tawaaf tha aur uske ilawa koi na tha, phir maine muhajireen w Ansar (ki jamat) ko bhi aisa hi kartey dekha. iske baad (baal katwana ehram kholna) koi kaam na hua. phir sabse aakhir mein jisey maine ye kartey dekha wo Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) hain. unhon-ne bhi Umerey ke zariey se apne Haj ko faskh (khatm) nahi kya, aur ye ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) logon ke paas maujood hain. ye unhi se kyon nahi poochh letey ? aur na guzrey huey logon (sahaba (Rizwanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( mein se kisi ne (ye kaam ( kya. wo ( sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( jab bhi Baitullah mein qadam rakhtey to tawaaf se pahley aur kisi cheez se shuruaat na kartey they (tawaf karne ke bad) ehram nahi kholtey they. maine apni walida aur khala ko bhi dekha, wo jab bhi Makka aatin tawaf se pahley kisi aur kaam se shuruat na kartin, iska tawaf kartin, phir ehram na kholtin (yahan tak ke Haj pura kar letin) meri walida ne mujhey bataya ke wo, unki behan (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha)), Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) falan-falan log kisi waqt Umra ke liye aaey they, jab unhon-ne hajre-Aswad ka istilaam kar liya (aur Umra mukammal ho gaya) to (iske baad) unhon-ne ehram khola. us shakhs ne iske barey mein jis baat ka zikr kya hai, usmein jhoot bola hai."
3002,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Mansoor bin Abdur-Rehman ne apni walida Safiya-binte-Sheba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Asma binte- abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. unhon-ne kaha : ham ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath) ehram baandhey huey rawana huey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jiske sath qurbani hai wo apne ehram par qaaim rahe aur jiske sath qurbani nahi hai (wo Umerey ke baad) ehram khol de. mere sath qurbani nahi thi maine ehram khol diya aur) mere shauhar ( Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath qurbani thi, unhon-ne nahi khola . Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : (umrey ke baad) maine (doosrey ( kapdey pahan liye aur Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aa baithi , wo kehney lagey : mere paas se uth jao, maine kaha : aapko khadsha hai ke main aap par jhapat padungi."
3003,"Wuhaib ne kaha : hamein Mansoor bin Abdur-Rehman ne apni walida (Safiya-binte-Sheba) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya : ham Haj ka talbiya kehtey huey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Makka pahunchey, phir aagey ibne-Juraij ki tarah hi hadis bayan ki, albatta (apni hadis mein ye izafa ( zikr kya : ( Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : mujh se door raho, mujh se door raho, maine kaha : aapko khadsha hai ke main aap par jhapat padungi."
3004,"hamein Haaroon-bin-Saeed eili aur Ahmed bin Esa ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( mujhey Amr ne ibne- Aswad se khabar di ke Asma (Raziallahu anha) ke Maula Abdullah (bin kaisaan) ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) jab bhi maqam Hajoon se guzartin to wo unhein ye kehtey huey suntey : Allah Taala apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par rahmatein farmaai ! ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath us maqam par padao kya tha. un dinon hamarey safar ke thailey halkey, sawariyan kam aur zaade-raah bhi thoda hota tha. main, meri behan Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) , Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) aur falan-falan shakhs ne Umra kya tha, phir jab ham (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke siwa baqi sab) ne Baitullah (aur Safa Marwa) ka tawaaf kar liya to ham (mein se jinhoney Umra karna tha unhone) ehram khol diye, phir ( tarwiya ke din) zawaal ke baad ham ne ( ehram baandh kar) Haj ka talbiya pukara . Harun ne apni riwayat mein kaha : Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ke aazad karda ghulam ne (kaha ( , unhon-ne unka naam , Abdullah nahi liya."
3005,"Shoba ne Muslim Qurrie se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se hajje-tamatto ke barey mein sawal kya. unhon-ne uski ijazat di, jabke ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) us se mana farmaya kartey they. unhon (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : ye ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida hain. wo hadis bayan karti hain ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski ijazat di, unke paas jao aur unse poochho (Qurrie ne) kaha : ham unki khidmat mein hazir huey wo (us waqt) bhari jism ki na-beena khatun thin, (hamarey sawal ke jawab mein) unhon-ne farmaya : yaqinan Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us (hajje-tamatto) ki ijazat ata farmai thi."
3006,"Abdur-Rehman aur Muhammad-bin-Jafar donon ne isi sanad ke sath Shoba se riwayat ki, unmein se Abdur-Rehman ki hadis mein sirf lafz tamatto hai, unhon-ne hajje-tamatto ke alfaz riwayat nahi kiye. jabke ibne-Jafar ne kaha : Shoba ka qaul hai ke Muslim (Qurrie) ne kaha : main nahi janta ke (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne hajje-tamatto ka zikr kya ya ke aurton se (nikah) mutaa ki baat ki."
3007,"Muaz (bin Muaz) ne hamein Shoba se hadis sunai, (kaha :) Muslim Qurrie (rh) ne hamein hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo farma rahe they : (hijjatul-wadaa ke mauqe par awwalan ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Haj ke sath milaakar ( Umra karne ka talbiya pukara tha, aur aap ke) kuchh ( sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne Haj ka talbiya pukara tha, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wo sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) jo qurbaniyan sath laey they, unhon-ne (jab tak Haj mukammal na kar liya) ehram na khola, baqi sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne (jinke sath qurbaniyan na thin) ehram khol diya. Hazrat Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unhi logon mein se they jo qurbaniyan sath laey they, lihaza unhon-ne ehram na khola ."
3008,"Muhammad , yani ibne- Jafar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath hadis sunai, albatta unhon-ne kaha : jinke paas qurbaniyan na thin unmein Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) aur aik doosrey sahib they, lihaza un donon ne ( Umerey ke baad) ehram khol diya."
3009,"Abdullah-bin-Taaus ne apne walid Taaus-bin-Kaisan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya : ( jahiliyat mein) logon ka khayal tha ke Haj ke mahinon mein Umra karna, zamin mein sabse bura kaam hai. aur wo log mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) ke mahiney ko safar bana liya kartey they, aur kaha kartey they : jab (oonton ka ( peeth ka zakhm mundamil ho jaey, ( musaafiron ka ( nishan ( qadam ( mit jaey aur sifar ( asl mein mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs)) guzar jaey to Umra waley ke liye Umra karna jaaiz hai. (halanke) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sahaba (Rizwanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ke sath char zul-hijja ki subah ko Haj ka talbiya pukartey huey Makka pahunchey, aur un (sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) ko hukm diya ke apne Haj (ki niyat) ko Umerey mein badal dein, ye baat un (sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) par badi nagawar thi, sab ne b-yak zaban kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ye kaisi hillat (ehram ka khaatma) hogi? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mukammal hillat."
3010,"Nasar bin Ali Jahzami ne hamein hadis sunai, (kaha : ( mere walid ne hamein hadis sunai, (kaha : ( Shoba ne hamein hadis sunai, unhon-ne Ayub se, unhon-ne abu Aaliya Bara se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo farma rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj ka talbiya pukara aur char zul-hijja ko tashrif laey aur fajr ki Namaz ada ki, jab namaze-Fajr ada kar chukey to farmaya : jo (apne Haj ko) Umra banana chahey, wo usey Umra bana ley."
3011,"yahi hadis Rooh, abu Shahab aur Yahya-bin-Kasir un tamam ne Shoba se isi sanad se riwayat ki, Rooh aur Yahya bin Kasir donon ne waisey hi kaha jaisa ke Nasar (bin Ali jahazmi ne kaha ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj ka talbiya pukara albatta abu Shahab ki riwayat mein hai : ham tamam Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj ka talbiya pukartey huey nikley. ( aagey ( un sab ki riwayat mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Batha mein fajr ki Namaz ada ki, siwaey jahazmi ke ke unhon-ne ye baat nahi ki."
3012,"hamein Wuhaib ne hadis sunai, (kaha ( hamein Ayub ne hadis sunai unhon-ne abu Aaliya Bara se unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) samet Ashra-e-zul-hijja ki char raatein guzarney ke baad (Makka) tashrif laey. wo ( sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( Haj ka talbiya pukar rahe they ( wahan pahunch kar) aap ne unhein hukm diya ke us (nusuk jiske liye wo talbiya pukar rahe they) ko Umarey mein badal dein."
3013,Mamar ne hamein khabar di unhon-ne Ayub se unhon-ne Abu-Aaliya se unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fajr ki Namaz zi tuwa mein ada farmai aur zul-hijja ki char raatein guzri thin ke tashrif laey aur apne sahaba kiram ko hukm farmaya ke jiske paas qurbani hai unke ilawa baqi sab log apne (hajj ke) ehram ko Umerey mein badal dein.
3014,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne aur Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ne apne walid ke waastey se hadis bayan ki. lafz Ubaidullah ke hain. kaha Shoba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne hukm se, unhon-ne Mujahid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye Umra ( ada hua) hai jis se ham ne fayda utha liya hai) ab ( jiske paas qurbani ka janwar na ho wo mukammal taur par halal ho jaey. ( ehram khol de) yaqinan ( ab ( qiyamat ke din tak ke liye Umra Haj mein dakhil ho gaya hai) donon aik sath ada kiye ja saktey hain)"
3015,"abu Hamza Zubai ne kaha : maine hajje-tamatto (ka irada) kya to (bahut se) logon ne mujhey us se roka, main (isi udhed-bun mein) Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur is mamley mein sawal kiya to unhon-ne mujhey is (hajje-tamatto) ka hukm diya. kaha phir main apne ghar lota aur aa kar so gaya, neend mein khuwab ke doran mere paas aik shakhs aaya aur kaha ( tumhara ( Umra qabool aur) tumhara ( Haj mabroor (har aib se paak ( hai. unhon-ne kaha, main ( dobara ( Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur jo dekha tha. keh sunaya. wo (khushi se) keh uthey : (Allahu-akbar! Allahu-akbar!) ye abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat hai (tumhara khuwab usi ki basharat hai.)"
3016,"Shoba ne Qatada se, unhon-ne abu Hassan se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, farmaya : aap ne zul-Hulaifa mein Zohar ki Namaz ada farmai, phir apni ontni mangwaai aur uski kohan ki daain taraf ( halkey se) zakhm ka nishan lagaya aur khoon poonchh diya aur 2 jootey uske galey mein latkaey. phir apni sawari par Sawar huey. (aur chal diye) jab wo aapko lekar beda ke uper pahunchi to aap ne Haj ka talbiya pukara."
3017,"Muaz bin Hisham ne kaha : mujhey mere walid (Hisham bin abi Abdullah sahib Dustwaai) ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath Shoba ki hadis ke ham mana hadis riwayat ki, albatta unhon-ne ye alfaz kahey : Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab zul-Hulaifa aaey ye nahi kaha : unhon-ne wahan ( zul-Hulaifa mein) Zohar ki Namaz ada farmai."
3018,"Shoba ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine abu Hassan Aaraj se suna, unhon-ne kaha banu-Hajeem ke aik shakhs ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ye kya fatwa hai. jisne logon ko uljha rakha hai ya pareshan kar rakha hai? ke jo shakhs Baitullah ka tawaaf karey ( Umra kar ley ( wo ehram se bahar aa jata hai. unhon-ne farmaya : yahi tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat hai chahey tumhari marzi na ho."
3019,"Hammam bin Yahya ne Qatada se, unhonney abu Hassan se hadis bayan ki, kaha Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya ke is mamley (fatwey) ne logon ko tifarqey mein daal diya hai ke jo Baitullah ka tawaf ( Umra ( karey wo ehram se bahar aa jata hai aur ye ke tawaf mustaqil Umra hai, farmaya : ( haan ( yahi tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat hai chahey tumhen na chahtey huey qabool karni padey."
3020,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Ata ne khabar di ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they : (ehram ki haalat mein) jo shakhs bhi Baitullah ka tawaaf karey wo haaji ho ya ghair haaji ( sirf Umra karne wala ( wo tawaaf ke baad ehram se aazad ho jaeyga ibne-Juraij ne kaha : maine Ata se malum kya, Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ye baat kahan se letey hain? (unke paas kya daleel hai? farmaya Allah Taala ke is farman se (daleel letey huey) phir unke halal ( zabah ( honey ki jagah al-baitul-Ateeq ( Baitullah (ke paas hai. ibne-Juraij ne kaha : maine (Ata se) kaha : is aayat ka talluq to wuqoofe-Arafaat ke baad se hai unhon-ne jawab diya : ( magar ( Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they : is aayat ka talluq wuqoofe-Arafaat se qabl aur baad donon se hai. aur unhon-ne ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us hukm se akhaz ki jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par) tawaaf w sae ke baad) ehram khol dene ke barey mein diya tha."
3021,"Hisham bin Hujair ne Taaus se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne zikr kya ke mujhey Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya kya aapko malum hai ke maine Marwa ke paas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baal qainchi se kaatey they? maine kaha : main ye to nahi janta magar (ye janta hun ke) aap ki ye baat aap hi ke khilaf daleel hai."
3022,"Hasan-bin-Muslim ne Taaus se unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di, kaha : maine qainchi se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baal tarashey jabke aap Marwa par) saee se farigh huey) they. ya kaha : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ke baal qainchi se tarashey ja rahe they, aur aap Marwa par they."
3023,"Abdul-Aala bin Abdul-Aala ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha ( hamein Dawud ne abu-Nazara se unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath intihai buland awaz se Haj ka talbiya pukaartey huey nikley. jab ham Makka pahunchey to aap ne hamein hukm diya ke jinke paas qurbani hai unke ilawa ham tamam usey ( Haj ko) Umerey mein badal dein. jab ( tarwiya ( aath (8) zul-hijja ka din aaya to ham ne ehram baandha Mina ki taraf rawaana huey aur Haj ka talbiya pukara."
3024,"Wuhaib bin Khalid ne Dawud se unhon-ne abu-Nazara se unhon-ne Jaabir aur Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, un donon ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Makka pahunchey aur ham bahut buland awaz se Haj ka talbiya pukar rahe they."
3025,abu-Nazara se riwayat hai kaha : main Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein maujood tha ke aik shakhs unke paas aaya aur kaha : Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne donon muton (hajje-tamatto aur aurton se mutaa) ke barey mein aik doosrey se ikhtilaf kya hai. Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein ye donon mutey kiye phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein un donon se rok diya to 2 baara ham ne donon nahi kiye.
3026,"(Abdur-Rehman (bin Mehdi ne hamein hadis sunai (kaha ( mujhey Saleem bin Hayyan ne Marwan Asghar se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) (hijjatul-wadaa ke mauqe par) Yaman se Makka pahunchey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha : tum ne kya talbiya pukara? unhon-ne jawab diya : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke talbiye ke mutabiq talbiya pukara . aap ne farmaya : agar mere paas qurbani na hoti to main zaroor ehlal (ehram se faraghat) iktiyar kar leta."
3027,"Abdus-Samad aur bahz donon ne kaha : hamein Saleem bin Hayyan ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta Behaz ki riwayat mein halal ho jata ( ehram khol deta (ke alfaz hain."
3028,"Hushaim ne Yahya bin abi Ishaq , Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb aur Humaid se khabar di ke un sab ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna unhon-ne farmaya : maine Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko) Haj w Umra ( donon ka talbiya pukaartey huey suna ye kehtey huey 'aey Allah! main Haj w Umra ke liye hazir hun, main Haj w Umra ke liye hazir hun."""
3029,"Ismail bin Ibrahim ne Yahya bin abi Ishaq aur Humaid Taweel se khabar di Yahya ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna wo farma rahe they : aey Allah ! main Haj w Umra ki niyat se terey dar par hazir hun. Humaid ne kaha : Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye kehtey huey suna : aey Allah! main Haj w Umra (ki niyat (ke sath hazir hun."
3030,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha ( mujhey Zohri ne Hanzala Aslami ke waastey se hadis bayan ki kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kar rahe they (ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya is zaate-aqdas ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai. ibne-Maryam (Alaihissalam) ( zamin par dobara aaney ke baad) fajje-Roha (ke maqam) se Haj ka ya Umerey ka ya donon ka naam letey huey talbiya pukarengey."
3031,"Leis ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki, (is mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jaan hai !"
3032,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di unhon-ne Hanzala bin Ali Aslami se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! ( aagey Sufiyan aur Lais-bin-Sad ( donon ki hadis ki tarah hai."
3033,"Haddab bin Khalid ne hamein hadis sunai (kaha : ( hamein Hammam ne hadis bayan ki, ( unhon-ne kaha : ( hamein Qatada ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( kal ( char Umerey kiye, aur apne Haj waley Umerey ke siwa tamam Umerey zul-qada hi mein kiye. aik Umra Hudaibiya se ya Hudaibiya ke zamaney ka zul-qada mein (jo amalan na ho saka lekin hukman ho gaya) aur doosra Umra ( uski adaaeygi ke liye) agley saal zul-qada mein ada farmaya (teesra) Umra Jaarana maqam se ( aa kar) kya jahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hunain ke amwaale-ghaneemat taqseem farmaey. (ye bhi) zul-qada mein kya aur (chotha ( Umra aap ne apne Haj ke sath zul-hijja mein) ada kya."
3034,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( mujhey Abdus-Samad ne hadis sunai (kaha) hamein Hammam ne hadis bayan ki (kaha : ( hamein Qatada ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kitney Haj kiye ? unhon-ne kaha : Haj aik hi kya ( albatta ( Umerey char kiye, phir aagey Haddab ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
3035,"Abu-Ishaq se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath mil kar kitni jangein ladin? kaha : satrah .) Abu-Ishaq ne) kaha : mujhey Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( kal ( unnees ghazwey kiye. aap ne hijrat ke baad aik hi Haj Hijjatul-wada ada kya. Abu-Ishaq ne kaha : aap ne Makka main ( rahtey huey) aur Haj ( bhi) kiye."
3036,"Ata ne khabar di kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di kaha : main aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujrey ke sath tek lagaey baithey they aur unki ( daanton par) miswak ragadney ki awaz sun rahe they. Urwa ne kaha : maine puchha : abu Abdur-Rehman ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki kunniyat ! ( kya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Rajab mein bhi Umra kya tha? unhon-ne kaha : haan! maine (wahin baithey-baithey) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko pukara. meri maan! kya aap abu Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat nahi sun rahin wo kya keh rahe hain? unhon-ne kaha (bataao) wo kya kehtey hain? maine kaha wo kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rajab main ( bhi) Umra kya tha. unhon-ne jawab diya : Allah Taala abu Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ko maaf farmaai mujhey apni zindagi ki qism ! aap ne rajab mein koi Umra nahi kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi Umra nahi kya magar ye ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) bhi aap ke sath hotey they. ( Urwa ne) kaha : ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki guftgu ( sun rahe they unhon-ne haan ya naa kuchh nahi kaha, khamosh rahe."
3037,"Mujahid se riwayat hai, kaha : main aur Urwa-bin-Zubair masjid mein dakhil huey, dekha to Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) masjid mein Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujrey (ki diwar ( se tek lagaey baithey they aur log masjid mein chasht ki Namaz padhney mein masroof they. ham ne unse logon ki (is ( Namaz ke barey mein sawal kya, unhon-ne farmaya ke bidat hai. Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse puchha : abu Abdur-Rehman ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( kal ( kitney Umerey kiye? unhon-ne jawab diya : char Umerey aur unmein se aik rajab ke mahiney mein kya. (unki ye baat sun kar) ham ne unhein jhutlana aur unka radd karna munasib na samjha, (usi doran mein) ham ne hujrey mein Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke miswak karne ki awaz suni. Urwa ne kaha : ummul-momeneen! abu Abdur-Rehman kya keh rahe hain aap nahi sun rahin? unhon-ne kaha wo kya kehtey hain? ( Urwa ne) kaha : wo kehtey hain Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne char Umerey kiye aur unmein se aik Umra rajab mein kya hai unhon-ne farmaya : Allah Taala abu Abdur-Rehman par raham farmaai ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jitney bhi Umerey kiye ye ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) unke sath they (ye bhool gaey hain) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rajab mein kabhi Umra nahi kya."
3038,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Ata ne khabar di, kaha : maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo hamein hadis bayan kar rahe they. kaha Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Ansariya aurat se farmaya, Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne uska naam bataya tha lekin main bhool gaya hun. tumhen hamarey sath Haj karne se kis baat ne rok diya ? us ne jawab diya : hamarey paas pani dhoney waley 2 hi oont they. aik par uske betey ka walid ( shauhar (aur beta Haj par chaley gaey hain aur aik oont hamarey liye chhod gaey ham is par pani dhotey hain. aap ne farmaya : jab Ramazan aaey to tum Umra kar lena kyonke us ( Ramazan ( mein Umra karna Haj ke barabar hai."
3039,"Habib muallim ne hamein hadis sunai, unhon-ne Ata se unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Ansari aurat se jisey Umme- Sanan kaha jata tha kaha : tumhen kis baat ne roka ke tum hamarey sath Haj kartin ? usne kaha : abu fulaan. iske khawind ke paas pani dhoney waley 2 oont they, aik par usne aur uske betey ne Haj kya aur doosrey par hamara ghulam pani dhota tha. aap ne farmaya : Ramzanul-Mubarak mein Umra Haj ya mere sath Haj (ki kami ( ko pura kar deta hai."
3040,Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis sunai (kaha : ( hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Madina se) shajra ke rastey se nikaltey aur maris ke rastey se dakhil hotey they. aur jab Makka mein dakhil hotey to saniya uliya se dakhil hotey aur saniya sufla se bahar nikaltey they.
3041,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed Qattan ne Ubaidullah se usi uper zikr ki gaee sanad se riwayat ki, aur Zuhair ki riwayat mein hai : wo oopri ( ghaati ( jo Batha ke qareeb hai."
3042,Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa-bin-Zubair se) unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka aaey to uski oopri taraf se usmein dakhil huey aur nichli taraf se aap (Makka se) bahar nikley.
3043,abu-Usama ne Hisham se mazkura (uper zikr) sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka waley saal kada se Makka ki opri taraf se Makka mein dakhil huey they. Hisham ne kaha : mere walid donon (oopri aur neechey) jaanibon se Makka mein dakhil hotey they lekin aksar oqaat wo kada hi se dakhil hotey .
3044,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur Ubaidullah bin Saeed ne mujhey hadis sunai. donon ne kaha : hamein Yahya al-Qattan ne hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Ubaidullah se riwayat ki, (kaha) mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zi tuwa maqam par raat guzari yahan tak ke subah kar li. phir Makka mein dakhil huey. ( Naafe ne) kaha : Hazrat Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi) aisa hi kya kartey they. ibne-Saeed ki riwayat mein hai yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne subah ki Namaz ada kar li. Yahya ne kaha : ya (Ubaidullah ne) kaha tha : yahan tak ke subah kar li."
3045,"Hammad ne Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab bhi Makka aatey to zi tuwa (ke maqam) hi mein raat guzaarey yahan tak ke subah ho jati ghusl farmatey phir din ke waqt Makka mein dakhil hotey. wo Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se zikr kartey they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa hi kya tha."
3046,Anas yani ibne- ayaaz ne Musa-bin-Aqba se unhon-ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Makka tashrif latey to pahley zi tuwa mein padao farmatey. wahan raat Basar kartey yahan tak ke subah ki Namaz ada kartey ( phir Makka mein dakhil hotey (aur Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Namaz padhney ki jagah chhotey mazbut teeley par thi us masjid mein nahi jo wahan banai gaee hai. balke us se nichey mazbut teeley par.
3047,Musa-bin-Aqba se riwayat hai unhon-ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke Abdullah (bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne unhein bataya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ke rukh par is pahaad ki donon ghatiyon ko samney rakha jo aap ke aur lambey pahaad ke darmyan tha aap us masjid ko jo wahan bana di gaee hai teeley ke kinarey wali masjid ke baain hath rakhtey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz padhney ki jagah us masjid se nichey kaley teeley par thi teeley se taqriban das hath ( jagah ( chhodtey. phir aap lambey pahaad ki donon ghatiyon ki taraf rukh karke Namaz padhtey wo pahaad jo tumharey aur Kaba ke darmyan padta hai.
3048,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Baitullah ka pahlaa tawaaf kartey to teen chakkar chhotey-chhotey qadmon se kandhey hilaa-hilaa kar tez chaltey huey lagaatey. aur char chakkar chal kar lagaatey aur jab Safa, Marwa ke chakkar lagaatey to wadi ki taraai mein daudtey aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aisa hi kiya kartey they."
3049,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aaney ( qudoom (ke baad sabse pahley Haj aur Umerey ka jo tawaaf kartey, usmein aap Baitullah ke teen chakkaron mein tez raftaari se chaltey phir, ( baqi ( char mein (aam raftaar se) chaltey , phir uske baad do rakatein ada kartey aur uske baad Safa, Marwa ke darmyan tawaaf kartey."
3050,Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne khabar di ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aap jab Makka aatey tawaaf farmatey iske saat (7) chakkaron mein se pahley teen mein chhotey qadam uthatey huey tez chaltey.
3051,"hamein ibne-Mubarak ne hadis bayan ki, hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se khabar di (kaha) : unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hajre-Aswad se hajre-Aswad tak teen chakkaron mein ramal kiya, aur) baqi ( char mein chaley."
3052,"Suleem-bin-akhzar ne Ubaidullah-bin-Umar se uper zikr ki gaee sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne hajre-Aswad se hajre-Aswad tak ramal kiya, aur bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa hi kiya tha."
3053,"Abdullaah-bin-Muslima-bin-qa'anab ne kaha : hamein hadis bayan ki jabke Yahya ne kaha aur alfaz unhi ke hain : maine Malik ke samney qirat ki (ke ( Jafar-bin-Muhammad ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aap ne hajre-Aswad se dobara wahan tak pahunchne tak , teen chakkaron mein ramal kiya."
3054,"Abdullah-bin-Wahab ne kaha : mujhey Malik aur ibne Juraij ne khabar di, unhon-ne Jafar-bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Muhammad Baaqar ( se, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen chakkaron mein hajre-Aswad se hajre-Aswad tak ramal kiya."
3055,"abdul-Wahid-bin-Ziyad ne hamein hadis sunai, (kaha : ( hamein Jurairi ne abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aap ki kya raey hai Baitullah ka tawaaf kartey huey teen chakkaron mein ramal aur char chakkaron mein chalnaa , kya ye sunnat hai? kyonke aap ki qaum ye samajhtii hai ke ye sunnat hai. kaha : ( unhon-ne ( farmaya : unhon-ne sahi bhi kaha aur ghalat bhii. maine kaha : aap ke is jumley ka ke unhon-ne durust bhi kaha aur ghalat bhi, kya matlab hai? unhon-ne farmaya : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka tashrif laey to mushrikon ne kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur unke sathi ( Madiney ki na-muwaafiq aab aur hua, bukhar aur) kamzori ke baais Baitullah ka tawaaf nahi kar saktey. kuffaar aap se hasad kartey they. (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : (unki baat sun kar) aap ne unhein ( sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ko) hukm diya ke teen chakkaron mein ramal karo aur char chakkaron main ( aam raftaar se) chalo. ( abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine un (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) se kaha : mujhey sawar hokar Safa, Marwa ki saee karne ke mutaalliq bhi bataiye , kya wo sunnat hai? kyonke aap ki qaum ke log samajhtey hain ke wo sunnat hai. unhon-ne farmaya : unhon-ne sahi bhi kaha aur ghalat bhi, maine kaha : is baat ka kya matlab hai ke unhon-ne sahi bhi kaha aur ghalat bhi ? unhon-ne farmaya : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par logon ka jamghataa ho gaya, wo sab ( aapko dekhney ke khahish mand they aur aik doosrey se) keh rahe they, ye hain Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam). ye hain Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) yahan tak ke naujawaan auratein bhi gharon se niklin. (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney se ( hataaney ke liye) logon ko maara nahi jata tha. jab aap (ke rastey ( par logon ka thattha lag gaya to aap Sawar ho gaey. ( kuchh hissey mein) chalnaa aur) kuchh mein) saee karna ( tez chalnaa hi ( afzal hai. (kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) asl mein yahi karna chahtey they. ("
3056,"Yazeed (bin Zaree tameemi) ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha ( hamein Jurairi ne isi sanad se khabar di, albatta us ne ye kaha ke ahale-Makka haasid log they, ye nahi kaha ke wo aap se hasad kartey they."
3057,"ibne-abi Husain ne abu Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aap ki qaum ka khayal hai ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah (ke tawaaf mein) aur Safa Marwa ke darmyan mein ramal kya tha, aur ye sunnat hai. unhon-ne farmaya : unhon-ne sahi bhi kaha aur ghalat bhi."
3058,"abdul-Malik-bin-Saeed-bin-Abjar ne abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : mera khayal hai ke maine (hijjatul-wadaa ke mauqe par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha tha. (unhon-ne) kaha : unki sifat (tumhen kis tarah nazar aai) bayan karo. maine kaha : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Marwa ke paas ontni par) sawar ( dekha tha, aur aap (ko dekhney ke liye) logon ka bahut hujoom tha. Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ( haan ( wahi Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) they. logon ko aap se ( door bataaney ke liye) dhakkey diye jatey they na unhein daanta jata tha."
3059,"Saeed-bin-Jubair ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) (Umra qaza ke liye) Makka aaey to unhein yasrib (Madina (ke bukhar ne kamzor kar diya tha. mushrekeen ne kaha : kal tumharey yahan aisey log aa rahe hain jinhein bukhar ne kamzor kar diya hai. aur unhein us se badi takleef pahunchi hai. aur wo log Hateem ke sath ( lag kar) baith gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un (apne sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ko hukm diya ke Baitullah ke teen chakkaron mein chhotey qadmon ki tez , mazbut chaal chalein , aur donon ( Yamani ( konon ke darmyan aam chaal chalein taake mushrikon ko unki mazbootii nazar aa jaey. ( musalmanon ki mazbut chaal dekh kar) mushrikon ne kaha : yahi log hain jinke barey main tumhara khayal tha ke unhein bukhar ne kamzor kar diya hai. ye to falan-falan se bhi zyada mazbut hain Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : unhein poorey chakkaron mein ramal na karne ka hukm deney se, aapko mahz us shafqat ne rokaa jo aap un par farmatey they."
3060,"Ata ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safa Marwa ki saee aur Baitullah ke tawaaf mein ramal sirf mushrekeen ko apni (qaum ki) taqat aur quwwat dikhaaney ke liye kya tha."
3061,"Leis ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Salim bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko 2 yamaani konon ke ilawa Baitullah (ke kisi hissey) ko chhootey nahi dekha."
3062,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Salim se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rukn Aswad ( hajre-Aswad waley koney (aur uske sath waley koney ke ilawa, jo ke banu-jamah ke gharon ki taraf hai, Baitullah ke kisi aur koney ko nahi chhotey they."
3063,"Khalid-bin Haris ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki. unhon-ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hajre-Aswad aur rukne-yamani ke ilawa kisi aur koney ka istilaam nahi kartey they."
3064,"hamein Yahya ne Ubaidullah se riwayat bayan ki, (kaha :) mujhey Naafe ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, farmaya : maine mushkil ho ya aasani, us waqt se un donon ruknon, rukne-yamaani aur hajre-Aswad ka istilaam nahi chhoda, jab se maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko un donon ka istilaam kartey (hath ya honton se chhotey) huey dekha."
3065,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se riwayat ki kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke wo hajre-Aswad ko apne hathon se chhotey phir apne hath ko choom letey. unhon-ne kaha : maine jab se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aisa kartey dekha, us waqt se usey tark nahi kya."
3066,"abu-Tufail bakri (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo farma rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nahi dekha ke aap 2 yamaani kinaron (rukne-yamaani aur hajre-Aswad) ke ilawa kisi aur kinarey ko chhotey hon."
3067,"mujhey Hurmala bin Yahya ne hadis sunai, (kaha : ( hamein ibne- Wahab ne khabar di, (kaha : ( mujhey Yunus aur Amr ne khabar di, isi tarah mujhey Haaroon-bin-Saeed eili ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : ibne- Wahab ne Amr se khabar di, unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Salim se riwayat ki ke unke walid ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne unhein hadis bayan ki, kaha : (eik martaba (Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne hajre-Aswad ko bosa diya aur farmaya : haan , Allah ki qism ! main achi tarah janta hun ke to aik patthar hai, agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko na dekha hota ke wo tumhen bosa detey they, to main tumhen (kabhi) bosa na deta. Harun ne apni riwayat main ( kuchh ( izafa kya, Amr ne kaha : mujhey Zaid-bin-Aslam ne apne walid Aslam se usi ki tarah riwayat ki thi."
3068,Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne hajre-Aswad ko bosa diya aur kaha : main tujhey bosa deta hun aur main ye bhi janta hun ke to ek patthar hai lekin maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha tha wo tujhey bosa detey they. (is liye mein bhi bosa deta hun)
3069,"hamein Khalaf bin Hisham, muqaddami, abu-Kaamil, aur Quteba bin Saeed sab ne Hammad se hadis bayan ki, Khalaf ne kaha : hamein Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Aasim ahwal se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Sarjis se riwayat ki, kaha : maine sar ke agley hissey se udey huey baalon waale, yani umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, wo hajre-Aswad ko bosa detey they aur kehtey they : Allah ki qism ! main tujhey bosa de raha hun, aur be-shak main janta hun ke to aik patthar hai, to nuqsan pahuncha sakta hai na nafa , agar aisa na hota ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tujhey bosa detey dekha tha, to main tujhey bosa na deta. muqaddami aur abu-Kamil ki riwayat main ( udey huey baalon waley ki bajaey) aagey se chhoti si ganj waley ko dekha ke alfaz hain."
3070,"Aabis bin Rabee se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko hajre-Aswad ko bosa detey huey dekha, wo farma rahe they bila shubah maine tujhey bosa diya hai aur main janta hun ke to ek patthar hi hai. agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tujhey bosa detey na dekha hota to tumhen kabhi bosa na deta."
3071,"Suwed bin Ghafala se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhon-ne hajre-Aswad ko bosa diya aur us se chimat gaey, aur Farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha wo tum se bahut qareeb hotey they."
3072,"Abdur-Rehman ne Sufiyan se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, aur kaha : lekin maine abul-Qaasim ko dekha wo tum se bahut qareeb hotey they. unhon-ne wo (hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) us se chimat gaey ke alfaz nahi kahey."
3073,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada mein oont par tawaaf farmaya, aur aap apni aik sirey se mudi hui chhadi se hajre-Aswad ka istilaam farmatey they."
3074,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne hamein hadis sunai, unhon-ne ibne-Juraij se, unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada main apni sawari par Baitullah ka tawaaf farmaya, aap apni chhadi se hajre-Aswad ka istilaam farmatey they. (sawari par tawaaf isliye kya) taake log aapko dekh sakein, aur aap logon ko uper se dekhein, log aap se sawal kar lein kyonke logon ne aap ke ird-gird hujoom kar liya tha."
3075,"Ali-bin-khashram ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Esa-bin-Yonus ne ibne-Juraij se khabar di, neez hamein abd bin Humaid ne hadis bayan ki (kaha :) hamein Muhammad, yani ibne-Bakr ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : ibne-Juraij ne abu-Zubair se khabar di ke unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Baitullah aur Safa Marwa ka tawaaf apni sawari par kya, taake log aapko dekh sakein aur aap uper se logon ko dekh sakein aur log aap se sawal kar sakein kyonke logon ne (har taraf se azdahaam karke) aapko chipa liya tha. ibne-khashram ne taake wo aap se sawalat poochh saken (ke alfaz) riwayat nahi kiye."
3076,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada mein apne oont par Kaba ke ird-gird tawaaf farmaya, aap (apni mudey huey sirey wali chhadi se) hajre-Aswad ka istilaam farmatey they, isliye ke aapko ye baat na-pasand thi ke aap se logon ko mar kar hataya jaey."
3077,"abu Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap Baitullah ka tawaaf farma rahe they, aap apni mudey huey sirey wali chhadi se hajre-Aswad ka istilaam kartey they aur us chhadi ko bosa detey they."
3078,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shikwa kya ke main bimar hun to aap ne farmaya : Sawar ho kar logon ke peechhey se tawaaf kar lo. unhon-ne kaha : jab maine tawaaf kya to us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Baitullah ki aik taraf Namaz ada farma rahe they, aur (namaz mein) ( وَالطُّورِ‌۝ وَكِتَابٍ مَّسْطُورٍ‌ ( ki tilawat farma rahe they."
3079,"hamein abu-Muawiya ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se khabar di, unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa-bin-Zubair ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha : mera khayal hai ke agar koi shakhs Safa Marwa ke beech saee na karey to usey koi nuqsan nahi ( iska Haj w Umra durust hoga.) unhon-ne puchha : wo kyon ? maine kaha : kyonke Allah Taala farmata hai : beshak Safa Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein se hain, aakhir tak, (phir koi Haj karey ya Umra to usko gunah nahi ke wo un donon ka tawaaf karey aur jisne shauq se koi neki ki to Allah qadrdaan hai sab janta hai.) unhon-ne jawab diya : jo shakhs Safa Marwa ke beec saee nahi karta, Allah Taala uska Haj aur Umra mukammal nahi farmata . agar baat isi tarah hoti jis tarah tum keh rahe ho to (Allah ka farman) yun hota is shakhs par koi gunah nahi jo in donon ka tawaaf na kare. kya tum jantey ho ke ye aayat kis barey mein (nazil) hui thi? bila shubah jahiliyat mein Ansar un 2 buton ke liye ehram baandhtey they jo samandar ke kinarey par they, jinhein Isaaf aur naayla kaha jata tha, phir wo aatey aur Safa Marwa ki saee kartey, phir sar munda kar (ehram khol detey), jab Islam aaya to logon ne jahiliyat mein jo kuchh kartey they, uski wjah se un donon (Safa Marwa) ka tawaaf karna bura jana, kyonke wo jahiliyat mein unka tawaaf kya kartey they. (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) farmaya : is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farma di : bila shubah Safa Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein se hain. aakhir aayat tak. farmaya : to logon ne ( phir se unka ( tawaaf shuru kar diya."
3080,"abu-Usama ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa ne hadis bayan ki ke mujhey mere walid (Urwa-bin-Zubair ne) khabar di, kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se arz ki, main is baat main apne uper koi gunah nahi samajhta ke main ( Haj aur Umerey ke douraan mein) Safa, Marwa ke darmyan saee na karun. unhon-ne farmaya : kyon ? maine kaha : isliye ke Allah Taala farmata hai : ''bila shubah Safa, Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein se hain.'' (phir jo koi Baitullah ka Haj karey ya Umra is par gunah nahi ke wo un donon ka tawaaf kare.) unhon-ne farmaya agar (Quraan ki aayat ka ( wo mafhoom hota jo tum kehtey ho, to ye hissey is tarah hota is shakhs par koi gunah nahi jo un donon ka tawaaf na kare. asl mein ye aayat Ansar ke kuchh logon ke mutaalliq nazil hui. wo jahiliyat mein jab talbiya pukaartey to manat (but) ka talbiya pukaartey they. aur (us waqt ke aqeedey ke mutabiq) unke liye Safa, Marwa ka tawaaf halal na tha. jab wo log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj par aaey. to aap se apne usi puraaney amal ka zikr kiya is par Allah Taala ne aayat nazil farmai . mujhey apni zindagi ( dene waale) ki qism ! Allah Taala us shakhs ka Haj pura nahi farmata jo Safa, Marwa ka tawaaf nahi karta."
3081,"Sufiyan ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : maine Zohri se suna, wo Urwa-bin-Zubair se hadis bayan kar rahe they, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha : main nahi samajhta ke koi shakhs jisne ( Haj aur Umerey mein) Safa, Marwa ka tawaaf nahi kiya is par koi gunah hoga aur mujhey bhi koi parwah nahi ke main Safa, Marwa ka tawaaf ( karun ya ( na karun. unhon-ne jawab diya : bhaanjey tum ne jo kaha, wo kitna ghalat hai ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye tawaaf kiya aur tamam musalmanon ne bhi kiya. yahi ( Haj aur Umerey ka ( tariqa qarar paya. asl mein jo log manaat ( but (ke liye jo ke mushal-lal mein tha, ehram baandhtey they wo Safa, Marwa ke beech tawaaf nahi kartey they. jab Islam aaya to ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq sawal kiya to izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne ye aayat nazil farmai : ''bila shubah Safa aur Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein se hain.'' to jo shakhs Baitullah ka Haj ya Umra karey to is par koi gunah nahi ke wo un donon ka tawaaf kare. agar wo baat hoti jis tarah tum keh rahe ho to ( aayat ke alfaz ( is tarah hotey : to is par koi gunah nahi jo un donon ka tawaaf na kare. Zohri ne kaha : maine is baat ka zikr (jo Urwa se suni thi) Abu-Bakar-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Haris-bin-Hisham se kiya, unhein ye baat bahut achi lagi , unhon-ne farmaya : bila shubah yahi to ilm hai. maine bhi kai ahale-ilm se suna, wo kehtey they : Arbon mein se jo log Safa, Marwa ke darmyan tawaaf na kartey they wo kehtey they : un do pattharon ke darmyan tawaaf karna to jahiliyat ke maamlaat mein se tha, aur Ansar mein se kuchh aur logon ne kaha : hamein to sirf Baitullah ke tawaaf ka hukm diya gaya hai. Safa, Marwa ke beech (tawaaf (ka to hukm nahi diya gaya. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farma di : ''bila shubah Safa, Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein se hain.''  Abu-Bakar-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne kaha : mujhey lagta hai ye aayat un donon tarah ke logon ke barey mein nazil hui."
3082,"Aqeel ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : aur) aagey ( usi ( Sufiyan ki ibne-Shahab se) riwayat ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur (apni ( hadis mein kaha : jab unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apne us amal ke mutaalliq sawal kiya to kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ham to Safa, Marwa ka tawaaf karne mein harj mehsus kiya kartey they. to Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai : ''bila shubah Safa, Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein se hain'' to jo koi Baitullah ka Haj karey ya Umra to is par koi gunah nahi ke wo un donon ka tawaaf kare. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : un donon ke beech tawaaf ka tariqa to Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne muqarrar farmaya : kisi ko is baat ka haq nahi ke un donon ke darmyan tawaaf ko tark kar de."
3083,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein bataya ke Ansar aur banu- ghassaan Islam laney se qabl manaat ka talbiya pukara kartey they aur is baat mein sakht harj mehsus kartey they ke wo Safa, Marwa ke beech tawaaf karein. ( dar-haqiqat ( ye tariqa unke baap-dada aur ajdaad mein raaij tha ke jo bhi manaat ke liye ehram baandhey wo Safa, Marwa ka tawaaf nahi karega. un logon ne jab ye Islam laey to iske barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se istifsaar (sawal) kiya. is par Allah Taala ne iske barey mein ye aayat nazil farmai : ''bila shubah Safa, Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein se hain'' to jo shakhs Baitullah ka Haj ya Umra karey is par koi harj nahi ke wo un donon ka tawaaf karey aur jo koi shauq se neki karey to Allah qadr daan hai sab jaanney wala hai."
3084,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha : Ansar Safa, Marwa ke darmyan tawaaf karna naa pasand kartey they yahan tak ke (ye aayat ( nazil hui : ''bila shubah Safa, Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein se hain'' to jo koi Baitullah ka Haj ya Umra karey to is par koi gunah nahi ke wo un donon ka tawaaf kare."
3085,"hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki : (kaha : ( mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo farma rahe they : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sahaba ne Safa, Marwa ke aik ( baar ke) tawaaf ( saee (ke siwa koi aur tawaaf nahi kiya."
3086,"hamein Muhammad-bin-Bakr ne khabar di (kaha : ( hamein ibne-Juraij ne isi sanad ke sath iske jaisi hadis bayan ki, aur kaha : siwaey aik ( baar ke) tawaaf (yani ( pahley tawaaf ke."
3087,"Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Kureb ne Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Arafaat se ( waapsii ke waqt) main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( ontni par) sawar hua, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) daain taraf wali us ghaati par pahunchey jo Muzdalfa se zara pahley hai aap ne apna oont bithaya peshab se farigh huey phir ( wapas ( tashrif laey to maine aap (ke hathon ( par wuzu ka pani dala. aap ne halka wuzu kiya phir maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Namaz ? aap ne farmaya : Namaz aagey ( Muzdalfa mein) hai. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sawar huey yahan tak ke Muzdalfa tashrif laey aur Namaz ada ki. phir (agley din) Muzdalfa ki subah Hazrat Fazal (bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ontni par Sawar huey. Kureb ne kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jamara ( Aqba ( pahunchne tak talbiya pukaartey rahe."
3088,Ata ne khabar di (kaha : ( mujhey Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzdalfa se Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne ( sath ontni par) peechhey sawar kiya. ( phir ( kaha : mujhey Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jamarae-Aqba ko kankariyaan maarney tak musalsal talbiya pukaartey rahai.
3089,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Mabad ne ( Abdullah ( Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke (sath ontni par) peechhey sawar they aap ne Arfa ki Sham aur Muzdalfa ki subah logon ke chalney ke waqt unhein talqeen ki : sukoon se ( chalo (aur aap apni ontni ko) tez chalney se) rokey huey they yahan tak ke aap wadi ( mohsir ( mein dakhil huey. padhi. wo Mina hi ka hissa hai. padhi. aap ne farmaya : tum ( do ungliyon ke darmyan rakh kar) maari janey wali kankariyaan zaroor ley lo jin se jamarae-Aqba ki rami ki jaeygi. ( Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jamara Aqba ko kankariyaan maarney tak musalsal talbiya pukaartey rahe.
3090,"ibne-Juraij se riwayat hai : (kaha) mujhey abu-Zubair ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne (apni ( hadis mein ye zikr nahi kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jamara Aqba ko kankariyaan maarney tak musalsal talbiya pukaartey rahe albatta apni hadis mein ye izafa kiya : aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne hath se (is tarah) ishara kar rahe they jaisey insan (apni ungliyon se) kankar phenktaa hai."
3091,"abu-hosh ne Husain se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaseer-bin-mudrik se unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) (bin-Masood ( ne, jab ham Muzdalfa mein they. kaha : maine us hasti se suna jin par sura Baqra nazil ki gaee, wo us maqam par) لبيك اللهم لبيك ( keh rahe they."
3092,"Hushaim ne kaha : hamein Husain ne kaseer-bin-mudrik Ashjai se khabar di, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) (bin-Masood ( ne Muzdalfa se lot'tey waqt talbiya kaha : to kaha gaya : kya ye dehati ( baddoo ( hain? is par Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya log bhool gaey hain ya gumraah ho gaey hain? maine us hasti se suna jin par sura Baqra nazil ki gaee wo us jagah par) لبيك اللهم لبيك ( keh rahe they."
3093,Sufiyan ne hamein Husain se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki.
3094,"Ziyad-bukaaii ne Husain se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaseer-bin-mudrik Ashjai se unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed aur Aswad-bin-Yazeed se riwayat ki, donon ne kaha : ham ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo Muzdalfa mein farma rahe they. maine us hasti se suna, jin par sura Baqra nazil ki gaee. aap usi jagah ( لبيك اللهم لبيك ( keh rahe they. (ye keh kar) unhon ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne talbiya pukara aur ham ne bhi unke sath talbiya pukara."
3095,"ham se Yahya-bin-Saeed ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai Salma se unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Abdullah-bin umr se unhon-ne apne walid ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham subah ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Mina se arafaat gaey to ham mein se koi talbiya pukarney wala tha aur koi takbeer kehney wala."
3096,"Umar-bin-Husain ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai-Salma se unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Arfa ki subah ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they ham mein se koi takbeerey kehney wala tha aur koi ( la ilaa-h illallaah ( kehney wala tha. albatta ham takbeerey keh rahe they. (Abdullah-bin-Ubai Salma ne) kaha : maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! tum par tajjub hai tum ne unse ye kyon na puchha ke aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kiya kartey huey dekha tha? ."
3097,Yahya-bin-Yahya ne hamein hadis sunai kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney qirat ki ke Muhammad-bin-abi-Bakr Saqafi se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se jab wo donon subah ke waqt Mina se Arfa ja rahe they malum kiya : aap us ( Arfa ke) din mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kaisey zikr aur ibadat kar rahe they? unhon-ne kaha : ham mein se tahleel kehney wala ( la-ilaa-h-illallaah ( kehta to is par koi aitraaz  nahi kiya jata tha aur takbeerein kehney wala takbeerein kehta to is par bhi koi nakeer na ki jati thi.
3098,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne kaha : mujhey Muhammad-bin-abi-Bakr ne hadis bayan ki kaha : maine Arfa ki subah Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aap us din mein talbiya pukarney ke barey mein kya kehtey hain? unhon-ne kaha : maine ye safar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sahaba ke sath kiya, to ham mein se kuchh takbeerein kehney waley they aur kuchh ( la-ilaa-h-illallaah ( kehney waley aur ham mein se koi bhi apne sathi (ke amal ( par aib nahi lagata tha."
3099,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney qirat ki ke Musa-bin-Aqba se riwayat hai unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Kureb se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon ( Kureb ( ne un (Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu)) se suna, keh rahe they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Arfa rawaana huey. yahan tak ke jab ghaati ke paas pahunchey to (sawari se) nichey utrey peshab se farigh huey phir wuzu kiya aur zyada takmeel ke sath wuzu nahi kiya. maine aap se kaha : Namaz ? farmaya : Namaz ( padhney ka maqam ( tumharey aagey ( Muzdalfa mein) hai. iske baad aap (phir) Sawar ho gaey jab Muzdalfa aaey to aap ( sawari se) nichey utrey wuzu kiya aur khub achi tarah wuzu kiya phir Namaz ke liye iqamat kahi gaee aap ne maghrib ki Namaz ada ki phir har shakhs ne apne oont ko apne padao ki jagah mein bithaya, phir isha ki iqamat kahi gaee to aap ne wo padhi aur un donon namazon ke darmyan koi (nafl) Namaz nahi padhi."
3100,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Zuber ke Maula Musa-bin-Aqba se isi sanad se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Arfa se waapsii ke baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye un ghatiyon mein se aik ghaati ki taraf chaley gaey ( phir ( iske baad maine ( wuzu ke liye) aap (ke hathon ( par pani dala aur arz kiya, aap Namaz padhengey ? farmaya : Namaz ( padhney ka maqam ( tumharey aagey ( Muzdalfa mein) hai."
3101,"Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne Ibraaheem-bin-Aqba se unhon-ne Kureb Maula Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Arafaat se lo tey jab ghaatii ke paas pahunchey to utrey aur peshab kiya. Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne (ishaaron mein) ye nahi kaha ke aap ne pani bahaya . kaha : aap ne pani mangwaya aur wuzu kiya jo ke halka sa wuzu tha. maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Namaz ? farmaya : Namaz ( padhney ka maqam ( tumharey aagey ( Muzdalfa mein) hai. kaha : phir aap chaley yahan tak ٰ ke Muzdalfa pahunch gaey aur maghrib aur isha ki namazein ( ikatthi ( ada kin."
3102,"abu khaisma Zuhair ne ham se hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Ibrahim-bin-Aqba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Kureb ne khabar di hai ke unhon-ne Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kya : Arfa ki Sham (Syria) jab tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari par aap ke peechhey sawar huey to tum ne kya kya? kaha : ham us ghaati ke paas aaey jahan log maghrib (ki Namaz (ke liye (apni sawaariyan) bithatey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni sawari ko bithaya aur peshab se farigh huey aur unhon-ne (kinaya kartey huey yun) nahi kaha ke aap ne pani bahaya . phir aap ne wuzu ka pani mangwaya aur wuzu kya jo ke halka saa tha. maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)! namaz? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Namaz ( padhney ka maqam ( tumharey aagey ( Muzdalfa mein) hai. iske baad aap sawar huey yahan tak ke ham Muzdalfa aaey to aap ne maghrib ki iqamat kahlwaai. phir sab logon ne (apni sawariyan) apne padao ki jaghon mein bitha dein aur unhon-ne abhi ( paalaan ( nahi kholey they ke aap ne isha ki iqamat kehlwa di, phir unhon-ne ( paalaan ( kholey . maine kaha : jab tum ne subah ki to tum ne kya kya? unhon-ne kaha : Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke peechhey Sawar ho gaey aur main Quraish ke aagey janey waley logon ke sath paidal gaya."
3103,Muhammad-bin Aqba ne Kureb se aur unhon-ne Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us darrey par tashrif laey jahan hukmaraan utartey hain. aap ( sawari se) utrey aur peshab se farigh huey aur unhon-ne pani bahaya ka lafz nahi kaha ( balke yun kaha : ( phir aap ne wuzu ka pani mangwaya aur halka wuzu kya. maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Namaz ? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Namaz ( padhney ka maqam ( tumharey aagey ( Muzdalfa mein) hai.
3104,"Ata Maula bin Sabaa ne Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Arfa se lautey to wo aap ke) sath ontni par) peechhey sawar they, jab aap ghaati par pahunchey, aap ne apni ontni ko bithaya , phir qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye chaley gaey, jab lautey to maine aik bartan se aap (ke hathon ( par pani daala , aap ne wuzu kya, phir aap Muzdalfa aaey to wahan maghrib aur isha ikatthi ada kin."
3105,Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Arfa se lautey aur Usama (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke sath ( ontni par) sawar they. Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap usi haalat mein musalsal chaltey rahe yahan tak ke Muzdalfa pahunch gaey.
3106,"hamein Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Hisham ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kya gaya aur main maujood tha. ya kaha : maine Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Arafaat se ( waapsi par) unhein apne sath peechhey sawar kya tha. maine kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Arfa se lautey to aap kaisey chal rahe they? kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) darmyaney darjey ki tez raftaari se chaltey they, jab kushaada jagah patey to ( sawari ko) tez daudaatey ."
3107,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hamein ye hadis sunai (kaha : ( hamein Abda bin Sulaiman, Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur Humaid ki hadis mein ye izafa kya : Hisham ne kaha : nas ( tez raftaarii mein) ( unuq ( se uper ka darja hai."
3108,"Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se riwayat ki, (kaha : ( mujhey Adi-bin Sabit ne khabar di ke Abdullah-bin Yazeed khutmi (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis bayan ki, abu Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di ke unhon-ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maghrib aur isha ki namazein Muzdalfa mein ada kin."
3109,"Quteba aur ibne- Rumeh ne Lais-bin-Sad se aur unhon-ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se isi sanad ke sath bayan ki, ibne- Rumeh ne apni riwayat mein kaha : Abdullah-bin Yazeed khitmi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai aur wo ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke door hukumat mein Kufa ke governer they."
3110,Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzdalfa mein maghrib aur isha ki namazein ikatthi ada kin.
3111,"Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin umr ne khabar di ke unke walid ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzdalfa mein maghrib aur isha ki namazein jama kin, un donon ke darmyan koi ( nafl ( Namaz na thi. aap ne maghrib ki teen rakatein ada kin aur isha ki 2 rakatein ada kin. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Muzdalfa mein isi tarah Namaz padhtey rahe yahan tak ke Allah Taala se ja miley."
3112,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hakam aur Salma bin Kuheil se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Muzdalfa mein maghrib aur isha ki namazein aik hi iqamat se ada kin, phir unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne isi tarah Namaz ada ki thi, aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isi tarah kya tha."
3113,Wakee ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur kaha : aap ne wo donon namazein aik hi iqamat se ada ki thin.
3114,"( Sufiyan ( Sory ne Salma bin kuheil se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se aur unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzdalfa mein maghrib aur isha ki namazein jama kin, aap ne aik hi iqamat se maghrib ki teen aur isha ki 2 rakatein ada kin."
3115,"Abu-Ishaq se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Saeed-bin-Jubair ne kaha : ham Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath ( Arfa se) rawaana huey yahan tak ke ham Muzdalfa aaey to unhon-ne hamein maghrib aur isha ki Namaz aik iqamat se padhai , phir ( peechhey ki taraf ( rukh modaa aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein is maqam par isi tarah (jama w qasr par amal kartey huey) Namaz padhai thi."
3116,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se khabar di, unhon-ne Umara se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko koi Namaz uske waqt ke baghair ada kartey nahi dekha, siwaey 2 namazon ke , Muzdalfa mein maghrib aur isha ki namazein (jama kin (aur isi din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fajr ki Namaz uske ( mamool (routine) ke) waqt se pahley ada ki."
3117,"Jarir ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath ye hadis bayan ki, aur kaha : ( fajr ki Namaz ( uske ( mamool (routine) ke) waqt se pahley andherey main ( ada ki.)"
3118,"Aflah, yani ibne-Humaid ne Qasim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Muzdalfa ki raat Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat talab ki ke wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, aur logon ka azdahaam honey se pahley pahley ( Mina ( chali jaaein. aur wo tezi se harkat na kar sakney wali khatun thin. Qasim ne kaha : ( ثبطه ( bhari jism wali aurat ko kehtey hain. kaha, (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : (aap ne unhein ijazat de di. wo aap ki rawaangi se pahley hi nikal padin aur hamein aap ne rokey rakha yahan tak ke ham ne ( wahin ( subah ki, aur aap ki rawaangi ke sath hi ham rawaana huin. agar main bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat ley leti , jaisey Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ne ijazat li thi aur ye ke (hamesha) aap ki ijazat se (jald) rawaana hoti to ye mere liye har khush karne wali cheez se zyada pasandida hota."
3119,"Ayub ne Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Qasim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) badi (aur ( bhari jism wali khatun thin, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat chahi ke wo raat hi ko Muzdalfa se rawaana ho jayen, to aap ne unhein ijazat de di. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : kash! jaisey Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ne ijazat li, maine bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat ley li hoti. ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki rihlat ke baad) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (subah ko baqi logon ki tarah) ameer ( Haj (ke sath hi wapas lota karti thin."
3120,"Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Qasim se, aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : meri aarzoo thi ke jaisey Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ne ijazat li thi, maine bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat ley li hoti, mein bhi subah ki Namaz Mina mein ada kya karti aur logon ke Mina aaney se pahley jamara ( Aqba ( ko kankariyaan mar leti. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha gaya : (kya (Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ne ijazat li thi? unhon-ne kaha : haan. wo bhari aur kam harkat kar sakney wali khatun thin. unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat mangi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ijazat de di."
3121,Sufiyan ( Sory ( ne Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham-mana riwayat bayan ki.
3122,"Yahya Qattan ne hamein ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( Asma (Raziallahu anha) ke aazad karda ghulam Abdullah ne mujh se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne jab wo Muzdalfa ke (andar baney huey mashhoor ( ghar ke paas ghihri hui thin, mujh se puchha : kya chaand ghurub ho gaya? maine kaha : nahi, unhon-ne ghadi bhar Namaz padhi, phir kaha : betey ! kya chaand ghurub ho gaya hai? maine arz ki, ji haan. unhon-ne kaha : mujhey ley chalo. to ham rawaana huey yahan tak ke unhon-ne jamara ( Aqba ( ko kankariyaan maarin phir (fajr ki) Namaz apni manzil mein ada ki. to maine unse kaha : mohtarma ! ham raat ke aakhiri pahar main ( hi ( rawaana ho gaey. unhon-ne kaha : bilkul nahi, mere betey ! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton ko (pahley rawaana honey ki) ijazat di thi."
3123,Esa-bin-Yonus ne ibne-Juraij se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( riwayat bayan ki aur unki riwayat mein hai unhon ( Asma (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha : nahi mere betey ! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni aurton (aur bachchon ( ko ijazat di thi.
3124,ibne-Juraij se riwayat hai (kaha : ( mujhey Ata ne khabar di ke unhein ibne-Shawaal ne khabar di ke wo Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas hazir huey unhon-ne unko bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein Muzdalfa se raat hi ko rawaana kar diya tha.
3125,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Amr Naqid ne Sufiyan-bin-Uena ke hawale se Amr-bin-Dinar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saalim-bin Shawaal se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham ( khawaateen ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein yahi karti thin (ke ( ham raat ke aakhiri pahar mein jama ( Muzdalfa ( se Mina ki taraf rawaana ho jati thin aur) Amr ( al-Naqid ki riwayat mein hai : ham raat ke aakhiri pahar mein Muzdalfa se rawaana ho jati thin."
3126,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein Ubaidullah bin abi Yazeed se khabar di unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzdalfa se (oonton par ladey) bojh. ya kaha : kamzor logon ke sath raat hi rawaana kar diya tha."
3127,"ham se Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Ubaidullah bin abi Yazeed ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : main un logon mein se tha jinhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ghar ke kamzor afraad main ( shamil kartey huey) pahley rawaana kar diya tha."
3128,"Ata ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : un logon mein se tha jinhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ghar ke kamzor afraad main ( shamil kartey huey) pahley rawaana kar diya tha."
3129,hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di kaha : mujhey Ata ne bataya ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahar ke waqt Muzdalfa se oonton par ladey bojh ke sath (jis mein kamzor afraad bhi shamil hotey hain) rawaana kar diya (ibne-Juraij ne kaha : ( maine ( ata se) kaha : kya aapko ye baat pahunchi hai ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey lambi raat (ke waqt) rawaana kar diya tha? unhon-ne kaha : nahi sirf yahi (kaha : (ke sahar ke waqt rawaana kya. maine unse kaha : (kya (Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne (ye bhi) kaha : ham ne fajr se pahley jamara Aqba ko kankariyaan maarein ? aur unhon-ne fajr ki Namaz kahan ada ki thi? unhon-ne kaha : hamein ( mujh se) sirf yahi ( الفا ظ kahey .)
3130,"Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) apne ghar ke kamzor afraad ko pahley rawaana kar detey they. wo log raat ko Muzdalfa mein mash'ar- haram ke paas hi waquf (thehertey) kartey, aur jitna muyassar hota Allah ka zikr kartey, iske baad wo imam ke mash'ar haram ke samney waquf aur iski rawaangii se pahley hi rawaana ho jatey. unmein se kuchh fajr ki Namaz ( ada karne) ke liye Mina aa jatey aur kuchh uske baad aatey. phir jab wo sab log Mina aa jatey to jamara Aqba ko kankariyaan maartey . Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un ( kamzor logon ( ko rukhsat (ch'oont) di hai."
3131,"hamein abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ibrahim se unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne jamara Aqba ko wadi ke andar se saat (7) kankariyon ke sath rami ki wo har kankari ke sath ( Allahu-akbar ( kehtey they. ( Abdur-Rehman ne) kaha : unse kaha gaya : kuchh log usey ( jamara ko) uski oopri taraf se kankariyan maartey hain to Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is zaat ki qism jiske siwa koi maabood nahi ! yahi us hasti ke khadey honey ki jagah hai jin par sura Baqra nazil ki gaee."
3132,"ibne-Mus-hir ne mujhey Aamash se khabar di ( unhon-ne ( kaha : maine Hajjaj-bin-Yosuf se suna wo member par khutba detey huey keh raha tha : Quran ki wahi tarteeb rakho jo Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne rakhi ( neez sura Baqra kehney ke bajaey kaho ( wo sura jis mein Baqra ka zikr kya gaya hai wo sura jis mein Nisa ka tazkira hai wo sura jis mein aale-Imran ka tazkira hai. (Aamash ne) kaha iske baad mein Ibrahim se mila, maine unhein uski baat sunai to unhon-ne is par bura-bhala kaha aur kaha : mujh se Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed ne hadis bayan ki ke wo Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they. wo jamara Aqba ke paas aaey wadi ke andar khadey huey us ( jamara ( ko chaudai ke rukh apne samney rakha iske baad wadi ke andar se usko saat (7) kankariyan maarein wo har kankari ke sath Allahu-akbar kehtey they kaha : maine kaha : abu Abdur-Rehman kuchh log iske uper (ki taraf ( se usey kankariyan maartey hain unhon-ne kaha us zaat ki qasam! jiske siwa koi maabood nahi ! yahi us hasti ke khadey honey ki jagah hai jis par sura Baqra nazil hui."
3133,"ibne-abi-Zayda aur Sufiyan donon ne hamein Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hajjaj se suna, keh raha tha : sura Baqra na kaho. padhi.  aur un donon ne ibne-Mus-hir ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki,"
3134,"hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ghandar ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Shoba ne Hakam se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Ibrahim se aur unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) (bin Masood (ke sath Haj kya kaha : unhon-ne jamara Aqba ko saat (7) kankariyan maarin aur Baitullah ko apni baain taraf aur Mina ko daain taraf rakha aur kaha yahi unke khadey honey ki jagah hai jin par sura Baqra nazil ki gaee."
3135,"hamein Muaz Anbari ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne kaha : jab wo jamara Aqba ke paas aaey."
3136,"Salma bin kuheil ne Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya : kuchh log jamara Aqba ko ghaati ke uper se kankariyan maartey hain. kaha : to Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne wadi ke andar se usey kankariyan maarin . phir kaha : yahin se us zaat ki qism jiske siwa koi haqiqi maabood nahi ! us hasti ne kankariyaan maarin jin par sura Baqra nazil ki gaee."
3137,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aap qurbani ke din apni sawari par (sawar ho kar) kankariyaan mar rahe they aur farma rahe they : tumhen chahiye ke tum apne Haj ke tareeqey seekh lo, main nahi janta shayad us Haj ke baad mein (dobara) Haj na kar sakoon."
3138,"Maaqil ne Zaid-bin-abii-Unaisaa se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Yahya-bin-Husain se aur unhon-ne apni daadi Umme- Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ( Yahya-bin-Husain ne) kaha : maine unse suna keh rahi thin hujjatul-wadaa' ke mauqe par maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj kiya, maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us waqt dekha jab aap ne jamara Aqba ko kankariyaan maarein aur wapas paltey aap apni sawari par they aur Bilal aur Usama (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke sath they unmein se aik aagey se ( mahaar pakad kar) aap ki sawari ko haank raha tha aur doosra dhoop se ( bachao ke liye) apna kapda Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sar Mubarak par taaney huey tha. kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (is mauqe par) bahut si baatein irshad farmaein . phir maine aap se suna aap farma rahe they : agar koi katey huey a'azaa (ang) wala. ..۔ . mera khayal hai unhon ( Umme- Husain (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha :  kala ghulam bhi tumhara ameer bana diya jaey jo Allah ki kitab ke mutabiq tumhari qiyaadat karey to tum uski baat sunnaa aur itaat karna."
3139,abu abdur-Raheem ne Zaid-bin-abii-Unaisaa se unhon-ne Yahya-bin-Husain se aur unhon-ne apni daadi Umme- Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath alwad'aaii Haj kiya to maine Usama aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha unmein se aik Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ontni ki nakel thamey huey tha aur doosra kapdey ko uthaey garmi se ot kar raha tha yahan tak ke aap ne jamara Aqba ko kankariyaan maarein . Imam Muslim ne kaha : abu abdur-Raheem ka naam Khalid-bin-abi-Yazeed hai aur wo Muhammad-bin-Salma ke maamun hain unse Wakee aur Hajjaj Aawar ne ( hadis) riwayat ki.
3140,"abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bayan kar rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap ne jamara Aqba ko itni badi kankariyaan maarein jitni chutkii ( do ungliyon ( se maari janey wali kankariyaan hoti hain."
3141,"abu-Khalid-Ahmar aur ibne Idrees ne ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se aur unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani ke din chasht ke waqt jamara ( Aqba ( ko kankariyaan maarein aur uske baad (ke dinon mein tamam jamaron ko) us waqt jab suraj dhal gaya."
3142,"hamein Esa-bin-Yonus ne khabar di, (kaha : ( hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, (kaha : ( mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) . padhi. aagey usi ki tarah hai."
3143,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : istinja taaq dhelon se hota hai, jamaraat ki rami taaq hoti hai, Safa, Marwa ke darmyan saee taaq hoti hai, Baitullah ka tawaaf taaq hota hai. aur tum mein se jab koi istinja karey to taaq dhelon se kare."
3144,"Leis ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) (bin-Masood ( ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sar mundaayaa aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ki aik jamat ne sar mundaayaa , aur unmein se kuchh ne baal katwaaey. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah sar mundaaney walon par raham farmaey. aik ya do martaba (dua ki) phir farmaya : aur baal katwaaney walon par bhi. (unke liye sirf aik baar dua ki.)"
3145,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke samney qirat ki ke Naafe se riwayat hai, aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! sar mundaaney walon par raham farmaa. logon ( sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne kaha : aur baal katwaaney walon par aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! farmaya : aey Allah ! sar mundaaney walon par raham farmaa. sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne phir kaha : aur baal katwaaney walon par, aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! farmaya : aur baal katwaaney walon par) bhi raham farmaa.)"
3146,"hamein Abdullah-bin-Numair ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! sar mundaaney walon par raham farmaa. logon ( sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne kaha : aur baal katwaaney walon par aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! farmaya : aey Allah ! sar mundaaney walon par raham farmaa. sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne phir kaha : aur baal katwaaney walon par, aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! farmaya : aur baal katwaaney walon par bhii."
3147,"hamein abdul-wahaab ne hadis sunai, (kaha : ( hamein Ubaidullah ne isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne (apni ( hadis mein kaha : jab chothi baari aai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aur baal katwaaney walon par bhi."
3148,"Abu-Zaraa ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! sar mundaney walon ko bakhsh de. sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aur baal katwaney walon ko ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! sar mundaney walon ko bakhsh de. sahaba (Rizwanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aur baal katwaney walon ko ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! sar mundaney walon ko bakhsh de. sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aur baal katwaney walon ko ? farmaya : aur baal katwaney walon ko bhi."
3149,"Alaa ne apne walid ( Abdur-Rehman bin Yaqoob ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. aagey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se abu-Zura ki (riwaayat ki hui ( hadis ke ham-mana hai."
3150,"Wakee aur Abu-Dawud Tiyalisi ne hamein Shoba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Yahya bin Husain se aur unhon-ne apni daadi ( Umme- Husain (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sar mundaney walon ke liye teen baar aur baal katwaney walon ke liye aik baar duaa ki. aur Wakee ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par ka jumla nahi kaha."
3151,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par apne sar Mubarak ke baal mundaaey .
3152,"hamein Yahya-bin-Yahya ne hadis bayan ki (kaha ( hamein Hafs-bin-Ghiyas ne Hisham se khabar di unhon-ne Muhammad-bin-Sirin se aur unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Mina tashrif laey phir jamara Aqba ke paas aaey aur usey kankariyaan maarein phir Mina main apne padao par aaey aur qurbani ki, phir baal moondney waley se farmaya : pakdo aur aap ne apne ( sar ki) daain taraf ishara kiya phir baain taraf phir aap (apne baal Mubarak ( logon ko dene lagey."
3153,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba-ibne-Numair aur abu-Kuraib sab ne kaha hamein Hafs-bin-Ghiyas ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki lekin Abu-Bakar ne apni riwayat mein ye alfaz kahey aap ne hajjaam se kaha : ye lo aur apne hath se is tarah apni daain taraf ishara kiya (ke pahley daain taraf se shuru karo (aur apne baal Mubarak apne qareeb khadey huey logon mein taqseem farma diye phir hajjaam ko apni baain taraf ki taraf ishara kiya (ke ab baain taraf se hajaamat banao) hajjaam ne aap ka sar moond diya to aap ne (apne wo muey Mubarak ( Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ko ata farma diye aur abu-Kuraib ki riwayat mein hai kaha : ( hajjaam ne) daain taraf se shuru kiya to aap ne eik-eik, do-do baal karke logon mein taqseem farma diye, phir aap ne apni baain taraf ( hajaamat banaaney ka ( ishara farmaya, hajjaam ne is taraf bhi wahi kiya ( baal moond diye ( phir aap ne farmaya : kaha yahan abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) hain? phir aap ne apne muey Mubarak abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale farma diye."
3154,hamein Abdul-Aala ne hadis bayan ki (kaha ( hamein Hisham (bin-Hassan) ne Muhammad (bin-Sirin) se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jamara Aqba ko kankariyaan maarein phir qurbani ke oonton ki taraf tashrif le gaey aur unhein nehar kiya aur hajjaam (aap ke liye) betha hua tha aap ne (usey) apne hath ke sath apne sar se ( baal utaarney ka ( ishara kiya to usne aap (ke sar ( ki daain taraf ke baal utaar diye. aap ne wo baal un logon mein baant diye jo aap ke qareeb maujood they. phir farmaya : dusri taraf ke baal (bhi) utaar do. iske baad aap ne farmaya : abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) kahan hain? aur aap ne wo (muey mubarak) unhein de diye.
3155,"ham se Sufiyan ne hadis bayan ki (kaha ( maine Hisham-bin-Hassan se suna wo Ibne-Sirin se khabar de rahe they unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jamara Aqba ko kankariyaan maarein apni qurbani (ke oonton ( ko nehar kiya aur phir sar mundwaaney lagey to aap ne apne sar ki daain taraf moondney waley ki taraf ki to usne us taraf ke baal utaar diye aap ne abu-Talha Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya aur wo ( baal ( unke hawale kar diye. phir aap ne ( sar ki) baain taraf uski taraf ki aur farmaya, (iske ( baal utaar do. us ne wo baal utaar diye to aap ne wo bhi abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ko de diye aur farmaya : un ( baain taraf waley baalon ( ko logon mein taqseem kar do."
3156,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se unhon-ne Esa-bin-Talha-bin-Ubaidullah se unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha Hijjatul-wada' ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Mina mein logon ke liye thahrey rahe, wo aap se masayel poochh rahe they, aik aadmi aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main samajh na saka (ke pahley kya hai) aur maine qurbani karne se pahley sar mundwaa liya hai? aap ne farmaya : ( ab ( qurbani kar lo koi harj nahi. phir aik aur aadmi aaya aur kehney laga aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mujhey pata na chala aur maine rami karne se pahley qurbani kar li ? aap ne farmaya : ( ab ( rami kar lo koi harj nahi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kisi cheez ke mutaalliq jis mein taqdeem ya taakheer ki gaee nahi puchha gaya magar aap ne ( yahi ( farmaya : ( ab ( kar lo koi harj nahi."
3157,Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath khabar di ke Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) keh rahe they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( Mina mein) apni sawari par thahar gaey aur logon ne aap se sawalat shuru kar diye unmein se aik kehney wala keh raha tha. aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mujhey malum na tha ke rami (ka amal ( qurbani se pahley hai maine rami se pahley qurbaani kar li? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to ( ab ( rami kar lo koi harj nahi. koi aur shakhs kehta : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey malum na tha ke qurbani sar mundwaaney se pahley hai maine qurbani kar ne se pahley sar mundwaa liya hai? to aap farmatey ( ab ( qurbani kar lo koi harj nahi. ( Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha maine aap se nahi suna ke us din aap se un aamal ke barey mein jin mein aadmi bhool sakta hai ya la-ilm reh sakta hai unmein se kuchh umur (baton) ki taqdeem (aur taakheer (ya unse miltii-jultii baton ke barey mein nahi puchha gaya magar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( yahi ( farmaya : ( ab ( kar lo koi harj nahi.
3158,Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki. (iske baad) hadis ke aakhir tak Zohri se Yunus ki riwayat karda hadis ki tarah hai.
3159,"Esa ne hamein ibne-Juraij se khabar di kaha maine ibne-Shahab se suna keh rahe they Esa-bin-Talha ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, kaha mujhey Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke us doran mein jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qurbani ke din khutba de rahe they koi aadmi aap ki taraf ( rukh karke ( khada hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main nahi samajhta tha ke falan kaam falan se pahley hai phir koi aur aadmi aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mera khayal tha ke falan kaam falan-falan se pahley hoga ( unhon-ne ( un teen kaamon ( sar mundwaaney, rami aur qurbani ke barey mein puchha to (aap ne yahi farmaya : ( ab ( kar lo koi harj nahi."
3160,"Muhammad-bin-Bakr aur Saeed bin Yahya umwi ne apne walid (Yahya umwi) ke waastey se ibne-Juraij se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki, ibne-Bakr ki riwayat Esa ki guzishta riwayat ki tarah hai siwaey unke us qaul ke un teen chizon ke barey mein aur hai Yahya umwi to unki riwayat mein hai maine qurbani karne se pahley sar mundwaa liya, maine rami karne se pahley qurbani kar li aur usi se milti julti baatein ."
3161,"hamein (Sufiyan) bin Uena ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Esa-bin-Talha se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : koi aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : maine qurbani karne se pahley sar mundwa liya hai aap ne farmaya : ( ab ( qurbani kar lo rami kar lo koi harj nahi. ( kisi aur ne) kaha : maine rami se pahley qurbani kar li hai to aap ne farmaya : ( ab ( rami kar lo koi harj nahi."
3162,"Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( riwayat ki) Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ( maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha (aap) Mina mein ontni par) sawar ( they, to aap ke paas aik aadmi aaya. padhi. aagey ibne-Uena ki hadis ke ham-mana hadis hai."
3163,"Muhammad-bin abi Hafsa ne hamein Zohri se khabar di unhon-ne Esa-bin-Talha se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna jab aap ke paas qurbani ke din aik aadmi aaya aap jamara Aqba ke paas rukey huey they. usne kaha aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! maine rami karne se pahley sar mundwa liya hai. aap ne farmaya : (ab rami kar lo koi harj nahi. aik aur aadmi aaya. wo kehney laga : maine rami se pahley qurbani kar li hai? aap ne farmaya : ( ab ( rami kar lo koi harj nahi. phir aap ke paas aik aur aadmi aaya aur kaha maine rami se pahley tawaaf ifaaza kar liya ? hai? farmaya : ( ab ( rami kar lo koi harj nahi. kaha : maine aapko nahi dekha ke us din aap se kisi bhi cheez (ki taqdeem w taakheer (ke barey mein sawal kya gaya ho magar aap ne yahi farmaya : kar lo koi harj nahi."
3164,Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se qurbani karne sar mundwaaney rami karne aur) kaamon ki) taqdeem w taakheer ke barey mein puchha gaya to aap ne farmaya : koi harj nahi.
3165,Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani ke din tawaaf ifaaza kya. phir wapas aa kar Zohar ki Namaz Mina mein ada ki. Naafe ne kaha Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) qurbani ke din tawaaf ifaaza kartey phir wapas aatey Zohar ki Namaz Mina mein ada kartey aur bayan kya kartey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa hi kya tha.
3166,"Abdul-Azeez bin Rafee se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kya, maine kaha : mujhey aisi cheez bataiye jo aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se samjhi ho (aur yad rakhi ho) aap ne tarviya ke din (aath (8) zul-hijja ko) Zohar ki Namaz kahan ada ki thi? unhon-ne bataya Mina mein. maine puchha : aap ne ( Mina se) waapsi ke din Asr ki Namaz kahan ada ki? unhon-ne kaha Abtah mein. phir kaha ( lekin tum ( isi tarah karo jaisey tumharey Umra kartey hain."
3167,Ayub ne Naafe se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) Abtah mein padao kya kartey they (waapsi ke waqt Madina ke rastey mein Mina ke bahar wahin padao kya ja sakta tha)
3168,Sakhr bin Juveriya ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Muhassab mein padao karne ko sunnat samajhtey they aur wo rawaangi ke din Zohar ki Namaz ( hasba ( ) Muhassab ( mein ada kartey they. Naafe ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke baad khulafaa ne wadie-Muhassab mein qiyam kya.
3169,Abdullah-bin-Numair ne hadis bayan ki (kaha ( hamein Hisham ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha Abtah mein theharna (aemale-hajj ki sunnaton mein se koi ( sunnat nahi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan utrey they kyonke (Makka se) rawaana hotey waqt wahan se nikalna aasan tha.
3170,Hafs bin Ghiyas Hammad-bin-Zaid aur Habib almuallim sab ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
3171,Zohri ne Salim se riwayat ki ke Abu-Bakar umr aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Abtah mein padao kya kartey they. Zohari ne kaha mujhey Urwa ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di ke wo aisa nahi karti thin aur) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan utrey they kyonke padao ki wo jagah aap ke (Makka se) nikalney ke liye zyada aasan thi.
3172,Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha (Muhassab mein thaharna) koi cheez nahi wo to padao ki aik jagah hai jahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qiyam kya tha.
3173,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Zuhair-bin-Harab un sab ne ibne-Uena se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Saleh bin kaisaan se aur unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha abu Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab aap ne Mina se nikley, mujhey ye hukm nahi diya tha ke main Abtah mein qiyam karun lekin main ( khud ( wahan aaya aur aap ka khema lagaya iske baad aap tashrif laey aur qiyam kya Abu-Bakar (bin abi Sheba ( ne Saleh se ( bayan ki hui ( riwayat mein kaha unhon ( Saleh ( ne kaha maine Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se suna aur Quteba ki riwayat mein hai. ( Sulaiman ne) kaha abu Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke saman (ki hifazat aur naql w hamal ( par maamoor they."
3174,Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : kal ham insha-Allah khaif bani kinana ( wadi Muhassab) mein qiyam karengey jahan unhon (Quraish) ne aapasi kufr par (qaaim rehney ki) qism khaai thi.
3175,"Auzai ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha ( mujhey Zohri ne hadis sunai, (kaha : ( mujh se abu-Salma ne hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Mina mein they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein farmaya kal ham khaif banu-Kanana mein qiyam karengey jahan unhon (Qureish) ne aapas mein mil kar kufr par (datey rehney ki) qism khaai thi. waqia ye tha ke Quraish aur banu-Kanana ne banu-Haashim aur banu-Muttalib ke khilaf aik doosrey ke sath muaahida kya tha ke wo na unse shadi biyaah karengey na unse len-den karengey. yahan tak ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unke hawale kar dein. us ( khaif bani kinaana ( se aap ki murad wadi Muhassab thi."
3176,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya insha-Allah jab Allah ne fateh di to hamara qiyam khaif ( Muhassab ( mein hoga. jahan unhon ( Quraish ( ne aapas mein mil kar kufr par (qaaim rehney ki) qism khaai thi."
3177,"( Muhammad-bin-Abdullah (bin Numer aur abu-Usama donon ne kaha hamein Ubaidullah ne hadis bayan ki aur ibne-Numair ne. alfaz unhi ke hain. apne walid ke waastey se bhi Ubaidullah se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bin abdul-Muttalib ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat mangi ke wo ( zamzam par hajiyon ko) pani pilaaney ke liye Mina ki raatein Makka mein guzaar lein? to aap ne unhein ijazat de di."
3178,Esa-bin-Yonus aur ibne-Juraij donon ne Ubaidullah-bin-Umar (bin Hafs) se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
3179,Bakr-bin-abdullaah-Muzni ne kaha : main Kaba ke paas Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath betha hua tha ke unke paas aik dehati aaya aur kehney laga : kya wjah hai main dekhta hun ke tumharey chacha zaad ( haajiyon ko) doodh aur shehad pilaatey hain aur tum nabeez pilaatey ho? ye tumhen honewali haajat mandi ki wjah se hai ya kanjoosi ki wjah se? Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya al-hamdulillah na hamein zaroorat-mandi laahiq hai aur na kanjoosi ( asl baat ye hai ke) Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par) Sawar ho kar) tashrif laey aur aap ke peechhey Usama (Raziallahu anhu) sawar they aap ne pani talab farmaya to ham ne aapko nabeez ka aik bartan pesh kya aap ne khud piyaa aur baqi bachi Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ko pilaya aur farmaya : tum logon ne achchha kya aur bahut khub kya isi tarah kartey rehna. lihaza ham nahi chahtey ke jis kaam ka Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ham usey badal dein.
3180,"abu khisma ne hamein Abdul Karim se khabar di unhon-ne Mujahid se unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya ke main aap ke qurbani ke oonton ki nigraani karun aur ye ke unka gosht, kha lein aur jhoolen sadqa karun neez unmein se qassaab ko bataur ujrat kuchh bhi) na dun Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ham usko apne paas se ( ujrat ( dengey."
3181,ibne-Uena ne Abdul-Karim Jazri se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
3182,Sufiyan aur Hisham donon ne ibne-abi Najeeh se unhon-ne Mujahid se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki un donon ki hadis mein qassaab ki ujrat ka zikr nahi.
3183,Hasan-bin- Muslim ne khabar di ke unhein Mujahid ne khabar di unhein Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela ne khabar di unhein Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya ke wo aap ki qurbani ke oonton ki nigrani karein aur unhein hukm diya ke aap ki poori qurbaniyon ko (yani) unke gosht khaalon aur (unki pusht par dali hui ( jholon ko miskinon mein taqseem kar dein aur unmein se kuchh bhi zabah ki ujrat ke taur par na dein.
3184,Abdul Karim bin Malik Jazri ne Mujahid se (baqi bachi) usi pichhli sanad ke sath khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya. (aagey) usi ki tarah hai.
3185,"Imam Malik ne abu-Zubair se aur unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha Hudaibiya ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ham ne saat (7) afraad ki taraf se aik oont saat (7) ki taraf se aik gaaey ki qurbaniyan din."
3186,hamein Zuhair ne hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj ka talbiya kehtey huey nikley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke ham oont aur gaaey mein Sharik ho jayen ham mein se saat (7) aadmi aik qurbani mein Sharik hon.
3187,hamein Azra bin Sabit ne abu-Zubair se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj kya ham ne saat (7) aadmiyon ki taraf se aik oont nehar (Qurban) kya aur saat (7) aadmiyon ki taraf se aik gaaey ( zabah ki.)
3188,Yahya-bin-Saeed ne ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki (kaha ( mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna unhon-ne kaha ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj w Umerey mein saat (7) aadmi aik qurbani mein Sharik huey to aik aadmi ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha kya ehram ke waqt se sath laey gaey qurbani ke janwaron mein bhi is tarah sharaakat ki ja sakti hai jaisey baad mein khareedey gaey janwaron mein sharaakat ho sakti hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : wo bhi sath laey gaey qurbani ke janwaron hi ki tarah hain. aur Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) Hudaibiya ke mauqe par maujood they unhon-ne kaha ham ne us din 70 oont nehar (qurban) kiye ham saat (7) saat aadmi (qurbani ke aik) oont mein Sharik huey they.
3189,"hamein Muhammad-bin-Bakr ne hadis bayan ki (kaha) hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di (kaha) hamein abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Haj ka haal suna rahe they unhon-ne us hadis mein kaha : (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) hamein hukm diya ke jab ham ehram kholein to qurbani karein aur ham mein se chand ( saat (7) ( aadmi aik qurbani mein Sharik ho jayen aur ye ( hukm us waqt diya) jab aap ne hamein apne Haj ke ehram kholney ka hukm diya, ye baat bhi us hadis mein hai."
3190,Ata ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( Haj ke mahinon mein) Umra karne ka fayda uthatey (hajje-tamatto kartey) to ham (yaumun-Nahar aur Baqi tashreeq ke dinon mein) saat (7) afraad ki taraf se aik gaaey zabah kartey us (eik) mein Sharik ho jatey.
3191,hamein Yahya bin Zakariya-bin abi Zayda ne ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne abu-Zubair se unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : qurbani ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (aur doosrey ummahatul-momeneen) ki taraf se aik gaaey zabah ki.
3192,"Muhammad-bin-Bakr aur Yahya-bin-Saeed ne kaha hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki kaha hamein abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ki taraf se, aur ibne-Bakr ki hadis mein hai : apne Haj main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf se aik gaaey zabah ki."
3193,Ziyad bin Juber se riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aik aadmi ke paas aaey aur wo apni qurbani ke oont ko bitha kar nehar kar raha tha unhon-ne farmaya : usey utha kar khadi haalat mein ghutna baandh kar (nehar karo yahi) tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat hai.
3194,hamein Leis ne ibne-Shahab se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair aur Umara binte-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina se qurbani ke janwaron ka hadiya bheja kartey they aur main aap ke hadiye (ke janwaron (ke liye haar bat-ti thi phir aap kisi bhi aisi cheez se ijtinab na kartey jis se aik ehram wala shakhs ijtinab karta hai.
3195,Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath iske jaisi hadis bayan ki.
3196,"hamein Sufiyan ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Urwa se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, neez Hisham-bin-Urwa ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha jaisey mein khud ko dekhti rahi hun ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qurbani ke haar bat rahi hun. ( aagey ( isi tarah hai."
3197,Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim ne apne walid se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna wo farma rahi thin : main apne un donon hathon se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se bhejey janey waley janwaron ke haar bat-ti thi phir aap na ( aisi ( kisi cheez se alag hotey aur na (aisi koi cheez) tark kartey they (jo ehram ke baghair aap kya kartey they)
3198,Aflah ne hamein Qasim se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : maine apne donon hathon se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qurbaniyon ke haar batey phir aap ne unka ashaar kya (kohaan par cheer lagaey) aur haar pehnaey phir unhein Baitullah ki taraf bhej diya aur) khud ( Madina mein muqeem rahe aur aap par (unki wjah se) koi cheez jo (pahley (aap ke liye halal thi haram na hui.
3199,Ayub ne Qasim aur abu-Qilaba se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( Baitullah ki taraf ( qurbani ka janwar bhejtey they main apne donon hathon se unke haar bat-ti thi phir aap kisi bhi aisi cheez se ijtinab na kartey they jis se koi bhi ghair mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) ( baghair ehram wala shakhs) ijtinab nahi karta.
3200,hamein Ibne-Aun ne Qasim se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Ummul-Momenin (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha)) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : maine ye haar us oon se batey jo hamarey paas thi iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham mein ghair-mohrim hi rahe aap (apni beeviyon ke paas) aatey jaisey ghair mohrim apni biwi ke paas aata hai ya aap aatey jaisey aik ( aam ( aadmi apni biwi ke paas aata hai.
3201,Mansoor ne Ibrahim se unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : maine khud dekha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qurbani ka janwar (qurbani) ke liye bakriyon ke haar bat rahi hun iske baad aap unhein (Makka) bhejtey phir hamarey darmyan ehram ke baghair hi rehtey.
3202,"Yahya-bin-Yahya abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib mein se Yahya ne kaha : abu-Muawiya ne hamein khabar di aur doosrey donon ne kaha hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aamash se unhon-ne Ibrahim se unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : aisa hua ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qurbani ka janwar ( qurbani ke liye Baitullah bhejey janey waley janwar) ke liye haar taiyaar karti aap wo (haar) un janwaron ko daltey phir unhein (Makka) bhejtey phir aap (Madina hi mein) thehartey aap unmein se kisi cheez se ijtinab na farmatey jin se ehram baandhney wala shakhs ijtinab karta hai."
3203,Yahya-bin-Yahya abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib ne baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik baar Baitullah ki taraf qurbani ka janwar ( qurbani ( ki bakriyan bhejin to aap ne unhein haar daley.
3204,Hakam ne Ibrahim se unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha ham bakriyon ko haar pahnaatey phir unhein ( Baitullah ki taraf ( bhejtey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghair mohrim (baghair ehram ke) rahtey us se koi cheez (jo pahley aap par halal thi) haram na hoti thi.
3205,Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di ke ibne- Ziyad ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko likha ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha hai jisne qurbani ka janwar ( Baitullah ke liye qurbani ( bheja is par wo sab kuchh haram ho jaeyga jo Haj karne waley ke liye haram hota hai yahan tak ke qurbani ke janwar ko zabah kar diya jaey. aur maine apni qurbani ka janwar bheja hai to mujhey (is barey mein) apna hukm likh bhejiyey Umra ne kaha Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : ( baat ( is tarah nahi jaisey Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha hai maine khud apne hathon se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qurbaniyon ke haar batey phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se wo ( haar ( unhein pehnaey phir unhein mere walid ke sath (Makka) bheja iske baad qurbani ka janwar nehar ( qarbaan ( honey tak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par) aisi ( koi cheez haram na hui jo Allah ne aap ke liye halal ki thi.
3206,"Ismael-bin-abi Khalid ne hamein khabar di unhon-ne Shabi se aur unhon-ne Masruq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna wo pardey ki ot se hath par hath mar rahi thin aur keh rahi thin main apne hathon se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qurbaniyon ke haar bata karti thi, phir aap unhein (Makka) bhejtey aur qurbani ke janwar ko zabah karne (ke waqt) tak aap unmein se kisi cheez se bhi ijtinab na farmatey jis se ehram wala shakhs ijtinab (bachaa) karta hai."
3207,"Dawud aur Zakariya donon ne Shabi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Masruq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne usi ( hadis) ke mutabiq Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat bayan ki."
3208,"Imam Malik ne abu-Zinad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se, aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ko dekha wo qurbani ka oont haank raha hai to aap ne farmaya : is par Sawar ho jao. usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! ye qurbani ka oont hai aap ne farmaya : tumhari hilaakt ! is par Sawar ho jao . dusri ya teesri martaba (ye alfaz kahey.)"
3209,Mughira bin Abdur-Rehman-hazaamii ne abu-Zinad se aur unhon-ne Aaraj se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur kaha is beech mein ke aik aadmi haar daley gaey oont ko haank raha tha.
3210,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : ye hadisey hain jo hamein Hazrat abu hureira (Raziallahu anhu) ne Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, phir unhon-ne chand hadisey zikr kiin. unmein se aik ye hai, aur kaha : is beech mein ke aik shakhs haar waley qurbani ke oont ko haank raha tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : tumhari halaakt ! is par Sawar ho jao . usne kaha aey Allah ke rasool! ye qurbani ka oont hai. aap ne farmaya : tumhari halaakat ! is par Sawar ho jao . tumhari halaakat ! is par Sawar ho jao."
3211,"Sabit Bunani ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik aadmi ke paas se guzrey jo qurbani ka oont haank kar ley ja raha tha, to aap ne farmaya : is par Sawar ho jao . us ne jawab diya : ye qurbani ka oont hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : is par Sawar ho jao. do ya teen martaba (farmaya)."
3212,hamein Wakee ne Misar se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Bukair-bin-Akhnas se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : maine un ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) se suna keh rahe they Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se qurbani ke aik oont ya ( haram ke liye) hadiya kiye janey waley aik janwar ka guzar hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : is par Sawar ho jao . usne kaha : ye qurbani ka oont ya qurbani ka janwar hai aap ne farmaya : chahey aisa hi hai.
3213,"hamein ibne-Bishr ne Misar se hadis bayan ki, (kaha ( mujhey Bukair-bin-Akhnas ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se qurbani ka aik oont guzara gaya aagey usi ki tarah bayan kiya."
3214,ibne-Juraij se riwayat hai) unhon-ne kaha ( mujhey Zuber ne khabar di kaha maine Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna unse qurbani ke janwar par sawari karne ke barey mein puchha gaya to unhon-ne kaha maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna farma rahe they jab us ( par Sawar honey) ki zarurat ho to aur sawari milney tak Maruf (qaabile-qabool) tareeqey se is par sawari karo.
3215,hamein Maaqil ne abu-Zubair se hadis bayan ki kaha : maine Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se qurbani ke janwar (Baitullah ki taraf bhejey gaey hadiya qurbani) par sawari ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : dusri sawari milney tak is par Maruf tareeqey se Sawar ho jao.
3216,"hamein Abdul Waris-bin-Saeed ne abu-Tayyah Zubai se khabar di (kaha ( mujh se Musa-bin-Salma Hazli ne hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha, main aur Sanan-bin-Salma Umra ada karne ke liye nikley aur Sanan apne sath qurbani ka oont lekar chaley wo usey haank rahe they. to rastey hi mein wo thak kar ruk gaya, wo uski haalat ke sabab se (ye samajhney se) aajiz aagey ke agar wo bilkul hi reh gaya to usey (Makka) kaisey laaein . unhon-ne kaha : agar main balade-ameen (Makka ( pahunch gaya to main har sura iske barey mein achi tarah poochhoon ga. ( Musa ne) kaha : to mujhey din chadh gaya, jab ham ne Batha mein qiyam kiya to unhon-ne kaha : Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas chalein taake ham unse baat karein. kaha unhon-ne unko apni qurbani ke janwar ka haal bataya to unhon-ne kaha tum jaanney waley ke paas aa pahunchey ho. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ke sath Baitullah ke paas qurbani ke liye sola oont rawaana kiye aur usey unka nigraan banaya. kaha wo thodi door gaya phir wapas aaya aur kehney laga aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! unmein se koi thak kar ruk jaey, uske sath main kya karun? aap ne farmaya : usey nehar kar dena phir iske ( galley mein daley gaey ( donon jootey uske khoon se rang dena phir unhein (bataur nishani) iske pahlu par rakh dena aur (ehram ki haalat mein) tum aur tumharey sath janey walon mein se koi us (ke gosht mein) se kuchh na khaaey."
3217,"Ismail-bin-Ulaih ne abu-Tayyah se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Musa-bin-Salma se aur unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani ke atthaara oont aik aadmi ke sath rawaana kiye..... padhi. phir Abdul Waris ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, aur unhon-ne hadis ka shuruaati hissey bayan nahi kiya."
3218,"abu-qabeesa-zuweb ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke sath qurbani ke oont bhejtey phir farmatey agar unmein se koi thak kar ruk jaey aur tumhen iske mar janey ka khadsha (andeshaa) ho to usey nehar kar denaa, phir iske ( galley mein latkaey gaey ( jootey ko iske khoon mein dubonaa phir usey uske pahlu par daal dena, phir tum usmein se ( kuchh ( khana na tumharey sathiyon mein se koi. (is mein se khaaey)"
3219,Saeed-bin-Mansoor aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne hamein hadis bayan ki donon ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Sulaiman ahwal se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Taaus se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : log ( Haj ke baad) har samt mein nikal ( kar chaley ( jatey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi bhi shakhs hargiz rawaana na ho yahan tak ke uski aakhiri haziri ( bataur tawaaf ( Baitullah ki ho. Zuhair ne kaha : ''har simt'' aur ''har samt mein'' nahi kaha.
3220,Taaus ke betey ( Abdullah ( ne apne walid se unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : logon ko hukm diya gaya ke unki aakhiri haziri Baitullah ki ho magar usmein haaiza aurat ke liye kami ki gaee hai (wo aakhiri tawaaf se mustashnaa (aazad) hai.)
3221,Hasan-bin- Muslim ne Taaus se khabar di unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha ke Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap fatwa detey hain ke haaiza aurat aakhiri waqt mein Baitullah ki haziri ( tawaaf ( se pahley (iske baghair ( lot sakti hai? to Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : agar ( aapko yaqin ( nahi to falan Ansar ye se poochh lein kya rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein is baat ka hukm diya tha? kaha : iske baad Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) wapas aaey wo hans rahe they aur keh rahe they mein samajhta hun ke aap ne sach hi kaha hai.
3222,"hamein Leis ne ibne-Shahab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Salma aur Urwa se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) tawaaf ifaaza karne ke baad haaiza ho gain Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney unke haiz ka tazkira kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya wo hamein (waapsii se) rokney wali hain? ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! wo ( tawaaf ifaaza ke liye) gaee thin aur Baitullah ka tawaaf kiya tha phir ( tawaaf ( ifaaza karne ke baad haaiza hui hain to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to ( phir hamarey sath hi ( kooch karein."
3223,Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath khabar di (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) hujjatul-wadaa' ke mauqe par tahaarat (paakizgi) ki haalat mein tawaaf ifaaza kar leney ke baad haaiza ho gain . aagey Leis ki hadis ki tarah hai.
3224,Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim ne apne walid ( Qasim-bin-Muhammad-bin-abi-Bakr ( se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney zikr kiya ke Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) haaiza ho gaee hain aagey Zohri ki hadis ke ham mana (alfaz hain.)
3225,"Aflah ne hamein Qasim-bin-Muhammad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha ham dar rahi thin ke Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) tawaaf ifaaza karne se pahley haaiza na ho jaaein. kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laey aur farmaya : kya Safiya hamein rokney wali hain? ham ne kaha wo tawaaf ifaaza kar chuki hain aap ne farmaya to phir nahi (rokengii)."
3226,Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) haaiza ho gaee hain to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : shayad hamein ( waapsii se) rok lein gii. kya unhon-ne tumharey sath Baitullah ka tawaaf ( tawaaf ifaaza ( nahi kiya? unhon-ne kaha kyon nahi aap ne farmaya : to phir kooch karo.
3227,abu-Salma ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) se aisa koi kaam chaha jo aik aadmi apni biwi se chahta hai to sab ( beeviyon ( ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! wo haaiza hain aap ne farmaya : to (kya) ye hamein ( kooch ( karne se) rokney wali hain? unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! unhon-ne qurbani ke din tawaaf ziyaarat ( tawaaf ifaaza ( kar liya tha. aap ne farmaya : to wo bhi tumharey sath kooch karen.
3228,Hakam ne Ibrahim se unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab rawaangii ka irada kiya to achcha (dekha ke) Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) apne khemey ke darwazey par parieshaan khadi thin aap ne farmaya : tumhara na koi baal na bachcha ! ( phir bhi) tum hamein ( yahin ( rokney wali ho. phir aap ne unse puchha : kya tum ne qurbani ke din tawaaf ifaaza kiya tha? unhon-ne jawab diya : ji haan aap ne farmaya : to ( phir ( chalo. (yani unke paas ja kar unse bhi puchha aur tasdeeq ki)
3229,Aamash aur Mansoor donon ne ibrahim se unhon-ne Aswad se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. (aagey) hakam ki hadis ke ham mana riwaayat hai albatta wo donon (unke) ghamzada aur pareshan honey ka zikr nahi kartey.
3230,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba mein dakhil huey, Aap (sl), Usama , Bilal aur Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha ( Hajabi ( (Raziallahu anhu) . unhon (Usman (Raziallahu anhu)) ne (aap ke liye) iska darwaza band kar diya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske andar thaharey rahe. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nikley to maine Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (andar) kya kiya? unhon-ne kaha aap ne do sutoon apni baain taraf aik sutoon daain taraf aur teen sutoon apne peechhey ki taraf rakhey. un dinon Baitullah (ki Imaarat ( chh sutunon par) qaaim ( thi phir aap ne Namaz padhi."
3231,"hamein Hammad ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Ayub ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha fateh Makka ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif ley aaey aap Baitullah ke sehan mein utrey aur Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf paigham bheja wo chaabii lekar hazir huey aur darwaza khola, kaha : phir Nabi (sl), Bilaal, Usama-bin-Zaid aur Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) andar dakhil huey aap ne darwazey ke barey mein hukm diya to usey band kar diya gaya wo sab khasi der wahan thahrey phir unhon-ne (Usman (Raziallahu anhu)) ne darwaza khola Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha maine sab logon se sabqat ki aur bahar nikaltey waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mila, Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke peechhey-peechhey they, to maine Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein Namaz ada farmai hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan maine poochha, kahan? unhon-ne kaha : do sutunon ke darmyan jo aap ke samney they ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : main unse ye pochhnaa bhool gaya ke aap ne kitni rakatein padhein."
3232,"Sufiyan ne hamein Ayub sakhtiyan se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha fateh Makka ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ki ontni par) Sawar ho kar) tashrif laey yahan tak ke aap ne usey Kaba ke sehan mein la bithaya phir Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulwaya aur kaha : mujhey ( Baitullah ki) chaabii do wo apni walida ke paas gaey to usne unhein chaabii deney se inkar kar diya. unhon-ne kaha ya to tum ye chaabii mujhey dogii ya phir ye talwaar meri peeth se paar nikal jaeygi, kaha to usne wo chaabii unhein de di wo usey lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo chaabii unhi ko de di to unhon ( hi ( ne darwaza khola phir Hammad-bin-Zaid ki hadis ki tarah bayan ki."
3233,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Baitullah mein dakhil huey aap ke sath Usama , bilal aur Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they unhon-ne apne peechhey khasi der darwaza band kiye rakha phir ( darwaza ( khola gaya to main pahlaa shakhs tha jo ( darwazey se) dakhil hua, mein bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se mila aur puchha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kahan Namaz ada ki? unhon-ne kaha : aagey ke 2 sutunon ke darmyan jo aap ke samney they ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : main unse ye pochhnaa bhool gaya ke aap ne kitni rakatein ada kin."
3234,"Abdullah Aun ne hamein Naafe se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo Kaba ke paas pahunchey jabke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Bilal aur Usama (Raziallahu anhu) usmein dakhil ho chukey they Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke peechhey darwaza band kiya. kaha wo usmein kafi der thahrey phir darwaza khola gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey, main seedhi chadhaa aur Baitullah mein dakhil hua maine puchha Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kahan Namaz padhi? unhon-ne kaha is jagah , kaha : main unse ye poochhna bhool gaya ke aap ne kitni rakatein padhein."
3235,"Leis ne hamein ibne-Shahab se khabar di unhon-ne Salim se unhon-ne apne walid ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Baitullah mein dakhil huey Aap (sl), Usama-bin-Zaid , Bilal aur Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) unhon-ne apne peechhey darwaza band kar liya. jab unhon-ne darwaza khola to main sabse pahlaa shakhs tha, jo ( Kaba mein) dakhil hua mein bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se mila aur unse puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein Namaz ada ki? unhon-ne jawab diya : haan aap ne do yamnii sutunon ke darmyan Namaz ada ki."
3236,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di (kaha ( mujhey Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne apne walid ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se khabar di unhon-ne kaha maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba mein dakhil huey, Aap (sl), Usama-bin-Zaid , Bilal aur Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) . unke sath aur koi dakhil nahi hua phir unke peechhey darwaza band kar diya gaya. Aabdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha mujhey Bilal ya Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Kaba ke andar do yamnii sutunon ke darmyan Namaz ada ki."
3237,"ibne-Juraij ne hamein khabar di kaha : maine Ata se puchha : kya aap ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna hai ke : tumhen tawaaf ka hukm diya gaya hai is ( Baitullah ( mein dakhil honey ka hukm nahi diya gaya. unhon-ne jawab diya : wo usmein dakhil honey se mana nahi kartey they, lekin maine unse suna keh rahe they mujhey Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Baitullah mein dakhil huey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske tamam aas-paas mein dua ki aur is mein Namaz ada nahi ki. yahan tak ke bahar aagey jab aap tashrif laey to qible ke samney ki taraf do rakatein ada kiin aur farmaya : ye qibla hai maine unse puchha : iske aas-paas se kya murad hai? kya iske konon mein ? unhon-ne kaha : balke Baitullah ke har taraf."
3238,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba mein dakhil huey aur is mein chh (6) sutoon they aap ne aik sutoon ke paas khadey ho kar dua mangi , aur) wahan ( Namaz ada nahi ki."
3239,"hamein Ismail-bin-abi Khalid ne khabar di, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi Abdullah-bin-abi-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne Umerey ke doran mein Baitullah mein dakhil huey they? unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi."
3240,"abu-Muawiya ne hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa se khabar di unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : agar tumhari qaum ka zamana kufr qareeb ka na hota, to main zaroor Kaba ko giraataa aur usey Hazrat Ibrahim ki buniyaad par teyyaar karta. Quraish ne jab Baitullah ko tameer kiya tha to usey chhota kar diya tha. main ( asl tameer ke mutabiq ( iska pichhlaa darwaza bhi banata ."
3241,ibne-Numair ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki.
3242,"Saalim-bin-Abdullah se riwayat hai ke Abdullah-bin-Muhammad-bin-abi-Bakr siddeeq ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey huey Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum ne nahi dekha tumhari qaum ne jab Kaba tameer kiya to usey Hazrat Ibrahim ki buniyaadon se kam kar diya. kaha, maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya aap usey dobara Ibrahim ki buniyaadon par nahi lautaaein gey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tumhari qaum ka zamana, kufr qareeb ka na hota to main ( zaroor aisa ( karta. Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha agar ye baat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi to main nahi samajhta ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hateem ke qaribi donon arkaan ka bosa diya, uske ilawa kisi aur wjah se tark kiya ( ho, asl wjah ye thi) ke Baitullah Ibrahim ki buniyaadon par pura ( tameer ( nahi kiya gaya tha."
3243,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Naafe kehtey hain maine Abdullah-bin abi-Bakr-abi-qahaafa (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis suna rahe they, unhon ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap ne farmaya : agar tumhari qaum jahiliyat . ya farmaya zamanae kufr, se abhi-abhi na nikli hoti to main zaroor Kaba ke khazaaney Allah ki raah mein kharch kar deta iska darwaza zamin ke barabar kar deta aur hijr ( Hateem ( ko Kaba mein shamil kar deta."
3244,"Saeed yani ibne- Mina se riwayat hai kaha maine Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they. mujh se meri khala yani Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Aaisha ! agar tumhari qaum ka shirk ka zamana qareeb ka na hota to main zaroor Kaba ko giraataa us (ke darwazey ( ko zamin ke sath laga deta aur main iske do darwazey sharqii (purvi) darwaza aur doosra gharbii (pashchimi) darwaza banata aur hijr ( Hateem ( se chh (6) hath (ka hissey ( usmein shamil kar deta. bila shubah Quraish ne jab Kaba tameer kiya tha to usey chhota kar diya."
3245,"Ata se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : Yazeed-bin-Muawiya ke daur mein jab Sham (Syria) walon ne (Makka par) hamla kiya aur Kaba jal gaya to uski jo haalat thi so thi ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey (usi haalat par) rehney diya. yahan tak ke Haj ke mausam mein log (Makka) aaney lagey. wo chahtey they ke unhein himmat dilaaen. ya Sham (Syria) walon ke khilaf jang par ubhaarey. jab log aaey to unhon-ne kaha aey logo ! mujhey Kaba ke barey mein mashwara do main usey gira kar (naye sire se) iski Imaarat bana dun ya iska jo hissey boseeda ho chuka hai sirf uski marammat kara dun? Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mere samney aik raey waazeh hui hai meri raey ye hai ke iska bada hissey kamzor ho gaya hai aap uski marammat kara dein aur Baitullah ko (usi tarah baqi ( rehney dein. jis par log Islam laey aur un pattharon ko) baqi chhod dein ( jin par log Islam laey aur jin par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko paighamber bana kar bheija gaya, is par ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha agar tum mein se kisi ka apna ghar jal jaey to wo us waqt tak razi nahi hota jab tak ke usey nayaa (na) bana ley to tumharey rab ke ghar ka kya ho? main teen din apne rab se istikhaara karunga, phir apne kaam ka pukhta azm karunga. jab teen din guzar gaey to unhon-ne apni raey pukhta kar li ke isey gira dein to log (is dar se) us se bachney lagey ke jo shakhs is (Imaarat) par sabse pahley chadhey ga is par aasman se koi aafat nazil ho jaeygi. yahan tak ke aik aadmi is par chadhaa aur usne aik patthar gira diya jab logon ne dekha ke usey kuchh nahi hua to log aik doosrey ke peechhey (gira ne lagey) yahan tak ke usey zamin tak pahuncha diya. ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne chand ( aarizii ( sutoon banaey aur pardey un par latkaa diye yahan tak ke uski Imaarat buland ho gaee. ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko ye kehtey suna bila shubah Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar logon ke kufr ka zamana qareeb ka na hota, aur mere paas itna maal bhi nahi jo iski tameer (mukammal karne) mein mera muaawin ho, to main Hateem se panch hath ( zamin ( usmein zaroor shamil karta aur iska aik (aisa) darwaza banata jis se log andar dakhil hotey aur aik darwaza ( aisa banata ( jis se bahar nikaltey. (ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha aaj mere paas itna maal hai jo kharch kar sakta hun aur mujhey logon ka khof bhi nahi ( ata ne) kaha : to unhon-ne Hateem se panch hath usmein shamil kiye (khudaaee ki) yahan tak ke unhon-ne Ibraaheemii ( buniyaad ko zahir kar diya logon ne bhi usey dekha iske baad unhon-ne is par Imaarat banai Kaba ka tool (unchaaee) athareh (18) hath thi (ye is tarah hui ke) jab unhon-ne (Hateem ki taraf se) usmein izafa kar diya to (phir) unhein ( pehli unchaaee) kam mehsus hui chunanche unhon-ne uski unchaaee mein das hath ka izafa kar diya aur uske darwazey banaey aik mein se andar daa-khulla hota tha aur doosrey se bahar nikla jata tha. jab ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) qatl kar diye gaey to Hajjaj ne abdul-Malik-bin-Marwan ko itlaa' detey huey khat likha aur usey khabar di ke ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski tameer us ( Ibraaheemii ( buniyaadon par ustwaar ki jisey ahale Makka ke moa'tabar ( udool ( logon ne ( khud ( dekha Abdul-Malik ne usey likha. hamara ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke raddo badal se koi talluq nahi albatta unhon-ne uski oonchaaii mein jo izafa kiya hai usey bar qarar rehney do aur jo unhon-ne Hateem ki taraf se usmein izafa kiya hai usey (khatm karke) uski pichhli baniyaad par lota do aur us darwazey ko band kar do jo unhon-ne khola hai. chunanche us ne usey gira diya uski (pichhli ( buniyad par lota diya."
3246,"Muhammad-bin-Bakr ne hamein hadis bayan ki (kaha ( hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-Ubaid-bin-Umair aur Waleed-bin-Ata se suna, wo donon Haaris-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-Abdullah-bin-Ubai Rabee se hadis bayan kar rahe they, Abdullah-bin-Ubaid ne kaha : Haaris-bin-Abdullah , abdul-Malik-bin-Marwan ki khilaafet ke doran mein uske paas aaey, Abdul-Malik ne kaha : mera khayal nahi ke abu-Khubaib , yani ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se jo sunney ka dawa kartey they wo unse suna ho. Haris ne kaha : kyon nahi ! maine khud un (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( se suna hai usne kaha : tum ne us se suna wo kya kehti thin ? kaha : unhon (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha tha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah tumhari qaum ne ( Allah ke ghar ki Imaarat mein kami kar di aur agar unka zamana shirk qareeb ka na hota to jo unhon-ne chhoda tha mein usey dobara banata aur tumhari qaum ka agar mere baad usey dobara banaaney ka khayal ho to aao main tumhen dikhaaun unhon-ne usmein se kya chhoda tha. phir aap ne unhein saat (7) hath ke qareeb jagah dikhai. ye Abdullah-bin-Ubaid ki hadis hai Waleed-bin-Ata ne usmein ye izafa kiya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aur main zamin se lagey huey iske mashriqii aur maghribii do darwazey banata aur kya tum janti ho tumhari qaum ne iske darwazey ko uncha kyon kiya? (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha maine kaha nahi. aap ne farmaya : khud ko uncha dikhaaney ke liye taake us ( ghar ( mein sirf wahi dakhil ho jisey wo chaahein. jab koi aadmi khud usmein dakhil honaa chahta to wo usey ( seedhiyaan ( chadhney detey yahan tak ke jab wo dakhil honey lagta to wo usey dhakka de detey aur wo gir jata. Abdul-Malik ne Haris se kaha : tum ne khud unhein ye kehtey huey sunaa? unhon-ne kaha : haan ! kaha : to usne ghadi bhar apni chhadi se zamin ko kureda , phir kaha : kaash! ! main unhein ( ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko) aur jis kaam ki zimme-dari unhon-ne uthai usey chhod deta."
3247,abu-Aasim aur Abdur-Razzaq donon ne ibne-Juraij se isi sanad ke sath ( Muhammad ( bin-bikar ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
3248,"abu-Qaza' se riwayat hai ke abdul-Malik-bin-Marwan jab Baitullah ka tawaaf kar raha tha to usne kaha : Allah ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko halaak karey, ke wo Ummul-Momenin par jhoot bolta hai. wo kehta hai maine unhein ye kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Aaisha ! tumhari qaum ke kufr ka zamana qareeb ka na hota to main Baitullah ko giraataa yahan tak ke usmein Hateem mein se ( kuchh hissey ( badha deta bila shubah tumhari qaum ne uski Imaarat ko kam kar diya hai. is par Haaris-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-Rabee ne kaha : ameerul-momeneen aisa na kahey . maine khud Ummul-Momenin se suna hai wo ye hadis bayan kar rahi thin. ( Abdul-Malik ne) kaha : agar maine ye baat usey girane se pahley sun li hoti to main usey isi tarah chhod deta jis tarah ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne banaya tha."
3249,"abu-Ahwas ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Ash'as-bin-abu-Shasa ne Aswad-bin-Yazeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( Hateem ki) diwar ke barey mein malum kiya, kya wo Baitullah mein se hai? aap ne farmaya : haan. maine kaha : to unhon-ne usey Baitullah mein shamil kyon nahi kiya? aap ne farmaya : tumhari qaum ke paas kharch kam pad gaya tha. maine kaha iska darwaza kyon uncha hai? aap ne farmaya : ye kaam tumhari qaum ne kiya taake jisey chaahein andar dakhil honey dein aur jisey chaahein mana kar dein agar tumhari qaum ka zamana jahiliyat ke qareeb ka na hota, us wjah se main darta hun ke unke dil usey na-pasand karengey. to main is par ghaur karta ke) Hateem ki) diwar ko Baitullah mein shamil kar dun aur uske darwazey ko zamin ke sath mila dun."
3250,"Sheban ne hamein Ash'as-bin-abu-Shasa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aswad-bin-Yazeed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Hateem ke barey mein sawal kiya. aagey abu-Ahwas ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki aur is mein kaha : maine kaha : iska darwaza kis wjah se uncha hai, is par seedhi ke baghair chadhaa nahi ja sakta aur) Sheban ne ye bhi) kaha is dar se ke unke dil usey naa pasand karengey."
3251,"Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne ibne-Shahab se unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari par peechhey sawar they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas qabila Khasam ki aik khatun aai. wo aap se fatwa poochhaney lagi, Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) uski taraf aur wo unki taraf dekhney lagi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ka chehra dusri taraf pherney lagey. usne kaha aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! bila shubah Allah ka apne bandon par farz kya hua Haj mere kamzor aur boodhey walid par bhi aa gaya hai, wo sawari par jam kar baith nahi saktey to kya main unki taraf se Haj kar sakti hon? aap ne farmaya : haan aur ye Hijjatul-wada; mein hua."
3252,ibne-Juraij ne pichhli sanad ke sath Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke qabila Khasam ki aik aurat ne arz kiya. aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mere walid umr raseeda hain aur Allah ka fareeza Haj unke zimmey hai aur oont ki pusht par theek tarah baith nahi saktey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum unki taraf se Haj kar lo.
3253,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Ibraaheem-bin-Aqba se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Kureb se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke roohaa ke maqam par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mulaqat aik qafley se hui, aap ne puchha : kon log hain? unhon-ne kaha : musalman hain. phir unhon-ne puchha : aap kon hain? aap ne farmaya : main Allah ka rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hon usi doran mein aik aurat ne aap ke samney aik bachchey ko buland kiya aur kaha kya iska Haj hoga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan aur tumharey liye ajr hoga."
3254,abu-Usama ne Sufiyan se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : aik aurat ne aap ke samney aik bachchey ko buland kiya aur kaha : kya iska Haj hoga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan aur tumharey liye ajr hai.
3255,Abdur-Rehman ne Sufiyan se unhon-ne Ibraaheem-bin-Aqba se aur unhon-ne Kureb se riwayat ki ke : aik aurat ne aik bachchey ko buland kiya aur kaha aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iska Haj hoga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan aur tumharey liye ajr hai.
3256,"ham se Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman ne baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki."
3257,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein khutba diya aur farmaya : logo ! tum par Haj farz kiya gaya hai lihaza Haj karo. aik aadmi ne kaha : kya har saal? aey Allah ke rasool ! aap khamosh rahe yahan tak ke usne ye kalima teen baar dohraaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar main keh deta : haan to wajib ho jata aur tum ( uski ( istitaat (taaqat) na rakhtey. phir aap ne farmaya : tum mujhey usi ( baat ( par rehney diya karo jis par main tumhen chhod dun tum se pahley log kasarate-sawal aur apne anbiya se zyada ikhtilaaf ki bina par halaak huey. jab main tumhen kisi cheez ka hukm dun to baqadr istitaat usey karo, aur jab kisi cheez se mana karun to usey chhod do."
3258,"Yahya qattaan ne hamein Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( mujhey Naafe ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi aurat teen (din, raat) ka safar na karey magar is tarah ke uske sath mehrem ho."
3259,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham se Abdullah-ibne-Numair aur abu-Usama ne hadis bayan ki, neez ibne-Numair ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki un sab ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki Abu-Bakar ki riwayat mein hai ke teen din se zyada , aur ibne-Numair ne apne walid se bayan karda riwayat mein kaha : teen din magar is tarah ke iske sath mehrem ho."
3260,ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah ‌(sl) ne farmaya ‌ : halal nahi kisii aurat ko jo eimaan rakhti ho Allah par aur aakhiret ke din par ke safar karey teen raat ka magar uske sath koi mehrem ho ‌ .
3261,Qaza' ne kaha : maine abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se aik hadis suni jo mujhey bahut pasand aai aur maine unse kaha ‌ : aap ne Rasulullah ‌(sl) se suni hai? unhon-ne kaha ke jo maine unse na suni hoti to main kya Rasulullah ‌(sl) ki taraf nisbat karta ! jo aap se nahi suni. ‌ab suno ke janab Rasulullah ne farmaya : ''na baandho tum kajaawon ko (yani safar na karo) magar teen masjidon ki taraf aik meri ye masjid aur dusri masjidul-haraam aur teesri masjide-aqsaa aur suna maine aap se ke farmatey they ke koi aurat safar na karey do din ka zamaney mein se magar uske sath mehrem ho ya uska shauhar ho.
3262,"Shoba ne hamein abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Qaza' se suna, unhon-ne kaha maine Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se char baatein sunein jo mujhey bahut achi lagein aur bahut pasand aaein. aap ne mana farmaya ke koi aurat do din ka safar karey magar is tarah ke uske sath uska shoher ya koi mehrem ho. aur aagey baqi hadis bayan ki."
3263,"saham-bin-minjaab ne Qaza' se unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ‌ se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi aurat teen din ka safar na karey magar ye ke mehrem sath ho."
3264,Muaz Anbari ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Qaza' aur unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi aurat teen raaton se zyada ka safar na karey magar ye ke mehram ke sath ho.
3265,Saeed ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur kaha : teen ( din) se zyada ka safar magar ye ke mehram ke sath ho.
3266,"Leis ne hamein Saeed-bin-abi-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi musalman aurat ke liye halal nahi wo aik raat ki masafat (safar) tay karey magar is tarah ke iske sath aisa aadmi ho jo iska mehram ho."
3267,"ibne-abi-Ze-ib se riwayat hai (kaha : ( hamein Saeed-ibne-abi-Saeed ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : kisi aurat ke liye jo Allah aur yaum aakhirat par eman rakhti hai. halal nahi ke wo aik din ki masafat (safar) tay karey magar ye ke mehram ke sath ho."
3268,"Imam Malik ne Saeed-bin-abi-Saeed Maqbari se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo aurat Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhti hai uske liye halal nahi ke wo aik din aur raat ka safar karey magar is tarah ke uska mehram iske sath ho."
3269,"Abu-Saleh ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi aurat ke liye halal nahi ke teen din safar karey magar is tarah ke uske sath iska koi mehram ho."
3270,"abu-Muawiya ne hamein Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo aurat Allah aur yaum aakhirat par eman rakhti hai uske liye halal nahi ke wo teen din ya us se zayed ka safar karey magar ye ke uske sath uska walid ya uska betaa ya uska khawind ya uska bhai ya uska koi mehram ho."
3271,Wakee ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
3272,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Amr-bin-Dinar ne abu-Mabad se hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap khutba detey huey farma rahe they : koi mard kisi aurat ke sath hargiz tanha na ho magar ye ke uske sath koi mehram ho. aur koi aurat safar na karey magar ye ke mehram ke sath ho. aik aadmi utha aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke rasool ! meri biwi Haj ke liye nikli hai aur mera naam falan-falan ghazwey mein likha ja chuka hai. aap ne farmaya : jao aur apni biwi ke sath Haj karo."
3273,Hammad ne hamein Amr (bin-Dinar ( se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana hadis bayan ki.
3274,"ibne-Juraij ne ( Amr-bin-Dinar se) isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki, aur ye ( jumla ( zikr nahi kiya : koi mard kisi aurat ke sath hargiz tanha na ho magar ye ke uske sath koi mehram ho."
3275,"saiyedna Ali azdii (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke saiyedna ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein sikhaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kahin safar mein janey ke liye apne oont par Sawar hotey to teen baar Allahu-akbar farmatey, phir ye dua padhtey : (سبْحانَ الذي سخَّرَ لَنَا هذا وما كنَّا له مُقرنينَ ، وَإِنَّا إِلى ربِّنَا لمُنقَلِبُونَ . اللَّهُمَّ إِنَّا نَسْأَلُكَ في سَفَرِنَا هذا البرَّ والتَّقوى ، ومِنَ العَمَلِ ما تَرْضى . اللَّهُمَّ هَوِّنْ علَيْنا سفَرَنَا هذا وَاطْوِ عنَّا بُعْدَهُ ، اللَّهُمَّ أَنتَ الصَّاحِبُ في السَّفَرِ ، وَالخَلِيفَةُ في الأهْلِ. اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْ وعْثَاءِ السَّفَرِ ، وكآبةِ المنظَرِ ، وَسُوءِ المنْقلَبِ في المالِ والأهلِ)                          ''pak hai wo zaat jisne is janwar ko hamarey taabea' kar diya aur ham isko daba na saktey they aur ham apne parwardigar ke paas lot janey waley hain ( الزخرف : 14 , 13 (aey Allah ! ham tujh se apne is safar mein neki aur parhezgari maangtey hain aur aisey kaam ka sawal kartey hain jisey to pasand kare. aey Allah ! ham par is safar ko aasan kar de aur iski masafat ko ham par thoda kar de. aey Allah tu hi safar mein rafeeq safar aur ghar mein nigraan hai. aey Allah ! main tujh se safar ki takleefon aur ranj aur gham se aur apne maal aur ghar walon mein burey haal mein lot kar aaney se teri panah mangta hun.''                                                                                                                                                                         (ye to jatey waqt padhtey) aur jab lot kar aatey to bhi yahi dua padhtey magar ismein itna zyada kartey ke :                     (آيبون ، تائبون ، عائدون ، عابدون ، لربنا حامدون )                                                                                                                              ''ham lotney waley hain, tauba karne waale, khas apne rab ki ibadat karne waley aur usi ki tareef karne waley hain.''"
3276,"Ismail-bin-Ulaih ne hamein Aasim ahwal se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-sarjis se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab safar kartey to safar ki mashaqqat , waapsii mein uktaahat , ikattha honey ke baad bikhar janey , mazloom ki bad-duaa se aur ahal aur maal mein se kisi burey manzar se panah maangtey."
3277,"abu-Muawia ( Muhammad-bin-khaazim (aur abdul-Wahid donon ne Aasim se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki, magar abdul-Wahid ki hadis mein maal aur ahl mein ke alfaz hain aur Muhammad-bin-khaazim ki riwayat mein hai, kaha : jab aap wapas aatey to ahal (ki salamati ki dua ( se shuruaat kartey aur (ye) donon ki riwayat mein hai aey Allah ! main safar ki thakaan se teri panah mangta hun."
3278,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab badey lashkaron ya chhotey daston (ki muhimon ( se ya Haj ya Umerey se laut'tey to jab aap kisi ghaati ya unchi jagah par chadhtey , teen martaba Allahu-akbar kehtey, phir farmatey :                                (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد وهو على كل شيء قدير ، آيبون ، تائبون ، عابدون ، ساجدون ، لربنا حامدون ، صدق الله وعده ونصر عبده وهزم الأحزاب وحده)                                                                                                                                                                              ''Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, wo akelaa hai, iska koi Sharik nahi, Sara ikhtiyar isi ka hai. hamd usi ke liye hai aur wahi har cheez par qaadir hai. ham lotney waale, tauba karne waale, ibadat karne waale, sajda karne waale, apne rab ki tareef karne waley hain, Allah ne apna wada sachcha kiya, apne bandey ki madad ki aur tanha usi ne tamam jamaton ko shikast di.''"
3279,"Ayub , Malik aur Zuhhaak sab ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, siwaey Ayub ki hadis ke , usmein takbeer do martaba hai."
3280,"Ismail-bin-Ulaih ne hamein Yahya-bin-abi-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main aur abu Talha Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (safar se) waapas aaey aur Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki ontni par aap ke peechhey ( sawar ( thin. jab ham Madina ke oopri hissey mein they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ham lotney waale, tauba karne waale, ibadat karne waale, apne rab ki tareef karne waley hain, aap musalsal yahi baat kehtey rahe yahan tak ke ham Madina aa gaey."
3281,"Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Yahya-bin-abi-Ishaq ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ke manind riwaayat ki."
3282,"Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne barsati pani ki sangrezon aur ret wali guzargaah ( Batha ( mein jo zul-Hulaifa mein hai, ontni ko bithaya aur wahan Namaz ada ki. ( Naafe ne) kaha : Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) isi tarah kiya kartey they."
3283,"Leis ne hamein Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) us retlii, pathreelii wadi mein oont ko bithatey jo zul-Hulaifa mein hai, jahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ontni ko bithatey they aur Namaz ada kartey."
3284,"Anas (bin-ayaaz), yani abu-Zamra ne Musa-bin-Aqba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab Haj ya Umerey se laut'tey to us pathreelii, retiilii wadi mein oont ko bithatey jo zul-Hulaifa mein hai jahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ontni ko bithatey they."
3285,"Hatim , yani ibne- Ismail ne hamein Musa-bin-Aqba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Salim se, unhon-ne apne walid (Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke zul-Hulaifa mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raat ki aaram ki jagah par (eik aaney waley ko) bheja gaya, aur aap se kaha gaya ke aap aik Mubarak wadi mein hain."
3286,"Ismail-bin-Jafar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Musa-bin-Aqba ne Salim bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar se khabar di, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas , jab aap zul-Hulaifa main apni aaraam gaah mein jo wadi ke darmyan thi, ( kisi aaney waley ko) bheja gaya, aur aap se kaha gaya : aap Mubarak wadi mein hain. Musa (bin-Aqba ( ne kaha : Salim ne hamarey sath masjid ke qareeb usi jagah oont bithaaey jahan Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bithaya kartey they, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raat ke pichhley pahar ki aaram ki jagah talash kartey they, aur wo jagah usi masjid se nichey thi, jo wadi ke darmyan mein thi, us (masjid (ke aur qibley ke darmyan , iske beech mein."
3287,"Amr (bin-Haaris ( ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman (bin-Auf ( se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, neez Yunus (bin-Yazeed-eilii ( ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey us Haj mein jis mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada se pahley unhein ameer banaya tha, aik chhoti jamat ke sath rawaana kiya ke wo log qurbani ke din logon mein (ye ( elaan karein ke is saal ke baad koi mushrik Haj nahi karega aur na koi barahna shakhs Baitullah ka tawaaf karega. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman (bin-Auf (Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ki bina par kaha kartey they : qurbani ka din hi hajje-akbar ka din hai."
3288,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : bila shubah Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi din nahi jis mein Allah Taala Arfa ke din se badh kar bandon ko aag se aazad farmata ho, wo (apne bandon ke) qareeb hota hai. aur farishton ke samney un logon ki bina par fakhr karta hai aur poochhta hai : ye log kya chahtey hain?"
3289,"Imam Malik ne Abu-Bakar-bin-Abdur-Rehman ke aazad karda ghulam Sumai se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh aur sammaan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik Umra doosrey Umerey tak (ke gunahon (ka kaffara hai aur hajje-mabroor , iska badla jannat ke siwa aur koi nahi."
3290,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena, Suhel , Ubaidullah , Wakee aur Sufiyan ( Sory ( sab ne Sumai se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Malik-bin-Anas ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
3291,"Jarir ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs ( Allah (ke is ghar mein aaya, na koi gandi baat ki aur na gunah kiya to wo ( gunahon se paak ho kar) is tarah lautey ga jis tarah usey uski maan ne janm diya tha."
3292,"abu-Awana , abu-Ahwas , Misar , Sufiyan aur Shoba sab ne Mansoor se isi sanad ke sath ye hadis bayan ki aur un sab ki hadis mein ye alfaz hain : jisne Haj kiya aur us ne na na koi gandi baat ki aur na koi gunah kiya."
3293,"Sayyar ne abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, usi ki tarah."
3294,"Younus-bin-Yazeed ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di ke Ali-bin-Husain ne unhein khabar di ke Amr-bin-Usman-bin-Affan ne unhein Usama-bin-Zaid-bin-haaris (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di unhon-ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool ! kya aap Makka mein apne ( aabaaii ( ghar mein qiyam farmaaengey? aap ne farmaya : kya Aqeel ne hamarey liye iihaaton ya gharon mein se koi cheez chhodi hai. Aqeel aur taalib abu-Taalib ke waaris baney they aur Jafar aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse koi cheez wiraasat mein haasil na ki, kyonke wo donon musalman they, jabke Aqeel aur taalib kaafir they."
3295,"Mamar ne Zohri se unhon-ne Ali-bin-Husain se unhon-ne Amr-bin-Usman se aur unhon-ne Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ( unhon-ne kaha : ( maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! aap kal kahan qiyam karengey? ye baat aap ke Haj ke doran mein hui jab ham Makka ke qareeb pahunch chukey they, to aap ne farmaya : kya Aqeel ne hamarey liye koi ghar chhoda hai !?"
3296,"Muhammad-bin-abi-Hafsa aur zam'a-bin-Saleh donon ne kaha ibne-Shahab ne hamein hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Ali-bin-Husain se, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Usman se unhon-ne Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! kal insha-Allah aap kahan thahrein gey? ye fateh Makka ka zamana tha aap ne farmaya : kya Aqeel ne hamarey liye koi ghar chhoda hai !"
3297,"Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Humaid (bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ( se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Umar-bin-Abdul-Azeez ko Saaib-bin-Yazeed (Raziallahu anhu) se poochhtey huey suna keh rahe they : kya aap ne Makka mein qiyam karne ke barey mein) Rasulullah ka ( koi farman suna hai? Saaib ne jawab diya : maine Alaa-bin-hizramii (Raziallahu anhu) se suna : keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : (Makka se) hijrat kar janey waley ke liye (Minaa se) lotney ke baad Makka mein teen din qiyam karna jaaiz hai. bhale hi ya aap ye farma rahe they. ke us se zyada na thahrey."
3298,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Humaid se khabar di unhon-ne kaha : maine Umar-bin-abdul azeez se suna, wo apne sathi se keh rahe they : tum ne ( Haj ke baad) Makka mein thaharney ke barey mein kya suna? Saaib-bin-Yazeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Alaa ya kaha : Alaa-bin-hizramii (Raziallahu anhu)  se suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : hijrat kar janey wala apni ibadat ( Haj ya Umra ( mukammal karne ke baad Makka mein teen din thahar sakta hai."
3299,"Saleh ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Humaid se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Umar-bin-Abdul-Azeez se suna, wo Saaib-bin-Yazeed (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kar rahe they, to Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : maine Alaa-bin-hizramii (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : muhajir (Minaa se) lotney ke baad teen raatein Makka mein thahar sakta hai."
3300,Ismail-bin-Muhammad-bin-Sad ne mujhey khabar di ke Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne unhein bataya ke Saaib-bin-Yazeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Alaa-bin-hizramii (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khabar di : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : muhajir ka apni ibadat mukammal karne ke baad Makka mein qiyam teen din tak ka hai.
3301,"zuh'haak-bin-mukhlid ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein ibne-Juraij ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah khabar di."
3302,"Jarir ne hamein Mansoor se khabar di, unhon-ne Mujahid se, unhon-ne Taaus se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke din farmaya : ab hijrat nahi hai. albatta jihad aur niyat baqi hai. aur jab tumhen Nafair aam (jihad mein haazirii) ke liye kaha jaey to nikal pado. aur aap ne fateh Makka ke din farmaya : bila shubah ye Shahar (aisa) hai jisey Allah ne (us waqt se) hurmat ata ki hai jab se us ne aasmanon aur zamin ko paida kiya. ye Allah ki) ata karda ( hurmat (ki wjah ( se qiyamat tak ke liye mohtaram hai aur mujh se pahley kisi aik ke liye usmein ladai ko halal qarar nahi diya gaya aur mere liye bhi din mein se aik ghadi ke liye hi usey halal kiya gaya hai. ( ab ( ye Allah ki) ata karda ( hurmat ki wjah se qiyamat ke din tak haram hai, iske kaantey na kaatey jaye, iske shikar ko dara kar na bhagaa ya jaey, koi shakhs ismein giri hui cheez ko na uthaey , siwaey iske jo iska elaan karey, neez uski ghaas bhi na ka-tii jaey. is par Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! siwaey izkhir ( khushbu daar ghaas (ke , wo unke loharon aur gharon ke liye ( zaroori ( hai. to aap ne farmaya : siwaey izkhir ke."
3303,"Mufazzal ne hamein Mansoor se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne jis din se Allah Taala ne aasmanon aur zamin ko paida kiya ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye. qitaal ( ladai (ke bajaey qatl ka lafz kaha aur kaha yahan ki girii-padi cheez us shakhs ke siwa jo iska elaan karey, koi na uthaey ."
3304,"abu-shureh Adwi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Amr-bin-Saeed se jab wo ( ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke khilaf ( Makka ki taraf lashkar bhej raha tha kaha : aey ameer ! mujhey ijazat dein. mein aapko aik aisa farman bayan karun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke doosrey din irshad farmaya tha. usey mere donon kanon ne suna, mere dil ne yad rakha aur jab aap ne iske alfaz boley to meri donon aankhon ne aapko dekha. aap ne Allah Taala ki hamd aur sana bayan ki, phir farmaya : bila shubah Makka ko Allah ne hurmat ata ki hai. logon ne nahi. kisi aadmi ke liye jo Allah aur yaume-aakhirat par eman rakhta ho halal nahi ke wo usmein khoon bahaaey aur na (ye halal hai ke) kisi darakht ko kaatey. agar koi shakhs usmein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ladai ki bina par rukhsat nikaley to usey keh dena : bila shubah Allah ne apne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ijazat di thi, tumhen uski ijazat nahi di thi aur aaj hi uski hurmat isi tarah wapas aa gaee hai jaisey kal uski hurmat maujood thi. aur jo hazir hai (ye baat (us tak pahuncha de jo hazir nahi. is par abu Shureh (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya : ( jawab mein) Amr ne tum se kya kaha? (kaha : (us ne jawab diya : aey abu Shureh ! main ye baat tum se zyada janta hun haram kisi naafarmaan ( baaghii ( ko khoon karke bhag aaney waley ko aur chori karke faraar hone-waale ko panah nahi deta."
3305,"Waleed-bin-Muslim ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha ( hamein Auzai ne hadis sunai, (kaha : ( mujhey Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne hadis sunai, (kaha : ( mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne aur) unhon-ne kaha : ( mujhey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Makka par fateh ata ki to aap logon mein) khutba dene ke liye) khadey huey Allah ki hamd aur sana bayan ki. phir farmaya : bila shubah Allah ne haathii ko Makka se rok diya aur apne rasool aur mominon ko is par tasallut ata kiya. mujh se pahley ye hargiz kisi ke liye halal na tha. mere liye din ki aik ghadi ke liye halal kiya gaya. aur mere baad ye hargiz kisi ke liye halal na hoga. isliye na iske shikar ko dara kar bhagaaya jaey aur na iske kaantey ( daar darakht ( kaatey jayen aur is mein girii-padi koi cheez uthana elaan karne waley ke siwa kisi ke liye halal nahi. aur jiska koi qaribi (azeez) qatl kar diya jaey uske liye do Suraton mein se wo hai jo ( uski nazar mein) behtar ho : ya uski diyat di jaey ya (qaatil ( qatl kya jaey. is par Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! izkhir ke siwa, ham usey apni qabron (ki silon ki darzon (aur gharon (ki chhaton ( mein istemal kartey hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izkhir ke siwa , is par Yaman waalon mein se aik aadmi abu Shah khadey huey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! (ye sab ( mere liye likhwaa dijiye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : abu Shah ke liye likh do. Waleed ne kaha : maine Auzai se puchha is ( yamnii (ka ye kehna aey Allah ke rasool ! mujhey likhwaa dein. (is se murad ( kya tha? unhon-ne kaha : ye khutba ( murad tha) jo usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha."
3306,"Sheban ne Yahya se riwayat ki, (kaha : ( mujhey abu-Salma ne khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : fateh Makka ke saal khuza'aa ne banu- Leis ka aik aadmi apne aik maqtool ke badley mein jisey unhon-ne ( banu-Lais ( ne qatl kiya tha qatl kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski khabar di gaee to aap apni sawari par baithey aur khutba irshad farmaya : bila shubah izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne haathii ko Makka ( par hamley ( se rok diya. jabke apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur mominon ko is par tasallut (qaabu) ata kiya. mujh se pahley ye kisi ke liye halal nahi tha aur mere baad bhi hargiz kisi ke liye halal na hoga. sun lo ! ye mere liye din ki aik ghadi bhar halal kiya gaya tha. aur) ab ( ye meri is maujooda ghadi mein bhi hurmat wala hai. na dandey ke zariey se iske kaantey jhaadey jayen, na iske darakht kaatey jayen aur na hi elaan karne waley ke siwa ismein giri hui cheez uthaey aur jiska koi qaribi qatl kar diya gaya uske liye do Suraton mein se wo hai jo ( uski nazar mein) behtar ho : ya usey ata kar diya jaey. yani khoon baha . ya maqtool ke ghar walon ko us se badla leney diya jaey. kaha : to ahal Yaman mein se aik aadmi aaya jisey abu Shah kaha jata tha usne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mujhey likhwaa dein aap ne farmaya : abu Shah ko likh do. Quraish ke aik aadmi ne kaha : izkhir ke siwa , (kyonke) ham usey apne gharon aur apni qabron mein istemal kartey hain to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izkhir ke siwa."
3307,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : tum mein se kisi ke liye Makka mein aslaha uthana halal nahi."
3308,"Abdullaah-bin-Muslima Qa'nabi , Yahya-bin-Yahya aur Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne hamein hadis bayan ki, Qa'nabi ne kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney qirat ki Quteba ne kaha : ham se Imam Malik ne hadis bayan ki aur Yahya ne kaha, padhi. alfaz unhi ke hain maine Imam Malik se puchha : kya ibne-Shahab ne aapko Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh ke saal Makka mein dakhil huey aur aap ke sar Mubarak par khud tha jab aap ne usey utara to aap ke paas aik aadmi aaya aur kehney laga : ibne- khatal Kaba ke pardon se chimtaa hua hai aap ne farmaya : usey qatl kar do? to Imam Malik ne jawab diya. :  haan"
3309,Yahya-bin-Yahya tamimi aur Qutaiba-bin-Saeed Saqafi ne hamein hadis bayan ki. Yahya ne kaha : hamein Muawiya-bin-Ammar-dahnii ne abu-Zubair se khabar di aur Quteba ne kaha : hamein hadis bayan ki. unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein dakhil huey. padhi. Quteba ne kaha : fateh Makka ke din . baghair ehram ke dakhil huey aur aap (ke sar Mubarak ( par siyah amama tha. Quteba ki riwayat mein hai (Muaawiya-bin-Ammar ne) kaha : hamein abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki.
3310,Sharik ne hamein Ammar dahnii se khabar di unhon-ne abu-Zubair se unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka ke din dakhil huey to aap (ke sare-mubaarak ( par siyah rang ka amama tha.
3311,"Wakee ne hamein musaawir war'raaq se khabar di, unhon-ne Jafar bin-Amr-bin Hurais se unhon-ne apne walid ( Umra bin-hurriyat-bin-Amr makhzumi (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko khutba diya jabke aap (ke sar Mubarak ( par siyah amama tha."
3312,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Hasan Hulwani ne hamein hadis bayan ki donon ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne musaawir war'raq se hadis bayan ki. kaha : mujhey hadis bayan ki) Jafar-bin-Amr ne) aur Hulwani ki riwayat mein hai kaha : maine Jafar-bin-Amr-bin-hurriyat se suna. unhon-ne apne walid ( Amr-bin-Hurais (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jaisey main ( ab bhi) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko member par dekh raha hun, aap (ke sar Mubarak ( par siyah amama hai aap ne iske donon kinaron ko apne donon kandhon ke darmyan latkaaya hua hai. Abu-Bakar (bin-abi-Sheba ( ne member par ke alfaz nahi kahey."
3313,Abdul-Azeez yani Muhammad darawardi ke betey ne Amr-bin-Yahyaa Mazni se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Ibad-bin-Tameem se unhon-ne apne chacha Abdullah-bin-Zaid Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah Ibrahim ne Makka ko haram qarar diya aur uske rehney walon ke liye dua ki aur maine Madina ko haram qarar diya jaisey Ibrahim ne Makka ko haram qarar diya tha aur maine iske saa aur mudd mein us se dugnii ( barkat ( ki dua ki jitni Ibrahim ne Makka waalon ke liye ki thi.
3314,Abdul-Azeez yani ibne- Mukhtar Sulaiman-bin-Bilal aur Wuhaib (bin-Khalid Bahili ( sab ne Amr-bin-Yahyaa Mazni se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki Wuhaib ki hadis darawardi ki hadis ki tarah hai is se dugnii ( barkat ( ki jitni barkat ki Ibrahim ne dua ki thi jabke Sulaiman-bin Bilal aur Abdul-Azeez bin Mukhtar donon ki riwayat mein hai jitni ( barkat ki) Ibrahim ne dua ki thi.
3315,"Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Usman ne Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah Hazrat Ibrahim ne Makka ko haram thehraya aur main us ( Shahar ( ki donon siyah patthar zaminon ke darmyan mein waaqe hissey ko haram qarar deta hun.  Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad Madina tha."
3316,"Naafe-bin-Juber se riwayat hai ke Marwaan-bin-Hakam ne logon ko khitab kiya, us ne Makka ke baashindon aur uski hurmat ka tazkira kiya aur Madina ke baashindon aur uski hurmat ka tazkira na kiya to Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ne buland awaz se usko mukhatibb kiya aur kaha : kya hua hai? mein sun raha hun ke tum ne Makka , iske baashindon aur uski hurmat ka tazkira kiya, lekin Madina , iske baashindon aur uski hurmat ka tazkira nahi kiya. halanke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske donon siyah pattharon wali zaminon ke darmyan mein waaqe  iilaqae ko haram qarar diya hai. aur (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ( wo farman Kholani chamdey mein hamarey paas mehfooz hai. agar tum chaho to usey main tumhen padha dun. is par Marwan khamosh hua phir kehney laga : iska kuchh hissey maine bhi suna hai."
3317,Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah Ibrahim ne Makka ko haram qarar diya aur main Madina ko. jo in do siyah pattharilii zaminon ke darmyan hai haram qarar deta hun. na iske kaantey daar darakht kaatey jayen aur na iske shikar ke janwaron ka shikar kiya jaey.
3318,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Usman bin-Hakim ne hadis bayan ki (kaha ( mujh se Aamir-bin-Sad ne apne walid ( Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main Madina ki do siyah pathreelii zaminon ke darmyani hissey ko haram thehra-taa hon ke iske kaantedaar darakht kaatey jayen ya ismein shikar ko maara jaey. aur aap ne farmaya : agar ye log jaan lein to Madina unke liye sabse behtar jagah hai. koi bhi aadmi is se be raghbatii kartey huey isey chhod kar nahi jata. magar uske badley mein Allah Taala aisa shakhs usmein ley aata hai jo us ( janey waale) se behtar hota hai. aur koi shakhs iski tangdastii aur mashaqqat par Sabit qadam nahi rehta magar main qiyamat ke din uske liye sifarishi ya gawah hoonga."
3319,"Marwan-bin-Muawiya ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Usman-bin-Hakim Ansari ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( mujhey Aamir-bin-Sad-bin-abi-Waqas ne apne walid se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : phir ibne-Numair ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya aur hadis mein in alfaz ka izafa kiya : aur koi shakhs nahi jo ahal Madina ke sath burai ka irada karega. magar Allah Taala usey aag mein seesey ke pighlney ya pani mein namak ke pighlney ki tarah pighlaa dega."
3320,Ismail-bin-Muhammad ne aamir-bin-Sad se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Sad (bin-abii-waqaas (Raziallahu anhu)) (Madina ke qareeb) aqeeq mein apne mahal ki taraf rawaana huey. unhon-ne aik ghulam ko dekha wo darakht kaat raha tha ya iske pattey jhaad raha tha. unhon-ne us se (iska libaas aur saazo saman) salb kar liya. jab Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) (Madina ( lotey to ghulam ke Malik unke paas hazir huey aur unse guftgu ki ke unhon-ne jo unke ghulam se salb kiya hai wo ghulam ko ya unhein wapas kar dein. unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki panah ke main koi aisi cheez wapas karun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bataur ghaneemat di hai aur unhon-ne wo ( saman ( unhein wapas karne se inkar kar diya.
3321,"Ismail-bin-Jafar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( mujhey matlab-bin-Abdullah-bin-hantab ke Maula Amr-bin-abi-Amr ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : mere liye apne ( Ansar ke) ladkon mein se aik ladka dhoondo jo meri khidmat kiya kare. abu-Talha mujhey sawari par peechhey bithaaey huey lekar nikley aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jahan bhi qiyam farmatey, main aap ki khidmat karta. aur (is ( hadis mein kaha : phir aap ( lot kar) aaey yahan tak ke jab pahaad uahad aap ke samney numaayaan hua to aap ne farmaya : ye pahaad hai jo ham se mohabbat karta hai aur ham is se mohabbat kartey hain. phir jab bulandi se Madina par nigaah dali to farmaya : aey Allah ! main iske donon pahadon ke darmyan ke ilaaqey ko haram qarar deta hun jis tarah Ibrahim ne Makka ko haram qarar diya tha. aey Allah ! un ( ahal Madeena) ke liye unke mudd aur saa mein barkat ata farmaa."
3322,Yaqoob-bin-Abdur-Rehman-al-qaari ne hamein Amr-bin-abi-Amr se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki. magar unhon-ne kaha : main iski donon kaley sangrezon wali zaminon ke darmyani hissey ko haram qarar deta hun.
3323,"Aasim ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina ko haram qarar diya tha? unhon-ne kaha : haan , falan maqam se falan maqam tak (ka ilaqa ( jisne usmein koi bidat nikali, phir unhon-ne mujh se kaha : ye sakht waeed hai : jisne usmein bidat ka irtikaab kiya is par Allah ki farishton ki aur tamam insanon ki laanat hogi, qiyamat ke din Allah Taala uski taraf se na koi uzr aur heela qabool farmaaey ga na koi badla . kaha : ibne- Anas ne kaha : ya ( jisne ( kisi bidat ka irtikaab karne waley ko panah di."
3324,"hamein Aasim ahwal ne khabar di kaha, maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina ko haram qarar diya hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan , ye haram hai uski ghaas na kati jaey jisne aisa kya is par Allah ki, farishton ki, aur sab logon ki laanat hogi."
3325,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! un ( ahale-Madeena) ke liye unke naapney ke paimaaney mein barkat ata farma, unke saa mein barkat ata farma aur unke mudd mein barkat farma."
3326,"Zohri ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! Madina mein us se dugni barkat rakh jitni Makka mein hai."
3327,"hamein abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba Zuhair-bin-Harab aur abu-Kuraib, sab ne abu-Muawiya se hadis bayan ki (kaha ( hamein Aamash ne Ibrahim Taimi se unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne khutba diya aur kaha : jisne ye guman kya ke hamarey paas kitabullah aur us saheefey (ravi ne) kaha : aur wo saheefa unki talwaar ke thailey ke sath latkaa hua tha. ke ilawa kuchh hai jisey ham padhtey hain to usne jhoot bola usmein ( diyat ke) oonton ke daanton ( umaron (aur zakhmon (ki diyat ( kuchh ehkam hain. aur is mein ye hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Eir se Saur tak ke darmyan ( Sara ( Madina haram hai, jisne usmein kisi bidat ka irtikaab kya ya bidat ke kisi murtakib ko panah di, to is par Allah ki farishton ki aur sab logon ki laanat hogi. qiyamat ke din Allah Taala us se koi uzr qabool karega na koi badla aur sab musalmanon ki zimme-dari ( aman ( aik ( jaisi ( hai unka adna shakhs bhi aisa kar sakta hai) aman de sakta hai.) jis shakhs ne apne walid ke siwa kisi aur ka ( beta) honey ka dawa kya ya jis ( ghulam ( ne apne mawali ( aazad karne walon (ke siwa kisi aur ki taraf nisbat ikhtiyar ki is par Allah ki, farishton ki aur sab logon ki laanat hai. qiyamat ke din Allah Taala us na se koi uzr qabool farmaeyga na badla. Abu-Bakr aur Zuhair ki hadis Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farman unka adna shakhs bhi aisa kar sakta hai par khatm ho gaee aur un donon ne wo hissey zikr nahi kya jo iske baad hai aur na unki hadis mein ye alfaz hain : wo unki talwaar ke thailey ke sath latka hua tha."
3328,Ali-bin-Mus-hir aur Wakee donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki jis tarah aakhir tak abu-Muawiya se abu-Kuraib ki riwayat ki hui hadis hai aur (is mein) ye izafa kya : lihaza jisne kisi musalman ki aman todi is par Allah Taala ki) tamam ( farishton ki aur sab insanon ki laanat hai qiyamat ke din us se koi uzr qabool kya jaeyga na badla . un donon ki hadis mein ye alfaz nahi hain jisne apne walid ke siwa kisi aur ki nisbat ikhtiyar ki aur na Wakee ki riwayat mein qiyamat ke din ka tazkira hai.
3329,Sufiyan ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath ibne-Mus-hir aur Wakee ki hadis ki tarah bayan ki magar usmein jisne apne mawali (aazad karne walon) ke ilawa kisi ki taraf nisbat ikhtiyar ki aur is par laanat ka zikr nahi hai.
3330,"Zayda ne Sulaiman se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Madina haram hai jisne usmein koi bidat (Deen ka kaam samajhkar koi aisa kaam karna jiski Deen mein koi haisiyat na ho) ikhtiyar ki ya kisi aise sakhs ko panah di jisne koi bidat ikhtiyar ki ho is par Allah ki, farishton ki, aur sab insanon ki laanat hai. qiyamat ke din na us se koi uzr qabool kya jaeyga na koi badla ."
3331,"Sufiyan ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath isi ki tarah riwayat ki, aur unhon-ne qiyamat ke din ke alfaz nahi kahey aur ye izafa kya : aur tamam musalmanon ka zimma aik ( jaisa ( hai unka adna aadmi bhi panah ki pesh kash! kar sakta hai jisne kisi musalman ki aman todi is par Allah ki farishton ki aur sab insanon ki laanat hai. qiyamat ke din us se koi badla qabool kya jaeyga na koi uzr."
3332,"hamein Yahya-bin-Yahya ne hadis sunai, kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney qirat ki ke ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, wo kaha kartey they : agar main Madina mein hirniyan charti hui dekhun , to main unhein pareshan nahi karunga (kyonke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : iske 2 siyah pathreeley maidaanon ke darmyan ka ilaqa haram hai."
3333,"Mamar ne hamein Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina ke 2 siyah pattharon waley maidaanon ke darmyani hissey ko haram qarar diya hai, Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar main un 2 siyah pathreeley maidaanon ke darmyan hirniyon ko paaun to main unhein pareshan nahi karunga Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina ke ird-gird baara meel ka ilaqa mehfooz charagah qarar diya hai."
3334,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ke samney jin hadison ki qirat ki gaee unmein se Suhel bin abi Saleh ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : log jab ( kisi mausam ka ( pahla phal dekhtey to usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aatey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab usey pakadtey to farmatey : aey Allah ! hamarey phalon mein barkat ata farma, hamarey liye Shahar (Madina ( mein barkat ata farma, hamarey liye hamarey saa mein barkat ata farma aur hamarey mudd mein barkat ata farma. aey Allah ! bila shubah Ibrahim terey bandey terey khaleel aur terey Nabi they main tera banda aur Nabi hun unhon-ne tujh se Makka ke liye dua ki, main tujh se Madina ke liye itni ( barkat ( ki dua karta hun jo unhon-ne Makka ke liye ki aur uske sath itni hi mazeed barkat ki bhi. (abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir aap apne bachchon mein sabse chhotey bachchey ko bulatey aur wo phal usey de detey."
3335,"Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad madni ne hamein Suhel bin abi Saleh se khabar di unhon-ne apne walid se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney jab ( kisi mausam ka ( pahla phal pesh kya jata to aap farmatey : aey Allah ! hamarey liye hamarey Shahar (Madina ( mein, hamarey phalon mein, hamarey mudd main aur hamarey saa mein barkat par barkat farma phir aap wo phal apne paas maujood bachchon mein sabse chhotey bachchey ko de detey."
3336,"Hammad bin Ismail bin-Ulaih ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha :) hamein mere walid ne Wuhaib se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Yahya bin abi Ishaq se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Mehri ke Maula abu-Saeed se hadis bayan ki ke unhein Madina mein bad-hali aur sakhti ne aa liya, wo Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur unse kaha : mera kandan bada hai aur hamein tangdasti ne aa liya hai, mera irada hai ke main apne ghar ke logon ko kisi sar-sabz w shadab ilaqey ki taraf muntaqil kar dun. to Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aisa mat karna, Madina main hi thahrey raho, kyonke ham Allah ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (safar par) nikley. mera khayal hai unhon-ne kaha, yahan tak ke ham asfan pahunchey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahan chand raatein qiyam farmaya, to logon ne kaha : ham yahan kisi khas maqsad ke tehet nahi theharey, aur hamarey khandan ke log peechhey ( akeley ( hain ham unhein mehfooz nahi samajhtey, unki ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye kya baat hai jo tumhari taraf se mujhey pahunchi hai? main nahi janta Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kis tarah farmaya, us zaat ki qism jiski main qism khata hun. ya ( farmaya (us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! maine irada kya ya ( farmaya ( agar tum chaho . main nahi janta ke aap ne un donon mein se kon sa jumla irshad farmaya : main apni ontni par paalaan rakhney ka hukm dun, phir uski aik gireh bhi na kholun yahan tak ke Madina pahunch jaun aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! bila shubah Ibrahim ne Makka ki hurmat ka elaan kya, aur usey haram banaya, aur maine Madina ko iske donon pahadon ke darmyan ko hurmat wala qarar diya ke usmein khoon na bahaya jaey, usmein ladai ke liye aslaha na uthaya jaey aur is mein chaarey ke siwa (kisi aur gharaz se) iske darakhton ke patey na jhaadey jaaein. aey Allah ! hamarey liye hamarey Shahar (Madina ( mein barkat ata farma. aey Allah ! hamarey liye hamarey saa mein barkat ata farma, aey Allah ! hamarey liye hamarey mudd mein barkat ata farma, aey Allah ! hamarey liye hamarey saa mein barkat ata farma, aey Allah ! hamarey liye hamarey mudd mein barkat ata farma, aey Allah ! hamarey liye hamarey Shahar (Madina ( mein barkat ata farma aur us barkat ke sath 2 barkatein (mazeed ata ( kar de. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! Madina ki koi ghaati aur darra nahi magar is par 2 Farishtey hain jo uski hifazat karengey yahan tak ke tum usmein wapas aa jao. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon se farmaya kooch karo. to ham ne kooch kya aur Madina aa gaey. us zaat ki qism jiski ham qism khaatey hain ! ya jiski qism khaai jati hai. ye shak Hammad ki taraf se hai. Madina mein dakhil ho kar ham ne apni sawaariyon ke paalaan bhi nahi utaarey they ke banu- Abdullah-bin Ghatfan ne ham par hamla kar diya aur us se pahley koi cheez unhein mushtail nahi kar rahi thi."
3337,"Ali bin-Mubarak se riwayat hai, (kaha :) hamein Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Mehri ke Maula abu-Saeed ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah ! ne farmaya : Allah hamarey mudd aur saa mein barkat ata farma aur aik barkat ke sath 2 barkatein ( mazeed ( ata farma."
3338,"Sheban aur harab, yani ibne-Shaddad donon ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se isi sanad ke sath, usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
3339,"Saeed bin abu-Saeed ne Mehri ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Saeed se riwayat ki wo saiyedna Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas Harra ki raaton mein aaey (yani jin dinon Madina tayiba mein aik fitna mashhoor hua tha aur zaalimon ne Madina ko loota tha) aur unse mashwara kya ke Madina se kahin aur chaley jayen aur unse wahan ki giraanii narkh (mahngai) aur khandan bada hone ki shikayat ki aur khabar di ke mujhey Madina ki mehnat aur bhook par sabr nahi aa sakta to saiyedna Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke teri kharabi ho mein tujhey iska mashwara nahi doonga (kyonke) maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke wo farmatey they : ke koi shakhs yahan ki takleefon par sabr nahi karta aur phir mar jata hai, magar ye ke main qiyamat ke din iska shafee ya gawah huga agar wo musalman ho."
3340,"Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman bin abi Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Abdur-Rehman ne unhein apne walid abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : main Madina ki 2 siyah pattharon wali zamin ke darmyani hissey ko haram qarar deta hun, jaisey Ibrahim ne Makka ko haram qarar diya tha. kaha : phir abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ham mein se kisi ko pakad letey , aur Abu-Bakar ne kaha : ham mein se kisi ko dekhtey ke uske hath mein parinda hai. to usey uske hath se chhudatey, phir usey aazad kar detey."
3341,"Sahal-bin-Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se Madina ki taraf ishara kya aur Farmaya : bila shubah ye haram hai, amn wala hai."
3342,"Abda ne hamein Hisham se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke jab ham Madina mein) hijrat karke ( aaey to wahan wabaai bukhar phaila hua tha aur saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur saiyedna Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) bimar ho gaey phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ashaab ki bimari dekhi to dua ki ke : aey Allah ! hamarey Madina ko hamarey liye dost kar de jaisey tu ney Makka ko dost kya tha ya us se bhi zyada aur usko sihat ki jagah bana de aur hamein iske ''saa'' aur ''mudd'' mein barkat de aur uske bukhar ko) Johfa ( ki taraf pher de."
3343,abu-Usama aur ibne-Numair donon ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham-mana hadis bayan ki.
3344,"Naafe ne hamein Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : jisne is (Madina) ki tangdasti par sabr kya, main qiyamat ke din uske liye sifarishi hunga."
3345,"Imam Malik ne qatan bin Wahab bin Uwemir bin Ajda se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Zuber ke aazad karda ghulam Yuhannas se riwayat ki, unhon-ne unhein ( qatan ko) khabar di ke wo fitna ( waqia Harra (ke doran mein Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas baithey huey they, unke paas unki aik aazad karda londi salam karne hazir hui aur kaha : abu Abdur-Rehman ! hamarey liye guzar auqat mushkil ho gaee hai lihaza main Madina se naqle-makani karna chahti hun. is par Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : ( yahin Madina mein) baithi raho, nadan aurat ! bila shubah maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : koi bhi uski tangdasti aur sakhti par sabr nahi karta magar qiyamat ke din main uske liye gawah hunga ya sifarishi ."
3346,"Suhak ne hamein qatan Khuzai se khabar di, unhon-ne Musab ke Maula ( Yuhannas) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : jisne us ( Shahar ( ki tangdasti aur sakhti par sabr kya, main qiyamat ke din uska gawah hunga ya sifarishi. unki murad Madina se thi."
3347,"Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman (bin Yaqoob ( ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat mein se koi shakhs Madina ki tangdasti aur mashaqqat par sabr nahi karta magar qiyamat ke din , main iska sifarishi ya gawah hunga."
3348,"abu Abdullah qaraz kehtey hain : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ( aagey ( usi ki tarah hai."
3349,"Saleh bin Abu-Saleh ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi bhi Madina ki mashaqqaton par sabr nahi karta. (aagey) usi ki tarah hai."
3350,"Naeem bin-Abdullah ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Madina mein dakhil honey ke raston par Farishtey muqarrar hain, usmein taaoon aur dajjal dakhil nahi ho sakega."
3351,"Ismail bin Jafar se riwayat hai, (kaha : ( Alaa ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mashriq ki taraf se Masih dajjal aayega , uska irada Madina (mein daakhiley ka ( hoga yahan tak ke wo Uhud pahaad ke peechhey utrega, phir Farishtey uska rukh Sham (Syria) ki taraf pher dengey aur wahin wo halaak ho jaeyga"
3352,"hamein Abdul-Azeez yani darawardi ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Alaa se unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne saiyedna-abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik waqt logon par aisa aayega ke aadmi apne bhatijey aur apne qaraabat waley ko pukaarey ga ke khush'haalii ke mulk mein, khush'haalii ke mulk mein chalo. halanke Madina unke liye behtar hoga kaash! ! ke wo jantey hotey aur qism hai us parwardigar ki ke meri jaan jiske hath mein hai ke koi shakhs Madina se bezaar ho kar nahi nikalta, magar Allah Taala us se behtar doosra shakhs Madina mein bhej deta hai. aagah raho ke Madina lohaar ki bhattii ki manind (tarah) hai ke wo mail ko nikal deta hai. aur qiyamat qaaim na hogi jab tak ke Madina apne shareer logon ko nikal na dega jaisey ke bhattii lohey ki mail ko nikal deti hai."
3353,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha, maine abu-hubaab-Saeed-bin-Yasar se suna, wo keh rahe they, maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey aik basti (ki taraf hijrat kar janey (ka hukm diya gaya jo tamam bastiyon ko kha jaeygi (sab par ghalib aa jaeygi) log usey yasrib kehtey hain, wo Madina hai, wo ( shareer ( logon ko nikal degi jaisey bhattii lohey ke mail ko bahar nikal deti hai."
3354,Sufiyan aur Abdul-Wahaab donon ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur donon ne kaha : jaisey bhattii mail ko nikal deti hai un donon ne lohey ka zikr nahi kiya.
3355,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik baddu ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki. iske baad us baddu ko Madiney mein bukhar ne aa liya, wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, aur kehney laga : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mujhey meri bait wapas kar dein. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne inkar farma diya. phir wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kehney laga. mujhey meri bait wapas kar dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dobara inkar kar diya, phir wo (teesri baar ( aaya, aur kaha : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mujhey meri bait wapas kar dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( phir ( inkar farmaya, iske baad dehati nikal gaya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Madina bhatti ki tarah hai, wo apne mel-kuchel (burey logon) ko bahar nikal deta hai aur yahan ka pakeeza ( khalis eman wala) nikhar jata hai."
3356,"Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah ye taiba ( paak ( hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad Madina se thi. ye mail kuchail ko is tarah door kar deta hai jaisey aag chandi ke mail kuchail ko nikal deti hai."
3357,"Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna, bila shubah Allah Taala ne Madina ka naam taaba rakha hai."
3358,"Abdullah-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yuhannas ne mujhey abu-Abdullah qaraaz se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : main Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein gawahi deta hun ke unhon-ne kaha : abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo is Shahar (yani Madeena) walon ki burai ka irada karta hai, to Allah Taala usko aisa pighlaa deta hai jaisey namak pani mein pighal jata hai."
3359,"Muhammad-bin-Hatim aur Ibrahim bin-Dinar ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha, ham se Hajjaj ne hadis bayan ki, neez Muhammad-bin Raafe ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Abdur-Razzaq ne hadis sunai, unhon ( Hajjaj aur Abdur-Razzaq ( ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Yahya-bin-Ammara ne khabar di ke unhon-ne (abu Abdullah) qaraaz se suna aur wo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sathiyon ( shagirdon) mein se they, wo yaqin se kehtey they ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne iske baashindon ke sath . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad Madina se thi. burai ka irada kya. Allah usey is tarah pighla dega jis tarah namak pani mein pighal jata hai. ibne- Hatim ne ibne- ( Yuhannas ( ki hadis mein soo ( buraaii) ki jagah shar ( nuqsan (ka lafz bayan kya."
3360,"abu Harun Musa bin abi Esa aur Muhammad-bin Amr donon ne abu Abdullah qaraz se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat kartey huey suna."
3361,"Hatim, yani ibne-Ismail ne hamein Umar-bin nabiya se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Dinar qaraz ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne ahale-Madina ke sath burai ka irada kya Allah Taala usey is tarah pighla dega jis tarah namak pani mein pighal jata hai."
3362,"Ismail bin Jafar ne hamein Umar-bin nabiya kabi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu Abdullah qaraaz se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Sad bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( aagey ( usi ki tarah hai, albatta unhon-ne kaha : badi museebat ya burai (main mubtala karne) ka irada kya."
3363,"Usama-bin-Zaid ne hamein abu Abdullah qaraaz se hadis bayan ki, ( Usama ne) kaha : maine unse suna, keh rahe they : maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo donon keh rahe they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! ahale-Madina ke liye unke mudd mein barkat ata farmaa. aagey (usi tarah) hadis bayan ki aur is mein hai : jisne iske baashindon ke sath burai ka irada kya, Allah Taala usey is tarah pighla dega jis tarah pani mein namak pighal jata hai."
3364,"Wakee ne hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Sufiyan bin abi Zuhair (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Sham (Syria) fateh kar liya jaeyga to kuchh log intihai tezi se oont haanktey huey apne ahal w ayaal samet Madina se nikal jaeinge , halanke Madina unke liye behtar hoga agar wo jantey hon. phir Yaman fateh hoga to kuchh log tez raftaari se oont haanktey huey apne ahal w ayaal samet Madina se nikal jaeinge , halanke Madina unke liye behtar hoga agar wo jantey hon, phir Iraq fateh hoga to kuchh log tezi se oont haanktey huey apne ahal w ayaal samet Madina se nikal jaeinge halanke Madina unke liye behtar hoga agar wo jantey hon."
3365,"hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, (kaha : ( mujhey Hisham-bin-Urwa ne apne walid se khabar di, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Sufiyan-bin-abi-Zuhair (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : saiyedna Sufiyan-bin-abi-Zuhair (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke : Yaman fateh hoga to kuchh log Madina se apne oonton ko haanktey huey apne ghar walon aur khadimon ke sath niklengey. halanke Madina unke liye behtar hoga. kaash! ! wo jantey hotey . phir Sham (Syria) fateh hoga aur Madina ki aik qaum apne ghar walon aur khadimon ke sath , oonton ko haanktey huey nikley gii aur Madina unke liye behtar hoga, kaash! ! wo jantey. phir Iraq fateh hoga aur Madina ki aik qaum apne ghar walon aur khuddaam ke sath apne oonton ko haanktey huey nikley gii halanke Madina unke haq mein behtar hoga, kaash! ! wo jantey."
3366,"abu-safwaan aur ibne- Wahab ne Younus-bin-Yazeed se, unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina ke barey mein farmaya : iske rehney waley iske behtreen haalat mein honey ke bawajud isey us haalat mein chhod dengey ke wo khuraak ke talaash karne waalon ke qadmon ke nichey raundaa ja raha hoga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad darindon aur parindon se thi. Imam Muslim ne kaha : ye abu Safwan , Abdullah-bin-abdul-Malik hai, das saal tak ibne-Juraij ka ( parwarda ( yateem , jo unki god mein tha."
3367,"Aqeel-bin-Khalid ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke log Madina ko iske khair honey ke bawajud chhod dengey aur is mein koi na rahega siwaey darindon aur parindon ke. phir qabila muzena se do charwaahey apni bakriyon ko pukaartey huey Madina ( janey (ka irada kartey huey niklengey aur wo Madina ko weeraan paeingey yahan tak ke jab saniiyatul-wadaa' tak pahunchein gey to apne munh ke bal gir padiin gey ."
3368,"Abdullah-bin-Abu-Bakar ne Ibad-bin-Tameem se unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Zaid (bin-Aasim ( Mazni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo ( jagah ( mere ghar aur mere member ke darmyan hai, wo jannat ke baaghon mein se aik baagh hai."
3369,"Abu-Bakar ne Ibad Tameem se unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Zaid Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : jo ( jagah ( mere ghar aur mere member ke darmyan hai, wo jannat ke baaghon mein se aik baagh hai."
3370,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere ghar aur mere member ke darmyan (ki jagah ( jannat ke baaghon mein se aik baagh hai. aur mera member mere hauz par hai.
3371,"Hazrat abu Humaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha : jange-Tabook ke mauqe par ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley.aur ( aagey ( hadis bayan ki usmein hai phir ham (safar se wapas ( aaey yahan tak ke ham wadi mein pahunchey, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main apni raftaar tez karne wala hun. tum mein se jo chahey wo mere sath tezi se aa jaey aur jo chahey wo thahar kar aa jaey. phir ham nikley yahan tak ke jab bulandi se hamari nigaah Madina par padi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye taaba (pak karne wala Shahar) hai aur ye uahad hai aur ye pahaad (aisa) hai jo ham se mohabbat karta hai aur ham is se mohabbat kartey hain."
3372,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ne ham se hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( mere walid ne hamein hadis sunai, (kaha : ( hamein Qurra-bin-Khalid ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : be-shak uahad aisa pahaad hai jo ham se mohabbat karta hai aur ham us se mohabbat kartey hain."
3373,"Harmi-bin-Umara ne mujhey pichhli sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Uhud pahaad ki taraf dekha aur farmaya : be-shak uhud aisa pahaad hai jo ham se mohabbat karta hai aur ham us se mohabbat kartey hain."
3374,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, wo usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchatey they aap ne farmaya : meri is masjid mein aik Namaz dusri masjidon mein aik hazaar namazon se afzal hai siwaey Masjide-Haram ke."
3375,"Mamar ne hamein Zohri se khabar di unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri is masjid mein aik Namaz kisi bhi aur masjid ki aik hazaar namazon se behtar hai siwaey Masjide-Haram (ki Namaz ( ke."
3376,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman aur juhaina walon ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Abdullah Agharr se riwayat hai, aur ye Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sathiyon ( shaagirdon) mein se they. un donon ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki masjid mein aik Namaz Masjide-Haram ko chhod kar dusri masaajid mein aik hazaar namazon se afzal hai. bila shubah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tamam anbiya mein se aakhiri hain, aur aap ki masjid ( bhi kisi Nabi ki tameer karda ( aakhiri masjid hai. abu-Salma aur abu-Abdullah ne kaha : hamein is barey mein shak na tha ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis se bayan kar rahe hain. chunanche isi baat ne hamein ro ke rakha ke ham Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se is hadis ke barey mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sun-ney ka)  saboot farhaam karaaein. yahan tak ke jab Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey to ham ne aapas mein is baat ka tazkira kiya aur aik doosrey ko malamat ki, ke ham ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se is barey mein guftgu kyon nahi ki? taake agar unhon-ne ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi to uski nisbat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf kar detey. ham isi kaifiyat mein they ke Abdullah-bin-Ibrahim-bin-qaariz hamarey sath majlis mein aa baithey to ham ne is hadis ka aur jis baat ke barey mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se sarahat karaaney mein ham ne kotahi ki thi ka tazkira kiya. to Abdullah-bin-Ibrahim-bin-qaariz ne hamein kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah mein tamam anbiya mein se aakhiri Nabi hon aur meri masjid aakhiri masjid hai. (jisey kisi Nabi ne tameer kya.)"
3377,"Abdul Wahab ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha, maine Yahya-bin-Saeed ko kehtey huey suna ke maine abu saaleh se puchha : kya aap ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki masjid mein Namaz padhney ki fazeelat bayan kartey huey suna hai? unhon-ne kaha : nahi albatta mujhey Abdullah-bin-Ibrahim-bin-qaariz ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri is masjid mein aik Namaz iske siwa (doosri ( masjidon ki aik hazaar namazon se behtar . ya farmaya : aik hazaar namazon ki tarah hai.siwaye iske ke wo Masjide-Haram ho."
3378,Yahya qattaan ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se isi sanad ke sath (yahi) hadis bayan ki.
3379,"Yahya qattaan ne hamein Ubaidullah (bin Umar) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri is masjid mein aik Namaz iske siwa (doosri masjidon mein) aik hazaar namazein ada karne se afzal hai siwaey masjide-haram ke."
3380,abu-Usama Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Abdul Wahab sab ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath (ye) hadis bayan ki.
3381,"Musa Johni ne Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they. (aagey) usi ki tarah hai."
3382,Ayub ne Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
3383,"Leis ne Naafe se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Ibrahim bin-Abdullah-bin Mabad (bin Abbas) se riwayat ki, (kaha :) Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne kaha : aik aurat bimar ho gaee usne kaha : agar Allah ne mujhey shifa di to main baitul-maqdis mein ja kar zaroor Namaz ada karungi. wo sihatyab ho gaee, phir safar ke iraadey se taiyari ki (safar se pahley) wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein salam kehney ke liye hazir hui aur unhein ye sab bataya to Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne us se kaha : baith jao aur jo (zaade-rah) tum ne taiyaar kya hai wo kha lo aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki masjid mein Namaz padh lo. bila shubah ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : is (masjid ( mein aik Namaz padhna iske siwa ( baqi ( tamam masaajid mein aik hazaar namazein ada karne se afzal hai siwaey masjid Kaba ke."
3384,"Sufiyan ne Zohri se unhon-ne Saeed (bin Musaiyab) se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki wo us (silsilae-riwayat ( ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchatey they ke (ibadat ke liye) teen masjidon ke siwa rakhte-safar na baandha jaey : meri ye masjid, masjide-haram aur masjide-aqsaa."
3385,"Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, albatta unhon-ne kaha : (ibadat ke liye) teen masjidon ki taraf rakhte-safar baandha ja sakta hai."
3386,"Salman Agharr ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bata rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sirf teen masjidon ki taraf hi ( ibadat ke liye) safar kya ja sakta hai. Kaba ki masjid meri masjid aur Eliya ki masjid (masjide-Aqsa.)"
3387,"Humaid kharrat se riwayat hai kaha : maine abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se suna unhon-ne kaha : Abdur-Rehman bin abi Saeed Khudri mere yahan se guzrey to maine unse kaha : aap ne apne walid ko us masjid ke barey mein jiski buniyaad taqwa par rakhi gaee, kis tarah zikr kartey huey suna? unhon-ne kaha : mere walid ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aap ki aik ahliya mohtarma ke ghar mein hazir hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! donon masjidon mein se kon si (masjid ( hai jiski baniyad taqwa par rakhi gaee hai? kaha : aap ne muththi bhar kankriyaan lin aur unhein zamin par maara phir farmaya : wo tumhari yahi masjid hai. Madina ki masjid ke barey mein. (abu-Salma ne) kaha : to maine kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke maine bhi tumharey walid se suna, wo isi tarah bayan kar rahe they."
3388,Humaid (Taweel) ne abu-Salma se unhon-ne abu-Saeed khudii (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi manind (tarah) riwayat ki. aur unhon-ne sanad mein Abdur-Rehman bin abu-Saeed ka zikr nahi kya (barahe-raast Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki)
3389,"Ayub ne hamein Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Sawar ho kar aur (kabhi) paidal Quba ki ziyarat farmatey they."
3390,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Abdullah-bin-Numair aur abu-Usama ne Ubaidullah se hadis sunai. isi tarah Muhammad-bin Numer ne hamein hadis sunai, (kaha : ( mere walid ne hamein hadis sunai, (kaha : ( hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Sawar ho kar aur) paidal donon tarah se) Quba tashrif latey aur wahan 2 rakatein ada farmatey Abu-Bakar ne apni riwayat mein kaha : (ye abu-Usama ne nahi balke) ibne-Numair ne kaha : aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan 2 rakatein Namaz ada kartey."
3391,"hamein Yahya ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha :) hamein Ubaidullah ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha :) mujhey Naafe ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Sawar ho kar aur paidal Quba tashrif laya kartey they."
3392,"Khalid-bin Haris ne hamein ibne- Ajlan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Yahya qattan ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
3393,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney qirat ki ke Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Sawar ho kar aur paidal Quba tashrif laya kartey they."
3394,"hamein Ismail bin Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( mujhey Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Sawar ho kar aur paidal Quba tashrif laya kartey they."
3395,"mujhey Zuhair-bin-Harab ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis sunai. unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat ki ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) har haftey ke roz Quba aatey they wo kaha kartey they : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aap har haftey ke roz yahan tashrif latey they."
3396,ibne-abi-Umar ne Sufiyan se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har haftey ke roz Quba aatey aap wahan Sawar ho kar aur (kabhi) paidal tashrif latey they. ibne- Dinar ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) bhi) aisa hi kartey they.
3397,"Sufiyan Sory ne ibne- Dinar se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, magar har haftey ke roz ka zikr nahi kya."
